hadiths[441]{hadithnumber,text}:
93,"Kahmas ne ibne-bareeda se, unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Yamar se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke sabse pahlaa shakhs jisne Basra mein taqdeer (se inkaar) ki baat ki, Mabad Johni tha main ( Yahya (aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman Himyarii Haj ya Umerey ke iraadey se nikley, ham ne ( aapas mein) kaha : kash! ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kisi ke sath hamari mulaqat ho jaey to ham unse taqdeer ke barey mein un ( aaj kal ke) logon ki kahi hui baton ke mutaalliq malum kar lein. taufeeqe-Ilaahii se hamein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein dakhil hotey huey mil gaey. main aur mere sath ne unko darmyan mein ley liya, aik unki daain taraf tha aur doosra unki baain taraf . mujhey andaza tha ke mera sathi guftgu (ka mamla ( mere sipurd karega, to maine kaha : aey abu Abdur-Rehman ! (ye Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat hai) waqia ye hai ke hamari taraf kuchh aisey log zahir huey jo Quran Majeed padhtey hain aur ilm hasil kartey hain (aur unke halaat bayan kiye ( un logon ka khayal hai ke taqdeer kuchh nahi, (har ( kaam naey sirey se ho raha hai (pahley us barey mein na kuchh tay hai, na Allah ko iska ilm hai.) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jab tumhari un logon se mulaqat ho to unhein bata dena ke main unse barii hon aur wo mujh se barii hain. us ( zaat ( ki qism jis (ke naam (ke sath Abdullah-bin-Umar Halaf uthata hai! agar unmein se kisi ke paas uhud pahaad ke barabar sona ho aur wo usey kharch ( bhi) kar de to Allah Taala uski taraf se usko qabool nahi farmaaega yahan tak ke wo taqdeer par eman ley aaey, phir kaha : mujhey mere walid umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya : aik din ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke achcha aik shakhs hamarey samney namudaar hua. iske kapdey intihai safaid aur baal intihai siyah they. is par safar ka koi asar dikhai deta tha na ham mein se koi usey pehchanta tha yahan tak ke wo aa kar Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baith gaya aur apne ghutney aap ke ghutnon se mila diye, aur apne hath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raanon par rakh diye, aur kaha : aey Muhammad (sl)! mujhey Islam ke barey mein bataaiye. rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Islam ye hai ke tum is baat ki gawahi 2 ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske rasool hain, Namaz ka ehtimaam karo, zakat ada karo, Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur agar Allah ke ghar tak rasta ( tay karne) ki istitaat ho to uska Haj karo. ' usne kaha : aap ne sach farmaya, (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : hamein is par tajjub hua ke aap se poochhta hai aur) khud hi (aap ki tasdeeq karta hai. usne kaha : mujhey eman ke barey mein bataiye . aap ne farmaya : ye ke tum Allah Taala , uske farishton , uski kitaabon, uske rasulon aur aakhiri din (yaume-qiyaamat) par eman rakho aur achi aur buri taqdeer par bhi eman laao.' usne kaha : aap ne durust farmaya, ( phir ( usne kaha : mujhey ehsan ke barey mein bataaiye. aap ne farmaya : ye ke tum Allah Taala ki ibadat is tarah karo maano tum usey dekh rahe ho aur agar tum usey nahi dekh rahe to wo tumhen dekh raha hai.' usne kaha : to mujhey qiyamat ke barey mein bataaiye. aap ne farmaya : jis se us (qiyamat (ke barey mein sawal kya ja raha hai, wo poochhney waley se zyada nahi jaantaa.' usne kaha : to mujhey uski alaamaat bata diijiye. aap ne farmaya : ( alaamaat ye hain ke) londi apni maalika ko janm de aur ye ke tum nangey paaun, nangey badan, mohtaaj, bakriyan charaney walon ko dekho ke wo unchi se unchi Imaaratein banaaney mein aik doosrey ke sath muqaabla kar rahe hain.' hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir wo saail chala gaya, mein kuchh der usi aalim mein raha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se kaha : aey umar! tumhen malum hai ke poochhney wala kon thaa?' maine kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada aagah hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo Jibreel they, tumharey paas aaey they, tumhen tumhara Deen sikhaa rahe they.'"
94,"Kahmas ke bajaey Matar Warraaq ne Abdullah-bin Barida se, unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Yamar se naql kya ke jab Mabad ( Johni ( ne taqdeer ke barey mein wo (sab ( kaha jo kaha, to ham ne usey sakht na-pasand kya ( Yahya ne kaha ( main aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman Himyari ne Haj kya. . . . iske baad unhon-ne Kahmas ke waastey se bayan ki hui hadis ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki, albatta alfaz mein kuchh kami beshi hai."
95,"( Abdullah-bin Barida ke aik teesrey shagird ( Usmaan-bin-Ghiyaas ne Yahya-bin-Yamar aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman donon se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha : ham Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se miley aur ham se taqdeer ki baat ki aur wo log ( taqdeer ke munkir ( jo kuchh kehtey hain, iska zikr kya. iske baad) Usmaan-bin-Ghiyaas ne) pichhle rawiyon ke mutabiq Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marfooan riwayat ki. is riwayat mein kuchh alfaz zyada hain aur kuchh unhon-ne kam kiye hain."
96,"Motamir ke walid ( Sulaiman-bin-Tarkhan ( ne Yahya-bin-Yamar se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah mazkura (uper zikr) ustaadon ne riwayat ki."
97,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ( ibne-Ulaih ( ne abu-Hayyan se, unhon-ne abu-Zura bin-Amr bin Jarir se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din logon ke samney ( tashrif farma ( they, aik aadmi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! eman kya hai? aap ne farmaya : tum Allah Taala , uske farishton , uski kitab , (qiyamat ke roz (us se mulaqat ( uske samney haziri (aur uske rasulon par eman lao aur aakhiri ( baar zinda ho kar) uthney par) bhi) eman ley aao.' usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Islam kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Islam ye hai ke Allah Taala ki ibadat karo aur uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na thehrao , likhi ( farz ki) gaee namazon ki pabandi karo, farz ki gaee zakat ada karo aur Ramazan ke rozey rakho . usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ehsan kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ki ibadat is tarah karo maano tum usey dekh rahe ho aur agar tum usey nahi dekh rahe ho to wo yaqinan tumhen dekh raha hai.' usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! qiyamat Kab ( qaaim ( hogii? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis se sawal kya gaya hai, wo iske barey mein poochhney waley se zyada aagah nahi. lekin main tumhen qiyamat ki nishaniyan bataaey deta hun : jab londi apna Malik janegi to ye uski nishaniyon mein se hai, aur jab nangey badan aur nangey paon waley logon ke sardaar bin jaaengey to ye uski nishaniyon mein se hai, aur jab bhed-bakriyaan charaney waale, unchi oonchii Imaaratein banaaney mein aik doosrey se muqaabla karengey to ye uski alaamaat mein se hai. (qiyamat ke waqt ka ilm (in panch chizon mein se hai jinhein Allah Taala ke siwa koi nahi janta hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhi : beshak Allah Taala hi ke paas qiyamat ka ilm hai, wahi barish barsata hai aur wahi janta hai ke maaon ke peton mein kya hai, koi zii-rooh nahi janta ke wo kal kya karega, na kisi jaan ko ye malum hai ke wo zamin ke kis hissey mein faut hoga, bila shubah Allah Taala ilm wala khabardaar hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir wo aadmi wapas chala gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is aadmi ko mere paas wapas laao.' sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) usey wapas laney ke liye bhaag-daud karne lagey to unhein kuchh nazar na aaya, Rasulullah ne farmaya : ye Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ they jo logon ko unka Deen sikhaney aaey they."
98,"( ibne-Ulaih ke bajaey) Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein abu-Hayyan ne pichhli sanad se wahi hadis bayan ki, albatta unki riwayat mein : (إذا ولدت الأمة بعلها),' jab londi apna Malik janey gii,' (rab) ki jagah (ba'l), yani Maalik) ke alfaz hain. ((أمة) se mamlooka) laundiyaan murad hain."
99,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (sl) ne farmaya : mujhse (deen ke barey mein) poochh lo. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) Aapse itney mar'oob huey ke sawal na kar sakey, tab aik aadmi aaya aur aapke donon ghutnon ke qareeb baith gaya, phir kehney laga : Aey Allah ke rasool! Islam kya hai? Aapne farmaya : Tum Allah Taala ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thehraao, Namaz ka ehtimaam karo, zakat ada karo aur Ramazan ke rozey rakho. Usne kaha : Aapne sach farmaya, (phir) puchha : Aey Allah ke rasool! eman kya hai? Aapne farmaya : ye ke tum Allaah, uske farishton, uski kitaab, (qiyamat ke roz) usse mulaqat aur uske rasulon par eman laao, marney ke baad uthney par eman lao aur har (Amr ki) taqdeer par eman laao. Usne kaha : Aapne durust farmaya, (phir) kehney laga : Aey Allah ke rasool! ehsan kya hai? Aapne farmaya : Tum Allah Taala se is tarah daro maano tum usey dekh rahe ho, phir agar tum usey nahi dekh rahe to wo yaqinan tumhen dekh raha hai. Usne kaha : Aapne sahi farmaya : (phir) puchha : Aey Allah ke rasool! qiyamat Kab qaaim hogii? Aapne jawab diya : Jisse qiyamat ke barey mein puchha ja raha hai, wo poochhney waley se zyada nahi janta. Main tumhen uski alaamaat bataaey deta hun : Jab dekho ke aurat apne aaqa ko janm deti hai to ye uski nishaniyon mein se hai aur jab dekho ke nangey paon aur nangey badan waale, goongey aur behrey zamin ke badshah hain to ye uski alaamaat mein se hain aur jab dekho ke bhaidh bakriyon ke charwaahey unchi se unchi imaarat banaaney mein aapasii muqaabla kar rahe hain to ye bhi uski nishaniyon mein se hai. Ye (qiyaamat ka hona) ghaib ki un panch chizon mein se hai jinko Allah Taala ke siwa koi nahi janta. Phir aapne ye aayat padhi : Beyshak Allah Taala hi ke paas qiyamat ka ilm hai, wahi barish barsata hai aur wahi janta hai ke maaon ke peton mein kya hai aur koi shakhs nahi janta ke wo aaney waley kal mein kya karega aur koi shakhs nahi janta ke wo (kahaan) kis zamin mein faut hoga. . . . . . sura ke aakhir tak. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir wo aadmi khada ho gaya (aur chala gaya) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey mere paas wapas laao. Usey talash kiya gaya to wo unhein (sahaaba kiram ko) na mila. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ye Jibreel they, unhon-ne chaha ke tum nahi poochh rahe to tum (deen) seekh lo (unhon-ne aakar tumhari taraf se sawal kiya)."
100,"Malik-bin-Anas ne Abu Suhel se, aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ahle Najd mein se aik aadmi aaya, uske baal paraa-ganda they, ham uski halki si awaz sun rahe they lekin jo kuch wo keh raha tha ham usko samajh nahi rahe they yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb aa gaya, wo aapse Islam ke barey mein poochh raha tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : din aur raat mein panch namazein (farz) hain. Usne puchha : Kya inke ilawa (aur namaazein) bhi mere zimmey hain? Aapne farmaya : nahi, siwaey iske ke tum nafli Namaz padho aur maahe Ramazan ke rozey hain. Usne puchha : Kya mere zimmey iske ilawa bhi (rozey) hain? farmaya : nahi, siwaey iske ke tum nafli rozey rakho. Phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey zakat ke barey mein bataya to usne sawal kiya : kya mere zimmey iske siwa bhi kuchh hai? Aapne jawab diya : nahi, siwaey iske ke tum apni marzii se (naflii sadqa) do. (Hazrat Talha ne) kahaa: Phir wo aadmi wapas hua to keh raha tha : Allah ki qasam! Main na ispar koi izafa karunga na usmein koi kami karunga. Ispar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye falaah pa gaya agar isne sach kar dikhaayaa."
101,"Ismail bin Jafar ne Abu Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, siwaey iske ke kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Kaamyaab hua, iske bap ki qasam! Agar isne sach kar dikhaayaa, ya (farmaayaa :) , jannat mein dakhil hoga, iske bap ki qasam! Agar isne sach kar dikhaayaa."
102,"Haashim bin Qasim Abu Nazr ne kaha : Humein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Sabit ke hawale se ye hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (ghair zaroori taur par) kisi cheez ke barey mein sawal karne se rok diya gaya to humein bahut achchha lagta tha ke koi samajhdaar baadiya nasheen aapki khidmat mein hazir ho aur aapse sawal karey aur ham (bhi jawaab) sunein, chunanche aik badwi aaya aur kehney laga : Aey Muhammad! aapka qaasid humaarey paas aaya tha, usne humse kaha ke aap farmatey hain : Allah Taala ne aapko rasool banaakar bheja hai. Aapne farmaya : Usne sach kaha. Usne puchha : aasman kisne banaya hai? Aapne jawab diya : Allah ne. Usne kaha : zamin kisne banaaii? Aapne farmaya : Allah ne. Usne sawal kiya : Ye pahaad kisne gaadey hain aur unmein jo kuchh rakha hai kisne rakha hai? Aapne farmaya : Allah ne. badwi ne kaha is zaat ki qism hai jisne aasman banaya, zamin banai aur ye pahaad nasab kiye! Kya Allah hi ne aapko (rasool banaakar) bheja hai? Aapne jawab diya : Haan. Usne kaha : Aapke qaasid ne bataya hai ke humaarey din aur raat mein humaarey zimmey panch namazein hain. Aapne farmaya : Usne durust kaha. Usne kaha is zaat ki qism jisne aapko bheja hai! Kya Allah hi ne aapko iska hukm diya hai? Aapne jawab diya : Haan. Usne kaha : Aapke eilchii ka khayal hai ke hamarey zimmey hamarey maalon ki zakat hai. Aapne farmaayaa: Usne sach kaha, badwi ne kaha : Us zaat ki qism jisne aapko rasool banaayaa! Kya Allah hi ne aapko ye hukm diya hai? Aapne jawab diya : Haan. Ea'raabii ne kaha : Aapke eilchii ka khayal hai ke hamarey saal mein hamarey zimmey maahe Ramazan ke rozey hain. Aapne farmaya : Usne sahi kaha. Usne kaha is zaat ki qism jisne aapko bheja hai! kya Allah hi ne aapko iska hukm diya hai? Aapne farmaya : Haan. Wo kehney laga : Aapke bhejey huey (qaasid) ka khayal hai ke ham par Baitullah ka Haj farz hai, us shakhs par jo iske rastey (ko tay karne) ki istitaat rakhta ho. Aapne farmaya : Usne sach kaha. (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha :) Phir wo wapas chal padaa aur (chaltey chaltey) kaha is zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai! Main un par koi izafa karunga na unmein koi kami karunga. Ispar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Agar isne sach kar dikhaya to yaqinan jannat mein dakhil hoga."
103,"Bahz ne kaha : Humein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Sabit se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Humein Quran Majeed mein is baat se mana kar diya gaya ke (bilaa-zaroorat) kisi cheez ke barey mein aapse sawal karein. . . . iske baad (bahz ne) usi ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki."
104,"Amr bin Usman ne kaha : Humein Musa-bin-Talha ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Mujhey Hazrat Abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they jab aik dehati aapke samney aa khada hua, usne aapki ontni ki mahaar ya nakel pakad li, phir kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! (ya aey Muhammad!) mujhey wo baat bataiye jo mujhey jannat ke qareeb aur aag se door kar de. Abu Ayub ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ruk gaey, phir apne sathiyon par nazar daudaaii, phir farmaya : Isko taufeeq mili (yaa hidayat milii), phir badwi se puchha : Tum ne kya baat ki? Usne apni baat dohraaii to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Tum Allah Taala ki bandagii karo, uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraao, Namaz qaaim karo, zakat ada karo aur silaa rehmii karo. (ab) ontni ko chhod do."
105,"Muhammad bin Usman bin Abdullah bin mauhab aur unke walid Usman donon ne Musa-bin-Talha se suna, wo Hazrat Abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo nabii (sl) se pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) bayan kartey they."
106,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi aur Abu Bakr bin abi Shaiba ne kaha : Humein Abu Ahwas ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Musa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur puchha : Mujhey koi aisa kaam bataiye jispar main amal karun to wo mujhey jannat ke qareeb aur aag se door kar de. Aapne farmaya : ye ke to Allah ki bandagii karey, uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraaey, Namaz ki pabandi karey, zakat ada karey aur apne rishtedaron se sila rehmii kare. Jab wo peeth pherkar chal diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Agar usne in chizon ki pabandi ki jinka usey hukm diya gaya hai to jannat mein dakhil hoga. ibne-abi Shaiba ki riwayat mein hai :  Agar usne uski pabandi ki (to jannat mein dakhil hoga)."
107,"Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! Mujhey aisa amal bataiye ke jab main uspar amal karun to jannat mein dakhil ho jaun. Aapne farmaya : Tum Allah ki bandagii karo, uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraao, Namaz qaaim karo jo tumpar likh di gaee hai, farz zakat ada karo aur Ramazan ke rozey rakho. Wo kehney laga is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! Main na kabhi ispar kisi cheez ka izafa karunga aur na ismein kami karunga. Jab wo wapas janey laga to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisey is baat se khushi ho ke wo aik jannati aadmi dekhey to wo usey dekh ley."
108,"Abu Muaawia ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Nauman bin Qauqal (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! Aap kya farmatey hain ke jab main farz Namaz ada karun haram ko haram aur halal ko halal samjhoon to kya main jannat mein dakhil ho jaaunga? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Haan!"
109,"Shaibaan ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh aur Abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nauman bin Qauqal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! . . . . . phir us pichhli riwayat ki tarah hai aur is mein ye izafa kiya : Aur uspar kisi cheez ka izafa na karunga."
110,"Salama bin Shabeeb, Hasan bin Aa'yan, Maaqil yani ibne- Ubaidullaah, Abu Zubair, Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hokar arz kiya ke agar main farz Namaz padhta rahoon aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhoon aur halal ko halal samjhoon aur haram ko haraam, isse zyada kuchh na karun to aapki kya raey hai ke kya main jannat mein dakhil ho jaaungaa? To aapne farmaya : Haan! Us shakhs ne arz kiya : Allah ki qasam! Main isse zyada kuchh nahi karunga."
111,"Abu Khalid Sulaiman-bin-Hayyan Ahmar ne abu-Malik Ashjai se, unhon-ne Saad bin Ubeda se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Islam ki buniyad panch chizon par rakhi gaee hai : Allah ko Yakta qarar deney, Namaz qaaim karney, zakat ada karney, Ramazan ke rozey rakhney aur Haj karney par. aik shakhs ne kaha : Haj karney aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhney par? Ibne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : nahi. Ramazan ke rozey rakhney aur Haj karney par. Maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat isi tarah (isii tarteeb se) suni thi."
112,"Yahya bin Zakariya ne humein hadis bayan ki, kaha : Mujhey Saad bin Tariq (Abu Malik Ashjaii) ne hadis bayan ki. wo Hazrat Ibne Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Islam ki buniyad panch chizon par hai : ispar ke Allah ki ibadat ki jaey aur uske siwa har kisii ki ibadat se inkar kiya jaey, Namaz qaaim karne, zakat dene, Baitullah ka Haj karne aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhney par."
113,"Aasim bin-Muhammad bin Zaid Abdullah bin umr ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Islam ki buniyad panch (ruknon) par rakhi gaee hai is haqiqat ki (dil, zaban aur baad mein zikr kiye gaey buniyadi aamaal ke zariey se) gawahi dena ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske bandey aur uske rasool hain, Namaz qaaim karnaa, zakat ada karnaa, Baitullah ka Haj karna aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhnaa."
114,"Ikrima bin Khaalid, Taaus ko hadis suna rahe they ke aik aadmi ne Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Kya aap jihad mein hissey nahi letey? Unhon-ne jawab diya : Bila shubah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : Islam ki buniyad panch chizon par rakhi gaee hai : (is haqiqat ki) gawahi dene par ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, Namaz qaaim karne, zakat ada karne, Ramazan ke rozey rakhney aur Baitullah ka Haj karne par."
115,"Khalaf bin Hisham ne bayan kiya (kahaa) humein Hammad bin Zaid ne Abu Jamra se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Maine Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, neez Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : (Alfaaz unhi ke hain) Humein Ibaad bin Ibad ne Abu Jamra se khabar di ke Hazrat Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Abdul-Qais ka wafd aaya. Wo (log) kehney lagey : Aey Allah ke rasool! ham log (yaani) bano Rabee ka ye qabila hai. Humaarey aur aapke darmiyan (qabeela) Muzir ke kaafir haail hain aur ham hurmat waley mahiney ke siwa bahifaazat aap tak nahi pahunch saktey, lihaza aap humein wo hukm dijiye jispar khud bhi amal karein aur jo peechhey hain unko bhi uski dawat dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hun : (jinka hukm deta hun wo hain :), Allah Taala par eman laanaa, phir aapne unke samney eman billah ki wazaahat ki, farmaya is haqiqat ki gawahi dena ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi aur Muhammad bil-yaqeen Allah ke rasool hain. Namaz qaaim karnaa, zakat ada karna aur jo maale ghaneemat tumhen hasil ho, usmein se khumus (paanchwaan hissa) ada karna aur main tumhen roktaa hon kaddu ke bartan, sabz ghadey, lakdi ke andar se khodkar (banaaey huey) bartan aur aisey bartanon ke istemal se jinpar taarkol malaa gaya ho. Khalaf ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya : Is (sachchaaii) ki gawahi dena ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi. Isey unhon-ne ungli ke ishaarey se aik shumaar kiya."
116,"Shoba ne Abu Jamra se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Main Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur (doosrey) logon ke darmiyan tarjumaan tha, unke paas aik aurat aaii, wo unse ghadey ki nabeez ke barey mein sawal kar rahi thi to Hazrat Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Abdul-Qais ka wafd aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : Ye kon sa wafd hai? (ya farmaya : ye kon log hain?), unhon-ne kaha : Rabee (qabeela se hain). farmaya is qaum (ya wafd) ko khush aamadeed jo ruswa huey na naadim. (Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha, un logon ne kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! ham log aapke paas bahut door se aatey hain, hamarey aur aapke darmiyan Muzir ke kaafiron ka ye qabila (haail) hai, ham (kisi) hurmat waley mahiney ke siwa aapke paas nahi aa saktey, aap humein faisla-kun baat bataiye jo ham apne (gharon mein) peechhey logon ko (bhi) bataein aur uske zariey se ham jannat mein dakhil ho jaaein. Ibne Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya : Aapne in char baton ka hukm diya aur char chizon se rokaa. Aapne unko akeley Allah Taala par eman laney ka hukm diya aur puchha : Jaantey ho, sirf Allah par eman lana kya hai? Unhon-ne kaha : Allah aur uske rasool hi zyada jaanney waley hain. Aapne farmaya is haqiqat ki gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi Ilaah nahi aur Muhammad Allah ke rasool hain, Namaz qaaim karnaa, zakat denaa, Ramazan ke rozey rakhna aur ye ke tum maale ghaneemat mein se iska panchwan hissey ada karo. Aur unhein khushk kaddu se banaey huey bartan, sabz matkey aur taarkol maley huey bartan (iste'maal karne) se mana kiya (Shoba ne kaha :) Abu Jamra ne shayad (نقیر) (lakdii mein khudaaii karke banaya hua bartan) kaha ya shayad (مقیر) (taarkol malaa hua bartan) kaha, aur aapne farmaya : Inko khub yad rakho aur apne peechhey (waalon ko) bata do. Abu Bakr bin abi Shaiba ki riwayat mein (من ورائکم) ke bajaey (من وراءکم) (unko bataao jo tumharey peechhey hain) ke alfaz hain aur unki riwayat mein (مقیر) ka zikr nahi (balke (نقیر) ka hai.)"
117,"Qurra bin Khalid ne Abu Jamra se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Shoba ki (saabiqa riwayat ki) tarah hadis bayan ki (uske alfaz hain :) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Main tumhen us nabeez se mana karta hun jo khushk kaddu ke bartan, lakdi se taraasheeda bartan, sabz matkey aur taarkol maley bartan mein taiyaar ki jaey (us mein zyada Khumair uthney ka khadsha hai jisse nabeez sharab mein badal jati hai.), Ibne Muaz ne apne walid ki riwayat mein izafa kiya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdul-Qais ki peshani par zakhm waley shakhs (Ashajj) se kaha : tum mein 2 khubiyan hain jinhein Allah pasand farmata hai : Aql aur tahammul."
118,"(Ismaaeel) Ibne Ulaih ne kaha : Humein Saeed bin abi Arooba ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Mujhey us shakhs ne bataya jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honewaale Abdul-Qais ke wafd se mila tha (Saeed ne kaha : Qatada ne Abu nazra ka naam liya tha ye wafd se miley they, aur tafseel Hazrat abu-Saeed se sunkar bayan ki) unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se ye riwayat ki ke Abdul-Qais ke kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! ham Rabee'a ke log hain, humaarey aur aapke darmiyan Muzar ke kaafir haail hain aur ham hurmatwaale mahinon ke ilawa aapkii khidmat mein nahi pahunch saktey, isliye aap humein wo hukm dijiye jo ham apne pichhlon ko bataein aur agar uspar amal kar lein to ham (sab) jannat mein dakhil ho jaaein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa : (Hukm deta hun ke) Allah Taala ki bandagii karo aur uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na thahraao, Namaz ki pabandi karo, zakat detey raho, Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur ghaneematon ka panchwan hissey ada karo aur char chizon se main tumhen roktaa hun : Khushk kaddu ke bartan se, sabz matkey se, aisey bartan se jisko raughane-zuft (taarkol) lagaya gaya ho aur (نقیر) (lakdii ke taraashey huey bartan) se. Un logon ne kaha : Aey Allah ke nabii! Aapko naqeer ke barey mein kya ilm hai? farmaya : Kyun nahin! (ye) tanaa hai, tum usey andar se khokhla kartey ho, usmein mili julii chhoti khajoorein daltey ho) phir usmein pani daltey ho, phir jab uska josh (khameer uthney ke baad ka jhaag) khatm ho jata hai to usey pi letey ho yahan tak ke tum mein se aik (ya unmein eik) apne chacha zaad ko talwaar ka nishana banata hai. abu-Saeed ne kaha : Logon mein aik aadmi tha jisko isi tarah aik zakhm laga tha, usne kaha : Main sharmo haya ki bina par usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se chipa raha tha, phir maine puchha : Aey Allah ke rasool! To ham kis cheez mein piyaa karein? Apne farmaya : Chamdey ki un mushkon mein piyo jinke munh (dhaagey waghaira se) baandh diye jatey hain. Ahle wafd boley : Aey Allah ke rasool! Humaarii zamin mein choohey bahut hain, wahan chamdey ke mishkeezey nahi bach paatey. Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : chahey unhein choohey kha jaaein, chahey unhein choohey kha jaaein, chahey unhein choohey kha jaaein. kaha : (Phir) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdul-Qais ke us shakhs se jiske chehrey par zakhm tha, farmaya : tumharey andar 2 aisi khubiyan hain jinhein Allah Taala pasand farmata hai : Aql aur tahammul."
119,"Ibn abi Adi ne Saeed ke hawale se Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey Abdul-Qais ke wafd se mulaqat karne waley aik se zayed afraad ne bataya aur unmein se Abu Nazra ka naam liya (Abu Nazra ne) Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Abdul-Qais ka wafd Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. . . . phir Ibne Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, albatta usmein ye alfaz hain : Tum usmein mili julii khajoorein, (aam) khajoorein aur pani daltey ho. (Aur ibne-abi Adi ne apni riwayat mein) ye alfaz zikr nahi kiye ke Saeed ne kaha, ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kuchh khajoorein daltey ho."
120,"Muhammad bin Bakkaar Basrii, Aasim bin Juraij, Muhammad bin Raafe, Abdur Razzaaq, ibne- Juraij, Abu Qaza'a, Abu nazra, Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafd Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne arz kiya : Aey Allah ke nabii! ham aappar qurbaan! kon se bartan mein peenaa halal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : lakdi ke bartan mein na piyaa karo. Logon ne kaha : Aey Allah k rasool! Lakdii ka khatlaa kya hota hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : lakdi ko andar se khodkar bartan banaaney ko khatlaa kehtey hain aur lakdi ke taunbey mein bhi na piyaa karo aur sabz ghadey mein bhi na piyaa karo magar chamdey ke bartan mein pi liya karo jiska munh dorii se baandh diya jata ho."
121,"Abu Bakr bin abi Shaiba, abu-Kuraib aur Ishaq bin Ibrahim sab ne Wakee se hadis sunai Abu Bakr ne kaha : Wakee ne humein Zakariya bin Ishaq se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Mujhey Yahya bin Abdullah bin Saifii ne Abu Mabad se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki (Abu Bakr ne kaha : kabhi-kabhi Wakee kaha) Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bheja aur farmaya : Tum ahle kitab ki aik qaum ke paas ja rahe ho, unhein uski gawahi deney ki dawat do ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun. Agar wo usmein (tumhaarii) itaat karein to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne unpar har din-raat mein panch namazein farz ki hain. Agar wo usey maan lein to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne unpar sadqa (zakaat) farz kiya hai jo unke maaldaar logon se liya jaeyga aur unke mohtajon ko wapas kiya jaeyga phir agar wo is baat ko qabool kar lein to unke behtreen maalon se ehtiraaz karna (zakaat mein sabse achchha maal wsool na karnaa) aur mazloom ki baddua se bachna kyonke us (badduaa) ke aur Allah ke darmiyan koi hijaab nahiin."
122,Bishr bin sarii aur Abu Aasim ne Zakariya bin Ishaq se khabar di ke Yahya bin Abdullah bin Saifii ne Abu Mabad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ki taraf bheja to farmaya : Tum kuchh logon ke paas pahuncho gey . . . . . 'aagey Wakee ki hadis ki tarah hai.
123,"Ismail bin Umayya ne Yahya bin Abdullah bin Saifii se, unhon-ne Abu Mabad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bheja to farmaya : Tum aik qaum ke paas jaogey (jo) ahle kitab hain. To sabse pehli baat jiski taraf tumhen unko dawat deeni hai, Allah Taala ki ibadat hai. Jab wo Allah ko pehchan lein to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne unke din aur raat mein unpar panch namazein farz ki hain. Jab wo uspar amal pairaa ho jayen to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne unpar zakat farz ki hai jo unke (maaldaaron ke) amwaal se lekar unke fuqaraa ko di jaeygi. Jab wo usko maan lein to unse (zakaat) lena aur unke zyada qeemtii amwaal se ehtiraaz karnaa."
124,"Ubaidullaah bin Abdullah bin Utba-bin- Masood ne Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wafat paai aur aapke baad Hazrat Abu Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa banaey gaey to Arbon mein se kaafir honewaale kaafir ho gaey (aur Abu Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne maaniey zakat se jang ka irada kiya) to Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Aap un logon se kaisey jang karengey jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma chukey hain : Mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon se ladai karun yahan tak ke wo (laa ilaaha illallaah) ka iqrar kar lein, to jo koi (laa ilaaha illallaah) ka qaail ho gaya, usne meri taraf se apni jaan aur apna maal mehfooz kar liya, siwaey-iske ke us (laa ilaaha illallaah) ka haq ho, aur uska hisab Allah Taala par hai? Ispar Abu Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : Allah ki qasam! Main un logon se jang karunga jo Namaz aur zakat mein farq karengey, kyonke zakat ke maal (mein Allaah) ka haq hai. Allah ki qasam! Agar ye log (oont ka ( paon baandhney ki aik rassii bhi rokein gey, jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya kartey they, to main iske rokney par bhi unse jang karunga. Ispar Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha : Allah ki qasam! Asl baat iske siwa aur kuchh nahi ke maine dekha Allah Taala ne Hazrat Abu Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina jang ke liye khol diya, to main jaan gaya ke haq yahi hai."
125,"Saeed bin Musayyib ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon se jang karun yahan tak ke wo (laa ilaaha illallaah) ke qaail ho jaaein, chunanche jo (laa Ilaaha illallaah) ka qaail ho gaya, usne meri taraf se apna maal aur apni jaan mehfooz kar li, siwaey-iske ke us (iqraar) ka haq ho, aur us shakhs ka hisab Allah ke sipurd hai."
126,"Abdur Rehman bin Yaqoob ne Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon se jang karun yahan tak ke wo (laa ilaaha illallaah) ki shahadat dein aur mujhpar aur jo (deen) main lekar aaya hun uspar eman ley aaein, chunanche jab wo aisa karlein to unhon-ne meri taraf se apni jaan wa maal ko mehfooz kar liya, siwaey-iske ke us (shahaadat) ka haq ho aur unka hisab Allah ke sipurd hai."
127,"Aamash ne Abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, neez Aamash hi ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, (Jaabir aur Abu Huraira rz) donon ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Mujhey logon se jang karne ka hukm mila hai. . . . . Saeed bin Musayyib ki hadis ki tarah jo unhon-ne Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai."
128,"Abu Zuber ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon se ladun yahan tak ke wo (laa ilaaha illallaah) ke qaail ho jaaein, jab wo (laa ilaaha illallaah) ke qaail ho jaeinge to unhon-ne meri taraf se apne khoon aur maal mehfooz kar liye, siwaey-iske ke us (kalimey ke) haq ka (taqaazaa) ho, aur unka hisab Allah ke sipurd hai. phir aapne (ye aayat) tilawat farmai : aap to bas nasihat karne waley hain, aap unpar zabardastii karne waley nahi hain."
129,"Abu Ghassaan Mismaii, Malik bin Abdul Waahid, Abdul-Malik bin Assabbaah, Shoba, Waaqid bin-Muhammad Zaid-bin Abdullah, Ibne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey logon se us waqt tak ladney ka hukm hai jab tak wo la Ilaah illallaah Muhammad Rasulullah ki gawahi na deney lag jayen aur Namaz qaaim na kar lein aur zakat ada na karna shuru karlein, agar wo aisa karengey to unhon-ne mujhse apni jaan wa maal bacha liya magar haq par unka jaan aur maal ta'rruz nahi kya jaeyga unke dil ka mamla Allah Taala ke zimmey hai."
130,"Marwaan fazari ne abu-Malik (Saad bin Tariq Ashjaii) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne apne walid (Taariq bin Ashyam) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Jisne (laa ilaaha illallaah) kaha aur Allah ke siwa jinki bandagii ki jati hai, un (sab) ka inkar kiya to uska maal wa jaan mehfooz ho gaya aur uska hisab Allah par hai."
131,"Abu Khalid Ahmar aur Yazeed bin Harun ne Abu Malik se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Jisne Allah ko Yakta qarar diya. . . . . . Phir uper zikr ki gaee hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
132,"Yunus ne ibne Shihaab se, unhon-ne Saeed bin Musayyib se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke jab abu-Taalib ki maut ka waqt aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif laey. Aapne unke paas Abu Jahl aur Abdullah bin Abii Umayya bin Mughira ko maujood paayaa, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Chachaa! aik kalima (laa ilaaha illallaah) keh dein, main Allah ke yahan aapke haq mein iska gawah bin jaaunga. Abu Jahl aur Abdullah bin Umayya ne kaha : Abu Taalib! Aap Abdul Muttalib ke Deen ko chhod dengey? Rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalsal unko yahi peshkash kartey rahe aur yahi baat dohraatey rahe yahan tak ke abu-Taalib ne un logon se aakhiri baat kartey huey kaha : Wo Abdul Muttalib ki millat par (qaaim) hain, aur (laa ilaaha illallaah) kehney se inkar kar diya. Tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! Main aapke liye Allah Taala se maghfirat ki dua karta rahunga jab tak ke mujhey aap (ke hawaale) se rok na diya jaey. Ispar Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai : Nabi aur eman laney walon ke liye jaaiz nahi ke mushrikeen ke liye maghfirat ki dua karein, chahe wo unke rishtedar hi kyon na hon jabke unke samney waazeh ho chuka ke wo (mushrekeen) jahannami hain. Allah Taala ne Abu Taalib ke barey mein ye aayat bhi nazil farmai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mukhaatab karke farmaya : (Aey nabii!) Beshak aap jisey chaahein hidayat nahi de saktey lekin Allah jisko chahey hidayat de deta hai aur wo seedhi raah paaney walon ke barey mein zyada aagah hai."
133,"Mamar aur Saaleh, donon ne Zohri se unki pichhli sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki, farq ye hai ke Saleh ki riwayat : (فأنزل الله فيه), iske barey mein Allah Taala ne aayat utaarii, par khatm ho gaee, unhon-ne 2 aayatein bayan nahi kin. Unhon-ne apni hadis mein ye bhi kaha ke wo donon (Abu Jahl aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya) yahi baat dohraatey rahe. Mamar ki riwayat mein (المقالة) baat ke bajaey (الكلمة) kalima hai, wo donon unke sath lagey rahe."
134,"Marwaan bin Yazeed se, jo Kaisaan ke betey hain, hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne chacha ki maut ke waqt unse kaha : (laa ilaaha illallaah) keh dein, main qiyamat ke din aapke liye iske barey mein gawahi doonga. Lekin unhon-ne inkar kar diya. kaha : Ispar Allah Taala ne ye aayat utaarii, (إِنَّكَ لَا تَهْدِي مَنْ أَحْبَبْتَ) Beshak aap jisey chaahein raahe raast par nahi la saktey. . . aayat ke aakhir tak."
135,"Yahyaa bin Saeed ne kaha : HUmein Yazeed bin Kaisaan ne hadis sunai. . . . (iske baad mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke saath) Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne chacha se farmaya : (laa ilaaha illallaah) keh dijiye, main qiyamat ke din aapke liye iske barey mein gawah bin jaaunga. Unhon-ne (jawaab mein) kaha : Agar mujhey ye dar na hota ke Quraish mujhey aar dilaaeingey (kahengey ke usey (maut ki) ghabraahat ne is baat par aamada kiya hai) to main ye kalima padh kar tumhari aankhen thandii kar detaa. Ispar Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai : Aap jisey chahtey hon usey raahe raast par nahi la saktey lekin Allah Taala jisey chahey raahe raast par ley aata hai."
136,"Ismail bin Ibrahim (Ibne Ulaih) ne Khalid (حذاء) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Mujhey Waleed bin Muslim ne Humran se, unhon-ne Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jo shakhs mar gaya aur wo (yaqeen ke saath) janta tha ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga."
137,"Ibne Ulaih ke bajaey bishr bin Mufazzal ne bhi Khalid Hazza se yahi riwayat bayan ki, unhon-ne Waleed Abu bishr se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Maine Humran se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Maine Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna. . . . . iske baad bilkul pichhli riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
138,"Tal'ha bin Musrif ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik safar main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, logon ke zaade raah khatm ho gaey yahan tak ke Aapne logon ki kuchh sawaariyaan (oonton) ko zabh karne ka irada farma liya ispar umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : Allah ke rasool! Logon ka jo zaade raah bach gaya hai agar aap usey jama farma lein aur Allah Taala se uspar barkat ki dua farmaein (to behtar hoga), kaha : Aapne aisa hi kiya. Gandam wala apni gandam laya aur khajoor wala apni khajoor laya. Talha bin Musrif ne kaha : Mujahid ne kaha : Jiske paas guthliyaan thin, wo guthliyaan hi ley aaya. Maine (Mujaahid se) puchha : Guthliyon ka log kya kartey they? kaha : Unko chooskar pani pi letey they. Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is (thodey se zaade raah) par Aapne dua farmai to phir yahan tak hua ke logon ne zaade raah ke apne liye bartan bhar liye (Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) us waqt Aapne farmaya : Main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun. Jo banda bhi in donon (shaadaton) ke saath, unmein shak kiye baghair Allah se milega, wo (zaroor) jannat mein dakhil hoga."
139,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne (Aamash ko shak hai) Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ghazwa-e-Tabook ke din (safar mein) logon ko (zaade raah khatm ho janey ki bina par) faaqey laahiq ho gaey. Unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! Agar aap humein ijazat dein to ham pani dhoney waley oont zabh karlein, (unka gosht) khaaein aur (unki charbii) tel banaaein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisa karlo. (Kahaa : ( Itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! Agar aapne aisa kiya to sawaariyaan kam ho jaaeingii, iske bajaey aap sab logon ko unke bachchey huey zaade raah samet bulwa liijiye, phir uspar unke liye Allah se barkat ki dua keejiye, ummeed hai Allah Taala usmein barkat daal dega. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Theek hai. (hazrat Abu Huraira rz ya Abu Saeed rz ne kaha : ( Aapne chamdey ka aik dasterkhaan mangwaakar bichhaa diya, phir logon ka bacha hua zaade raah mangwaya (Hazrat Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ya abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( koi muththii bhar makaii, koi muththii bhar khajoor aur koi roti ka tukda laney laga yahan tak ke un chizon se dastarkhaan par thodi si miqdar jama ho gaee (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ya Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uspar barkat ki dua farmai, phir logon se farmaya : Apney apney bartanon main ( daal kar) ley jao . Sabne apney apney bartan bhar liye yahan tak ke unhon-ne lashkar ke bartanon mein koi bartan bharey baghair na chhoda (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( Iske baad sabne milkar (is dasterkhaan se) sair hokar khaya lekin khana phir bhi bacha diya. Ispar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( logon ko mukhaatab kartey huey) farmaya : Main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun, jo banda in donon mein shak kiye baghair Allah se milega usey jannat (mein dakhil honey) se nahi rokaa jaaeyga."
140,"( Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ( ibne- Jaabir ne kaha : mujhey Umer bin Hani ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Junaada bin abi Umayya ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : HUmein Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jis shakhs ne kaha : Main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, wo Yakta hai (uska koi Sharik nahi. (aur yaqinan Muhammad uske bandey aur rasool hain. aur Eisaa  Allah ke bandey, uski bandi ke betey aur uska kalima hain jisey usne Maryam ki taraf bheja tha, aur uski taraf se ( ata ki gai) Rooh hain, aur ye ke jannat haq hai aur dozakh haq hai, us shakhs ko Allah Taala jannat ke aath (8) darwazon mein se jisse chaaheyga , jannat mein dakhil kar dega."
141,"Umer bin Hani se ( Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ( ibne- Jaabir ke bajaey Auzai ke waastey se yahi hadis bayan ki gaee hai, albatta unhon-ne is tarah kaha : Allah Taala usey jannat mein dakhil karega, uske amal jaisey bhi hun. 'Aur usey jannat ke aath (8) darwazon mein se jisse chaaheyga ( dakhil kar dega )' ka zikr nahi kiya."
142,"Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se Junaada bin abi Umayya ke bajaey ( Abu Abdullah Abdur-Rehman bin Usaila ( Sunabihi ne riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Main Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut ke waqt unke paas hazir hua. Main roney laga to unhon-ne farmaya : Thehro ! Rotey kyon ho? Allah ki qism ! Agar mujh se gawahi mangi gaee to main zaroor tumharey haq mein gawahi doonga aur agar mujhey sifarish ka mauqa diya gaya to main zaroor tumhari sifarish karunga aur agar mere bas mein hua to main zaroor tumhen nafa pahunchaaunga , phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! koi aisi hadis nahi jo maine rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni , aur is mein tumhari bhalai ki koi baat thi aur wo maine tumhen na suna di ho, siwaey aik hadis ke. Aaj jab meri jaan qabz ki janey lagi hai to wo hadis bhi tumhen sunaaiye deta hun. Maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : Jis shakhs ne us haqiqat ki gawahi di ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad Allah ke rasool hain, Allah Taala ne uspar jahannam ki aag haram kar di."
143,"Anas-bin-Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis riwayat ki, kaha : Main ( sawari ke aik janwar par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey sawar tha, mere aur aapke darmiyan kajaawey ke pichhley hissey ki lakdi ( jitni jagah (ke siwa kuchh na tha, chunanche (is mauqe par) Aapne farmaya : Aey Muaz-bin-Jabal ! , Maine kaha : Main hazir hun Allah ke rasool! zahey naseeb . (iske baad) aap phir ghadi bhar chaltey rahe, iske baad farmaya : Aey Muaz-bin-Jabal ! , maine kaha : Main hazir hun, Allah ke rasool! zahey naseeb . Aap ne farmaya : Kya jantey ho ke bandon par Allah azz-wa-jall ka kya haq hai? kaha : Maine kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada aagah hain. irshad farmaya : Bandon par Allah azz-wa-jall ka haq ye hai ke uski bandagii karein aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na karein. Phir kuchh der chalney ke baad farmaya : Aey Muaz-bin-Jabal ! maine kaha : Main hazir hun Allah ke rasool! Zahey naseeb . Aap ne farmaya : Kya tum jantey ho ke jab bandey Allah ka haq ada karein to phir Allah par unka haq kya hai? Maine arz kiya, Allah aur Uska rasool hi zyada jaanney waley hain. Aap ne farmaya : Ye ke wo unhein azab na de."
144,"Amr-bin-Maimoon ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik gadhey par Sawar tha jisey Ufair kaha jata tha. Aapne farmaya : Aey Muaz ! jantey ho, bandon par Allah ka kya haq hai aur Allah par bandon ka kya haq hai? Maine kaha : Allah aur uske rasool zyada jaanney waley hain. Aapne farmaya : Bandon par Allah ka haq ye hai ke wo uski bandagii karein, uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thehraein aur Allah par bandon ka haq ye hai ke jo banda uske sath ( kisi cheez ko) Sharik na thahraaey , Allah usko azab na de. kaha : Maine kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! Kya main logon ko khushkhabri na sunaun? Aap ne farmaya : Unko khushkhabri na sunao warna wo usiipar bharosa kar lengey."
145,"Shoba ne Abu-Husain aur Ashas bin Sulaim se hadis sunai, un donon ne Aswad bin Hilal se suna, wo Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis bayan kartey they ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aey Muaz ! Kya tum jantey ho bandon par Allah ka kya haq hai? Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : Allah aur uska rasool hi behtar jantey hain. Aap ne farmaya : ye ke Allah ki bandagii ki jaey aur uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na thehraya jaey. Aap ne puchha : Kya jantey ho agar wo ( bandey ( aisa karein to Allah par unka kya haq hai? Maine jawab diya : Allah aur uska rasool behtar jantey hain. Aapne farmaya : ye ke wo unhein azab na de."
146,"Zaaida (bin Qudama ( ne Abu Husain se, unhon-ne Aswad bin Hilal se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Maine Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye bayan kartey huey suna ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bulaya , maine aapko jawab diya to aap ne puchha : Kya jantey ho logon par Allah ka haq kya hai? . . . . . phir un (pichhli rawiyon ( ki hadis ki tarah (hadees sunai. ("
147,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charon taraf aik jamat (ki sura ( mein baithey huey they. Humaarey sath Hazrat Abu-Bakr aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) humaarey darmiyan se uthey (aur kisi taraf chaley gaey ( , phir aap ne hamari taraf ( waapsii mein) bahut taakheer kar di to ham dar gaey ke kahin hamarey baghair aapko koi guzand na pahunchai jaey. Ispar ham bahut ghabraaey aur (aapki talash mein nikal ( khadey huey. Sabse pahley main hi ghabraayaa aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dhoondne nikla yahan tak ke main Ansar ke khandan Banu-Najjaar ke char diwari ( faseel ( se ghirey huey aik baagh tak pahuncha aur maine uske ird-gird chakkar lagaya ke kahin par darwaza mil jaey lekin mujhey na mila. achcha pani ki aik guzargaah dikhai di jo bahar ke kuwein se baagh ke andar jati thi ( Rabe aab pashi ki chhoti si neher ko kehtey hain) main laumdii ki tarah simat kar dakhil hua aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunch gaya. Aap ne puchha : Abu-Hurera ho? maine kaha : ji haan , aey Allah ke rasool! Aap ne farmaya : tumhen kya maamla darpesh hai? Maine kaha : Aap hamarey darmiyan tashrif farma they, phir wahan se uth gaey, phir aap ne hamari taraf ( wapas ( aaney mein der kar di to humein khatrah laahiq hua ke aap ham se kaat na diye jaaein. Ispar ham ghabraa gaey, sabse pahley main ghabraakar nikla to us baagh tak pahuncha aur is tarah simatkar (andar ghus ( aaya hun jis tarah laumdii simat kar ghustii hai aur ye doosrey log mere peechhey ( aa rahe ( hain. Tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aey Abu-Hurera ! Aur mujhey apne jootey ata kiye aur irshad farmaya : Mere ye jootey ley jao aur us char diwari ki dusri taraf tumhen jo bhi aisa aadmi miley jo dil ke poorey yaqin ke sath ( la ilaaha illallaah ( ki shahadat deta ho, usey jannat ki khushkhabri suna do. Sabse pahley meri mulaqat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se hui, unhon-ne ne kaha : Abu-Hurera ! ( tumharey hath mein) ye jootey kaisey hain? Maine kaha : Ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jootey hain. Aap ne mujhey ye jootey dekar bheja hai ke jis kisi ko miloon jo dil ke yaqin ke sath ( la ilaaha illallaah ( ki shahadat deta ho, usey jannat ki basharat de dun. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mere seeney par apne hath se aik zarb lagai jisse main apni suriinon ke bal gir padaa aur unhon-ne kaha : Aey Abu-Hurera ! Peechhey lauto . Main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas us aalim mein wapas aaya ke mujhey ronaa aa raha tha aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) mere peechhey lag kar chaltey aaey to achcha mere aqab se namudaar ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (mujh se) kaha : Aey Abu-Huraira ! tumhen kya hua? Maine kaha : Main umr se mila aur aap ne mujhey jo paigham dekar bheja tha, maine unhein bataya to unhon-ne mere seeney par aik zarb lagai hai jisse main apni suriinon ke bal gir padaa , aur mujh se kaha ke peechhey lauto . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : umr ! Tumne jo kiya uski wajah kya hai? Unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! Aap par mere maan-baap qurbaan hon ! Kya aap ne Abu-Hurera ko isliye jootey dekar bheja tha ke dil ke yaqin ke sath ( la ilaaha illallaah ( ki shahadat dene waley jis kisi ko miley, usey jannat ki basharat de ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Haan. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : To aisa na kijiye , mujhey dar hai ke log bas isi ( shahadat ( par bharosa kar baitheingey , unhein chhod dein ke wo amal kartey rahen , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Achchha to unko chhod do."
148,"Qatada ne kaha : Humein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se, jab wo paalaan par aap ke peechhey sawar they, farmaya : Aey Muaz ! Unhon-ne kaha : Main baar-baar hazir hun Allah ke rasool! Mere naseeb roshan ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : Aey Muaz ! Unhon-ne kaha : Main baar-baar hazir hun Allah ke rasool! zahey naseeb . Phir aap ne farmaya : Aey Muaz ! Unhon-ne arz kiya, main har baar hazir hun Allah ke rasool! meri khushbakhtii .(Ispar) Aap ne farmaya : koi banda aisa nahi jo ( sachey dil se) shahadat de ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad uske bandey aur rasool hain magar Allah aisey shakhs ko dozakh par haram kar deta hai.'Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! Kya main logon ko uski khabar na kar dun taake wo sab khush ho jayen ? Aap ne farmaya : Phir wo isi par bharosa karke baith jaengey. chunanche Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( katmaane ilm ke) gunah ke khof se apni maut ke waqt ye baat bataaii."
149,"Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne kaha : Humein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Mujhey Mehmood-bin Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Itbaan bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai. ( Mehmood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha ke main Madina aaya to Itbaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko mila aur maine kaha : aik hadis mujhey aap ke hawale se pahunchi hai. Hazrat Itbaan ne kaha : meri aankhon ko koi bimari laahiq ho gaee to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein paigham bheja ke aey Allah ke rasool! mera dil chahta hai ke aap mere paas tashrif laaein aur mere ghar mein Namaz ada farmaein taake main usi ( jagah ( ko Namaz padhney ki jagah bana loon. Unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sathiyon mein se jinko Allah ne chaha , tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere ghar mein dakhil huey, aap Namaz padh rahe they aur aap ke sathi aapas mein baatein kar rahe they. Unhon-ne zyada aur badi badii baatein Malik bin Dukhshum ke sath jod dein, wo chahtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske haq mein bad dua farmaein aur wo halaak ho jaey aur unki khahish thi ke is par koi aafat aaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey aur puchha : Kya wo is baat ki gawahi nahi deta ke Allah Taala ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hoon? sahaba kiram ne jawab diya : Wo ( zaban se) ye kehta hai lekin uske dil mein ye nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aisa shakhs nahi jo gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun to phir wo aag mein dakhil ho ya aag usey apni khuraak bana ley. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Ye hadis mujhey bahut achi lagi ( pasand aai ( to maine apne betey se kaha : Isey likh lo, Usne ye hadis likh li."
150,"Hammad ne kaha : Humein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Mujhey Itbaan bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke wo naabeenaa ho gaey they, us wajah se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf paigham bheja ke aap tashrif laaein aur mere liye masjid ki aik jagah mutayyan kar dein (taake main usmein Namaz padh sakun ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur un ( Itbaan (Raziallahu anhu)) ki qaum ke log bhi aa gaey, unmein se aik aadmi , jisey Malik bin dukhshum kaha jata tha, ghayab raha. . . . uske baad Hammad ne bhi) Sabit ke doosrey shagird ( Sulaiman-bin Mughira ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
151,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they is shakhs ne eman ka maza chakh liya jo Allah ke rab, Islam ko Deen aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rasool honey par (dil se) razi ho gayaa."
152,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se, unhon Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke nabii (sl) ne farmaya : eman ki 70 se zyada shakhein hain aur haya bhi eman ki aik shaakh hai."
153,"Suhail ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : eman ke 70 se uper (ya sath se uper ( shobe ( ajzaa ( hain. sabse afzal Juz ( la ilaaha illallaah (ka iqrar hai aur sabse chhota kisi azeeyat ( dene wali cheez ( ko rastey se hataanaa hai aur haya bhi eman ki shakhon mein se aik hai."
154,"Sufiyaan-bin-Uyaina ne Zohri se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi se suna jo apne bhai ko haya ke barey mein nasihat kar raha tha to aap ne farmaya : ( haya se mat roko ( haya eman mein se hai."
155,Sufiyaan-bin-Uyaina ke bajaey Mamar ne Zohri se mazkura (uper zikr) bil-isnaad ke sath khabar di aur kaha ke aap aik Ansari ke paas se guzrey jo apne bhai ko nasihat kar raha tha.
156,"Abu sawar bayan kartey hain ke unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haya se khair aur bhalai hi hasil hoti hai. Ispar Bashir-bin-kab ne kaha : Hikmat aur) daanaaii ki kitaabon ( mein likha hua ke us ( haya ( se waqaar  milta hai aur sukoon hasil hota hai. is par Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis suna raha hun aur to mujhey apne saheefon ki baatein sunata hai !"
157,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ishaq bin Suwaid se riwayat ki ke Abu Qatada ( Tameem bin Nazeer ( ne hadis bayan ki, kaha ke ham apne sathiyon samet Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir they, ham mein Bashir-bin-kab bhi maujood they, us roz Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne humein aik hadis sunai, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haya bhalai hai poori ki poori . (Unhon-ne kaha : Ye alfaz farmaai ( : haya poori ki poori bhalai hai. To Bashir-bin-kab ne kaha : Humein kitaabon ya hikmat (ke majmooaon ( mein ye baat miltii hai ke haya se itminan aur Allah ke liye waqaar (ka izhar ( hota hai aur uski aik qism zaeefii ( kamzori ( hai. Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) sakht ghussey mein aagey yahan tak ke unki aankhen surkh ho gain aur farmaney lagey : Kya main dekh nahi raha ke main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis suna raha hun aur tum usmein muqaabla kar rahe ho? abu-Qatada ne kaha : Imran ne dobara hadis sunai aur Bashir ne phir wahi kaha : is par Imran ( sakht ( ghussey mein aa gaey. ( Abu Qatada ne) kaha : To humne baar-baar ye kehnaa shuru kar diya : Aey Abu Nujaid ! (Hazrat Imran ki kunniyat ( ye ham mein se ( musalman aur hadis ka taalibe ilm ( hai. us (ke aqeedey ( mein koi aib ya naqs nahi hai."
158,"Nazr (bin Shumeil ( ne kaha : Humein Abu na'aama Adawii ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Maine Hujair bin Rabe Adawii se suna, wo kehtey they : Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. (jis tarah) Hammad-bin-Zaid ki hadis hai."
159,"Abdullah-bin Numair, Jarir aur abu-Usama ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis sunai, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sufiyan bin-Abdullah Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : Aey Allah ke rasool! Mujhey Islam ke barey mein aisi pakkii baat bataiye ke aap ke baad kisi se iske barey mein sawal karne ki zarurat na rahe ( abu-Usama ki riwayat mein, , aap ke ba'd, , ke bajaey , aap ke siwa , ke alfaz hain) Aap ne irshad farmaya : Kaho : (آمنت باللہ) ( Main Allah par eman laya ( , phir is par pakey ho jao."
160,"Lais ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne abu-Khair se aur unhon Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : kon sa Islam behtar hai? Aap ne jawab diya : Tum logon ko khana khilaao aur har kisi ko , chahe tum usey jantey ho ya nahi jaantey, salam kaho."
161,"Amr-bin-Haris ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne Abu-Khair se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they : aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : Musalmaanon mein se behtar kon hai? Aap ne farmaya : Jiski zaban aur hath se doosrey musalman amn mein hon."
162,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna : musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur hath se doosrey musalman mehfooz rahen.
163,"Yahyaa-bin-Saeed Umwii ne kaha : Humein abu-Burda ( Buraid ( bin-Abdullah-bin abi Burda bin abi Musa Ash-ari ne abu-Burda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : kon sa Islam afzal hai? Aap ne farmaya : (Uska Islam ( Jiski zaban se aur hath se musalman mehfooz rahen."
164,"Ibrahim bin Saeed Jauharii , abu-Usama , Buraid bin-Abdullah ki is riwayat mein dusri sanad ke sath ye alfaz hain jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kon sa musalman afzal hai? To aap ne is tarah zikr farmaayaa."
165,"Abu Qilaaba ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap ne farmaya : Jis shakhs mein teen baatein paaein jaeyngi wo unke zariey se eman ki halaawat pa lega : Jisey Allah aur uska rasool baqi har kisi se badhkar mahboob hon, (doosri ( ye ke jis kisi se bhi mohabbat karey Allah hi ke liye karey aur) teesri ( ye ke Allah ne jab usey kufr se bacha liya hai to wo dobara kufr ki taraf palatney se is tarah nafrat karey jaisi is baat se nafrat karta hai ke usey aag mein daal diya jaaey."
166,"Qatada Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey hain, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Teen baatein jis mein bhi hongi wo eman ka zaayqa pa lega (1) Jo shakhs kisi insan se mohabbat karta hai aur Allah ke siwa kisi aur ki khaatir usse mohabbat nahi karta. (2) Jiske liye Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baqi har kisi se zyada piyarey hain (3) Aur jab Allah ne usey kufr se bacha liya hai to aag mein daala jana , usey kufr mein dobara lotney se zyada pasand hai."
167,"Saabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . . .) phir isi tarah bayan kiya ( jaisey pichhli rawiyon ne bayan kiya hai, albatta unhon-ne ye (alfaz ( kahey : Usko phir se Yahudi ya iisaaii ho janey se ( aag mein daala jana zyada pasand ho)."
168,"Ismail bin-Ulaih aur Abdul Waaris donon ne Abdul-Azeez se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi banda (aur Abdul Waaris ki hadis mein hai koi aadmii) us waqt tak momin nahi ho sakta jab tak main usey uske ahlo ayaal, maal aur sab logon se zyada mahboob na hoon."
169,"Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (us waqt tak) momin nahi ho sakta jab tak main uske liye uski aulaad, uske walid aur tamam insanon se badhkar mahboob na hoon."
170,"Shoba ne kaha : Maine Qatada ko Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs momin nahi ho sakta yahan tak ke wo apne bhai ke liye (ya farmaya : apne padosi ke liye bhi) wahi pasand karey jo wo apne liye pasand karta hai."
171,"Husain Muallim ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! koi banda us waqt tak momin nahi ho sakta jab tak apne padosi ke liye (ya farmaya : apne bhai ke liye) wahi pasand na karey jo wo apne liye pasand karta hai."
172,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jiski eiizaa rasaanii se uske padosi mehfooz na hon, wo jannat mein nahi jaaeyga."
173,"Abu Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai, wo khair ki baat kahey ya khamosh rahe aur jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai, wo apne padosi ka ehtiraam kare aur jo aadmi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai, wo apne mehman ki izzat kare."
174,"Abu-Husain ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jo shakhs Allah aur qiyamat par eman rakhta hai, wo apne padosi ko eiizaa na pahunchaaey , aur jo shakhs Allah aur qiyamat par eman rakhta hai, wo apne mehman ki takreem karey, aur jo shakhs Allah aur qiyamat par yaqin rakhta hai, wo achi baat karey ya khamosh rahe."
175,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . . . aagey Abu Husain ki riwayat ki tarah hai, albatta Aamash ne (wo apne padosi ko eiizaa na de ke bajaey) ye alfaz kahey hain : wo apne padosi ke sath achchha sulook kare."
176,"Abu Shuraih ( Khuwelid bin-Amr ( Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jo shakhs Allah aur yaume aakhirat par eman rakhta hai, wo apne padosi ke sath husne sulook karey, aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par yaqin rakhta hai, wo apne mehman ki takreem karey aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai, wo achi baat kahey ya khamoshi ikhtiyar kare."
177,"Abu-Bakr bin abi Shaiba ne kaha : Humein Wakee ne Sufiyan se hadis sunai, neez Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : Humein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne aur unhein Shoba ne hadis sunai, un donon ( Sufiyan aur Shoba ( ne Qais-bin Muslim se aur unhon-ne Tariq bin Shihaab se riwayat ki, alfaz Abu-Bakr bin abi Shaiba ke hain. Tariq bin Shihaab ne kaha ke pehlaa shakhs jisne eid ke din Namaz se pahley khutbey ka shuruat kiya, Marwan tha. aik aadmi uske samney khada ho gaya aur pucha : Namaz khutbey se pahley hai? Marwan ne jawab diya : Jo tariqa ( yahan pahley) tha, wo tark kar diya gaya hai. is par Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is insan ne ( jisne sahi baat kahi thi) apni zimmedaarii poori kar di hai. Maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : tum mein se jo shakhs munkar ( naqabile-qabool kaam ( dekhey is par lazim hai ke usey apne hath ( quwwat ( se badal de aur agar uski taqat na rakhta ho to apni zaban se usko badley aur agar uski bhi taqat na rakhta ho to apne dil se ( usey bura samjhey aur uske badalney ki musbat tadbeer sochey (aur ye sabse kamzor eman hai."
178,"Aamash ne Ismail bin -Rajaa se, unhon-ne apne walid ( -Rajaa bin Rabee ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudrii (Raziallahu anhu) se, neez Aamash ne Qais bin Muslim se, unhon-ne Taariq bin Shihaab se aur unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se Marwan ka uper zikr ki gaee waqia aur Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis jo unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni , isi tarah bayan ki jis tarah Shoba aur Sufiyan ne bayan ki."
179,"Saleh bin Kaisaan ne Haris (bin Fuzel ( se, unhon-ne Jafar bin-Abdullah-bin Hakam se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Miswar se, unhon-ne ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam ( Abu Raafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ne mujhse pahley kisi ummat mein jitney bhi Nabi bhejey, unki ummat mein se unke kuchh hawaarii aur sathi hotey they jo unki sunnat par chaltey aur unke hukm ki ittaba (pairvi) kartey they, phir aisa hota tha ke unke baad naalaaiq log unke jaanasheen bin jatey they. Wo ( zaban se) aisi baatein kehtey jinpar khud amal nahi kartey they aur aisey kaam kartey they jinka unko hukm na diya gaya tha, chunanche jisne un ( jaisey logon (ke khilaf apne dasto bazu se jihad kiya, wo momin hai aur jisne unke khilaf apni zaban se jihad kiya, wo momin hai aur jisne apne dil se unke khilaf jihad kiya wo bhi momin hai) lekin) isse peechhey raai ke daney barabar bhi eman nahi. Abu Raafe ne kaha : Maine ye hadis Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko sunai to wo usko na maaney. ittifaq se Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bhi (Madina ( aagey aur wadi Qanaat (Madina ki wadi hai) mein thahrey . Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bhi unki iyaadat ke liye apne sath chalney ko kaha, main unke sath chala gaya ham jab jaakar baith gaey to maine Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se us hadis ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne mujhey ye hadis isi tarah sunai jis tarah maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko sunai thi. Saleh bin Kaisaan ne kaha : Ye hadis Abu Raafe se ( baraahe raast bhi) isi tarah riwayat ki gaee hai."
180,"Haris bin Fuzel Khatmii se ( Saleh bin Kaisaan ke bajaey) Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ki sanad ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Maula Abu Raafe se riwayat hai, Unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jo bhi Nabi guzra hai uske sath kuchh hawaarii they jo us (Nabi (ke namoona-e-zindagii ko apnaatey aur uski sunnat ki pairwi kartey they. . . . Saleh ki riwayat ki tarah. lekin) Abdul-Azeez ne) Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki aamad aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unki mulaqat ka zikr nahi kiya."
181,"Hazrat Abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath se Yaman ki taraf ishara kiya aur farmaya : Dekho! eman udhar hai aur shaqaawat aur sangdillii oonton ki dumon ki jadon ke paas cheekhney walon Rabee aur muzar mein hai, jiski taraf se shaitan ke do seeng namudaar hotey hain."
182,"Ayub ne kaha : Humein Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ahle Yaman aaey hain. Ye log bahut zyada narm dil hain. eman yamnii hai, fiq'h yamnii hai aur daanaaii ( bhi) yamnii hai."
183,"( Abdullah ( Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . usi pichhli ( hadis) ke maanind."
184,"Saleh ne Aaraj se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey paas yamnii log aaey hain, wo zyada kamzor dil aur seenon mein zyada riqqat rakhney waley hain. Fiq'h yamnii hai aur hikmat ( bhi) yamnii hai."
185,Abu zinaad ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Kufr ki riyaasat mashriq ki taraf hai. Fakhr wa takabbur ghodon aur oonton walon mein hai (jo unchi awaz mein chillaaney waley aur oon ke khemon mein rehney waley hain) aur itminan wa sukoon bakriyan paalne walon mein hai.
186,"Alaa (bin Abdur-Rehman Al-Juhnii ( ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : eman Yaman se hai, kufr mashriq ki taraf hai, sukoon wa itminan bhed bakriyan paalne walon main aur fakhro- dikhawey shor sharaabey ke aadi ghodey paalne walon aur ooni khemon ke baasii , chalaney walon mein hai"
187,"Yunus ne ibne-Shihaab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : fakhr wa takabbur chillaakar bolney waale, khemon ke baasiyon mein hai aur itminan wa sukoon bhedh bakri walon mein hai."
188,Shuaib ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat ki aur) aakhir mein ye ( izafa kya : eman yamnii hai aur hikmat bhi yamnii hai.
189,"Saeed-bin-Musayyib ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ahle Yaman aaey hain, unke dil ( dusron se) zyada narm hain aur mizaajon mein zyada riqqat hai. eman yamnii hai aur hikmat bhi yamnii hai. sukoon, bhedh bakriyan paalne walon mein hai aur fakhr wa takabbur ooni khemon ke baasii , cheekhney chillaaney waley logon mein, jo suraj tuloo' honey ki samt main ( rahtey hain. )."
190,"Abu Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey paas ahle Yaman aaey hain. wo dilon ke zyada narm aur mizaajon mein zyada riqqat rakhney waley hain. eman yamnii hai, hikmat bhi Yaman se hai aur kufr ka markaz mashriq ki taraf hai."
191,"Jarir ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, lekin us ne, , kufr ka markaz mashriq ki taraf hai, ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
192,"Shoba ne Aamash se pichhli sanad ke sath Jarir ki tarah hadis sunai aur ye alfaz zayed bayan kiye ke , ghurur aur ghamand oont walon main aur sukoon wa waqaar bhedh bakri ( paalne ( walon mein hai."
193,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dilon ki sakhti aur jafaa ( akkhadpan ( mashriq mein hai aur eman ahle hijaaz mein hai.
194,"Abu Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum jannat mein dakhil nahi hogey yahan tak ke tum momin ho jao, aur tum momin nahi ho saktey yahan tak ke aik doosrey se mohabbat karo. Kya tumhen aisi cheez na bataaun ke jab tum is par amal karo to aik doosrey ke sath mohabbat karne lago, aapas mein salam aam karo."
195,"(Abu Muawiya aur Wakee ke bajaey) Jarir ne Aamash se unki isi sanad se hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! tum jab tak eman nahi lao gey, jannat mein dakhil nahi ho sakogey . . . jis tarah abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ki hadis hai.`"
196,"Sufiyaan-bin-Uyaina ne kaha : maine Suhel se kaha ke Amr ne hamein Qaaqaa ke waastey se aap ke walid se hadis sunai ( Sufiyan ne kaha : ( mujhey ummeed thi ke wo (mujhey khud riwayat suna kar) aik rawi kam kar dega (chunaanche Suhel ne kaha ( maine usi se ye riwayat suni jis se mere walid ne suni , wo Sham (Syria) mein unka dost tha. ( Muhammad-bin Ibad ne kaha ( phir Sufiyan ne humein Suhel ke waastey se Ata-bin-Yazeed ki Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat sunai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Deen khair khahi ka naam hai. ham ( sahaba (Raziallahu anhu)) ne puchha : kis ki) khair khaahii ? (aap ne farmaya : Allah ki, uski kitab ki, uske rasool ki, musalmaanon ke ameeron ki aur aam musalmaanon ki) khair khahi .) , '"
197,"Sufiyan Saury ne Suhel bin abi Saleh se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Laisii se, unhon-ne Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pichhli hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
198,"Humein Rauh bin-Qasim ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( humein Suhel ne Ata se us waqt sun kar riwayat ki jab wo Abu-Saleh ko hadis bayan kar rahe they, (kaha : ( Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, (kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai, usi (pichhli hadis) ke maanind."
199,"Qais (bin abi Hazim ( ne Hazrat Jarir ( bin-Abdullah ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz qaaim karne, zakat ada karne aur har musalman ke sath khair khahi karne par bait ki."
200,"Ziyad bin Ilaqa ( Koofii ( se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se har musalman ke sath khair khahi karne par bait ki."
201,"Suraij bin Yunus aur Yaqoob Dauraqii ne kaha : Hushaim ne humein Sayyar ke waastey se Shabi se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ehkaam ( sunney aur itaat karne par bait ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sath ye kahlwaayaa : jahan tak tumharey bas mein hoga. aur har musalman ke sath khair khahi par. Yaqoob ne apni riwayat mein kaha : humein Sayyar ne hadis sunai. ( Yaqoob ne baraahe raast Sayyar se bhi ye riwayat suni aur Hushaim ke waastey se bhi, lafz wahi they. ("
202,"Yunus ne ibne-Shihaab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Saeed-bin-Musayyib se suna, donon kehtey they ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zaanii zina nahi karta ke jab zina kar raha ho to wo momin ho, chor chori nahi karta ke jab chori kar raha ho to wo momin ho, shraabii sharab nahi peetaa ke jab sharab pi raha ho to wo momin ho. ibne-Shihaab ne bayan kiya ke Abdul-Malik bin abii-Bakr bin Abdur-Rehman ne mujhey khabar di ke) uske walid ( abu-Bakr unke samney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ye sab baatein riwayat kartey, phir kehtey : aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) unmein ye baat bhi shamil kartey they ke , kisi badi qadr wa qeemat wali cheez ko , jiski wjah se log lotney waley ki taraf nazar utha kar dekhtey hon, wo nahi laut'taa ke jab lot raha ho to wo momin ho."
203,"Uqail bin Khalid ne hadis sunai ke ibne-Shihaab (Zohri ( ne kaha : mujhey abu-Bakr bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zaanii zina nahi karta. . . . . phir guzishta hadis ki tarah bayan kiya jis mein loot ka zikr to hai, lekin, , qadr wa manzilat wali cheez , ke alfaz nahi. ibne-Shihaab (Zohri ( ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musayyib aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah hadis sunai jis tarah abu-Bakr ki riwayat hai lekin us mein, , loot , ka zikr nahi hai."
204,"Auzaaii ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne- musayyib , abu-Salma aur abu-Bakr bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki jis tarah Uqaill ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki aur us mein, , loot , ka tazkira kiya lekin, , qadr wa qeemat wali cheez , ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
205,"Safwaan bin Sulaim ne Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Ata-bin-Yasar se aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye riwayat bayan ki."
206,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Abdul-Azeez darawardi , Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki."
207,"Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, un sab ( Safwan , Alaa aur Mamar ( ki riwayat ( 205 . 207 (Imam Zohri ki riwayat ( 204 ( ki tarah hain, albatta Alaa aur Safwan ki bayan ki hui hadis riwayat ( 205 , 206 ( mein, , jiski taraf se log nazar uthatey hain, , ke alfaz maujood nahi. aur Hammam ki riwayat ke alfaz is tarah hain : momin log (is cheez ki qadr wa qeemat ki bina par) uski taraf se apni nazrein uthatey hain aur wo ( laut'tey waqt) momin nahi hota. aur Mamar ne ye izafa bhi kiya hai : aur tum mein se koi khiyaanat nahi karta ke jab khiyaanat kar raha ho to wo momin ho, lihaza tum (un tamam kaamon se) bacho."
208,"Shoba ne Sulaiman se, unhon-ne Zakwan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zaanii zina nahi karta ke jab zina kar raha hota hai to momin ho, chor chori nahi karta ke jab chori kar raha ho to wo momin ho, sharaabii sharab nahi peetaa ke jab wo pi raha ho to momin ho. aur) unko ( baad mein tauba ka mauqa diya jata hai."
209,"Sufiyan ne ( Sulaiman ( Aamash ke hawale se khabar di ke Zakwan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiya, farmaya : zaanii zina nahi karta ke jab wo zina kar raha ho. . . . . aagey ( Sufiyan ne) Shoba ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
210,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Sufiyan ne Aamash se, unhon-ney Abdullah-bin Murra se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : char aadatein hain jis mein wo ( charon ( hongi , wo khalis munafiq hoga aur jis kisi mein unmein se aik aadat hogi to usmein nifaq ki aik aadat hogi yahan tak ke us se baaz aa jaey. (wo char ye hain : ( jab baat karey to jhoot boley aur jab muaahida karey to tod daaley, jab wada karey to wada khilaafii karey aur jab jhagdaa karey to gali de.' albatta Sufiyan ki riwayat main ( خلة (ke bajaey ( خصلة ) ka lafz hai) mana wahi hain. ("
211,"Naafe bin Malik bin abi Aamir ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : munafiq ki teen alamatein hain : jab baat karey to jhoot boley, jab wada karey to ( uski ( khilaf warzi karey aur jab usey ( kisi cheez ka ( ameen banaya jaey to (us mein) khiyaanat kare."
212,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : humein Hirqa ke aazad karda ghulam Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ne apne walid se khabar di aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : munafiq ki teen alamatein hain : jab baat karey to jhoot boley, wada karey to khilaf warzi karey aur ameen banaya jaey to khiyaanat kare."
213,"Yahya bin Muhammad-bin Qais abu Zakeer ne kaha : maine Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman ko usi ( uper zikr ki gaee (sanad ke sath hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne kaha : munafiq ki alaamaat teen hain, chahey wo roza rakhey , Namaz padhey aur apne aapko musalman samjhey ."
214,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Dawud bin abi Hinda se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musayyib ke hawale se Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki jo Yahya bin-Muhammad ki Alaa se bayan ki hui riwayat ke mutabiq hai aur is mein bhi ye alfaz hain : chahe roza rakhey , Namaz padhey aur apne aapko musalman samjhey ."
215,Naafe ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs apne bhai ko kaafir qarar de to donon mein se aik ( zaroor ( kufr ke sath wapas lautey ga .
216,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne apne bhai se kaha : aey kaafir ! to donon mein se aik ( kufr ki) us ( nisbat (ke sath lautey ga . agar wo aisa hi hai jis tarah usne kaha (to theek ( warna ye baat usi ( kehney waale) par lot aaeygii ."
217,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : jis shakhs ne daanista apne walid ke bajaey kisi aur (ka betaa honey) ka dawa kya to usne kufr kiya aur jisne aisi cheez ka dawa kiya jo uski nahi hai, wo ham mein se nahi, wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley. aur jis shakhs ne kisi ko kaafir keh kar pukara ya Allah ka dushman kaha, halanke wo aisa nahi hai to ye ( ilzam ( usi ( kehney waale) ki taraf lot jaeyga,"
218,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne baap-dada se beraghbatii na karo, chunanche jis shakhs ne apne walid se inhiraaf kiya to ye (amal ( kufr hai."
219,"Khalid ne abu-Usmaan se naql kiya ke jab Ziyad ki nisbat ( Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf honey) ka dawa kiya gaya tha to main janab Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur puchha : ye tum logon ne kya kiya ? maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke mere donon kanon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jisne Islam ki haalat main apne haqiqi bap ke siwa kisi aur ko bap banaaney ka dawa kiya aur wo janta hai ke wo uska bap nahi to is par jannat haram hai. is par Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : khud maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi suna hai."
220,"Aasim ne abu-Usmaan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sad aur Hazrat abu-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai ke wo donon kehtey they : ye baat mere donon kanon ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni (aur merey dil ne yad rakhi ( ke  Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : jisne apne walid ke siwa kisi aur ko walid banaaney ka dawa kiya, halanke wo janta hai ke wo iska walid nahi hai, to is par jannat haram hai."
221,"Muhammad-bin Talha , Sufiyan aur Shoba teenon ne Zubeda se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman ko gali dena fisq hai aur us se ladna kufr hai. Zubeda ne kaha : maine abu-Waail se puchha : kya aap ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey huey khud suna hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan. Shoba ki riwayat mein Zubeda ke abu-Waail se poochhney ka zikr nahi hai."
222,"Mansoor aur Aamash donon ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki."
223,"Abu Zur'a (Haram bin-Amr bin Jarir bin Abdullah Bajalii ( ne apne dada Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa' ke mauqe par mujh se farmaya : logon ko chup karao . uske baad aap ne farmaya : mere baad kaafir na bin jana ke aik doosrey ki gardanein maarney lago ."
224,"Muaaz-bin-Muaaz ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Waqid bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne nabii (sl) se pichhli hadis ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
225,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne Waqid bin Muhammad-bin Zaid se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne apne walid se suna, wo Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey they, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hajjatul-wadaa' ke mauqe par farmaya : tum par afsos hota hai) ya farmaya : tumharey liye tabahi hogi) tum mere baad kaafir na ho jana ke aik doosrey ki gardanein maarney lago ."
226,Abdullah-bin Wahb ne kaha : humein Umar-bin Muhammad ne hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne unhein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah Shoba ne Waqid se bayan ki hai.
227,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logon mein 2 baatein hain, wo donon unmein kufr (ki Baqiiya aadatein ( hain : ( kisi ke) nasb par ta'an karna aur mayyat par nauha karnaa.'"
228,"Mansoor bin Abdur-Rehman ne Shabi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke main Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : jo ghulam apne maalikon se bhag gaya, us ne kufr ka irtikaab kiya yahan tak ke unki taraf lot aaey. , ( na ye ke dobara musalman ho. ( Mansoor ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye hadis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki gaee hai lekin main na-pasand karta hun ke yahan ( Basra mein) mujh se ye (is tarah marfooan ( riwayat ki jaey. (kyonke Basra ke Khaarijii us se matlab kufr ka istidlaal karengey. ("
229,"Daawood ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo ghulam bhagodaa ho gaya to us (ke tahaffuz ( se ( Islami muaashrey aur hukumat ki) zimme-dari khatm ho gaee."
230,"Mugheera ne Shabi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiya kartey they : jab ghulam bhag jaey to uski Namaz qabool nahi hoti . (jis tarah haram khaney waley ki Namaz qabool nahi hoti .)"
231,"Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhnii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hudaibiya ke maqam par raat ko honey wali barish ke ba'd, humein subah ki Namaz padhai. jab aap ne salam phera to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : kya tum jantey ho tumharey rab ne kya farmaayaa? , unhon-ne jawab diya Allah aur uska rasool behtar jantey hain. aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne farmaya : ( aaj ( mere bandon mein se koi mujh par eman laney wala aur (koii mere saath) kufr karne wala ho gaya. jisne ye kaha hai ke ham par Allah Taala ke fazl aur rehmat se barish hui hai to wo mujh par eman rakhney wala aur sitaarey ke sath kufr karne wala hai aur jisne kaha ke ham par falan-falan sitaarey (ke ghurub wa tuloo honey) ki wajah se barish hui hai to wo mere sath kufr karne wala aur sitaarey par eman rakhney wala hai."
232,Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhen malum nahi ke tumharey rab azz-wa-jall ne kya farmaayaa? Us ne farmaya : jo nemat bhi main bandon ko deta hun to unmein se aik giroh (se talluq rakhney waley log (us ( nemat (ke sabab se kufr karne waley ho jatey hain aur kehtey hain : falan sitaarey ( ne ye nemat di hai) ya falan-falan sitaron ke sabab se ( mili hai).
233,"Muhammad-bin Salma Muradi ne apni sanad se aur Amr bin sawwaad ne apni sanad se Amr-bin-Haris se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : humein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Yunus ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey hadis sunai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala aasman se barkat ( barish ( nazil nahi karta magar logon ka aik giroh , uske sabab se kaafir ho jata hai, barish Allah Taala utaartaa hai) lekin) ye log kehtey hain : falan-falan sitaarey ke baais ( utri hai.) , aur Muradi ki riwayat ke ye alfaz hain : falan-falan sitaarey ke baais ( utri hai.)"
234,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein logon ko barish se nawaza gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logon mein se kuchh shukr-guzar ho gaey hain aur kuchh kaafir ( naa-shukrey ( , ( kuchh ( logon ne kaha : ye Allah ki rehmat hai aur kuchh ne kaha : falan-falan nau (9) (eik sitaarey ka ghurub aur uske sabab se doosrey ki bulandi ( sachchii nikli . (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) farmatey hain, is par ye aayat nazil hui : main sitaron ke girney ki jaghon ki qism khata hun. (se lekar (us aayat tak : aur tum apna hissey ye rakhtey ho ke tum uski takzeeb kartey ho."
235,Anas ‌(rz) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya munafiq ki nishani ye hai ke Ansar se dushmanii rakhey aur momin ki nishani ye hai ke Ansar se mahabbat rakhey.
236,"Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : humein Shoba ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ansar se mohabbat karna eman ki nishani hai aur unse bughz rakhna nifaq ki alamat hai."
237,"Shoba ne Adii-bin Sabit se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke aap ne Ansar ke barey mein farmaya : unse mohabbat nahi karta magar wahi jo momin hai aur unse bughz nahi rakhta magar wahi jo munafiq hai. jisne unse mohabbat ki, Allah us se mohabbat karta hai aur jisne unse bughz rakha Allah us se bughz rakhta hai. Shoba ne kaha : maine Adi se puchha : kya tum ne ye riwayat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hai? to unhon-ne jawab diya : unhon-ne ye hadis mujhii ko sunai thi."
238,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aisa aadmi Ansar se bughz nahi rakhega jo Allah Taala aur qiyamat par eman rakhta hai.
239,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi shakhs Ansar se bughz nahi rakh sakta jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho.
240,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is zaat ki qism jisne daney ko phaadaa aur Rooh ko takhleeq kiya ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bata diya tha ke , mere sath momin ke siwa koi mohabbat nahi karega aur munafiq ke siwa koi bughz nahi rakhega ."
241,"Lais ne ibne-Haad Laisii se khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : aey aurton ki jamat ! tum sadqa kiya karo, aur zyada se zyada istighfar kiya karo, kyonke maine dozkhiyon mein aksariyat tumhari dekhi hai. unmein se aik dilair aur samajh daar aurat ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! humein kya hai, dozakh mein janey walon ki aksariyat hamari ( kyon ( hai? aap ne farmaya : tum laanat bahut bhejtii ho aur khawind ka kufraan ( nemat ( karti ho, maine aql wa Deen mein kam honey ke bawajud , aqlmand shakhs par ghalib aaney main tum se badh kar kisi ko nahi dekha. , us ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! aql wa Deen mein kami kya hai? aap ne farmaya : aql mein kami ye hai ke 2 aurton ki shahadat aik mard ke barabar hai, ye to hui aql ki kami aur wo ( haiz ke doran mein) kai raatein (aur din) guzarti hai ke Namaz nahi padhti aur Ramazan mein beroza rehti hai to ye Deen mein kami hai."
242,( Lais ke bajaey) Bakr bin Muzar ne ibne-Haad se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki.
243,"Ayaaz bin-Abdullah ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur) Saeed ( Maqbari ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai,"
244,"Abu-Bakr bin abi Shaiba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : humein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab ibne-Aadam sajdey ki aayat tilawat karke sajda karta hai to shaitan rotey huey wahan se hat jata hai, wo kehta hai : haaye uski halaakat ! (aur abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai, haaye meri halaakat ! ( ibne-Aadam ko sajdey ka hukm mila to usne sajda kiya, is par usey jannat mil gaee aur mujhey sajdey ka hukm mila to maine inkar kiya, so mere liye aag hai."
245,"Wakee ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki. farq ye hai ke Wakee ne ( فأبيت . . . . .) maine inkar kiya, , ke bajaey) ( فعصيت فعلي النار ( maine nafarmani ki to mere liye jahannam ( muqaddar ( hui, , kahaa."
246,"abu Sufiyan se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : beshak aadmi aur shirk wa kufr ke darmiyan ( fasla mitaaney wala amal ( Namaz ka tark hai."
247,"Abu Zuber ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : aadmi aur shirk wa kufr ke darmiyan ( fasla mitaaney wala amal ( Namaz chhodnaa hai. (is riwayat main ( إن ( be-shak , ka lafz nahi, baqi wahi hai.)"
248,"Mansoor bin abi Mazaahim aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar bin Ziyad ne kaha : humein Ibrahim bin Sad ne ibne-Shihaab se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musayyib se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : kon sa amal sabse afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : Allah azz-wa-jall par eman lana . puchha gaya : phir iske baad kon sa ? aap ne farmaya : Allah ke rastey mein jihad karnaa.' puchha gaya : phir kon sa ? farmaya : hajje mabroor ( aisa Haj jo saraasar neki aur taqwa par mabni aur mukammal ho. ( Muhammad-bin-Jafar ki riwayat mein, , Allah aur uske rasool par eman , ke alfaz hain."
249,Ibrahim bin Sad ke bajaey Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki.
250,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se, unhon-ne abu Muraaweeh Laisii se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha, maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : Allah par eman lana aur uski raah mein jihad karnaa.' kaha : maine ( phir ( puchha : kon si gardan ( aazad karna ( afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : jo uske maalikon ki nazar mein zyada nafees aur zyada qeemtii ho. kaha : maine puchha : agar main ye kaam na kar sakun to? aap ne farmaya : kisi kaareegar ki madad karo ya kisi anaadii ka kaam ( khud ( kar do. maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap ghaur farmaein agar main aisey kisi kaam ki taqat na rakhta hun to? aap ne farmaya : logon se apna shar rok lo (unhein takleef na pahunchaao ( ye tumhari taraf se khud tumharey liye sadqa hai."
251,"( Hisham ke bajaey) Urwa-bin-Zubair ke aazad karda ghulam Hubaib ne pichhli sanad se yahi riwayat bayan ki, farq sirf ye hai ke unhon-ne ( ( تعین صانعا ) kisi kaareegar ke bajaey) ( فتعین الصانع ( (alif Lam ke saath) kaha hai."
252,"( Abu-Ishaq Sulaiman-bin Feeroz Koofii ( Shaibaanii ne Waleed bin Aizaar se, unhon-ne Sad bin Ayas abu Amr Shaibaanii se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine Rasulullah se puchha : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : Namaz ko uske waqt par padhna . maine puchha : iske baad kon sa ? farmaya : waalidain ke sath husne sulook karnaa.' maine puchha : phir kon sa ? farmaya : Allah ki raah mein jihad karnaa.' maine mazeed poochhna sirf isliye chhod diya ke aap par nagawar na guzrey."
253,"Abu Ya'foor ( Abdur-Rehman bin Ubaid bin Nistaas ( ne Waleed bin Aizaar ke hawale se abu Amr Shaibaanii se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kon sa amal jannat se zyada qareeb ( kar deta ( hai? farmaya : namazein apney apney oqaat par padhna . maine puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aur kiya? farmaya : waalidain ke sath husne sulook karnaa.' maine puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aur kiya? farmaya : Allah ki raah mein jihad karnaa.'"
254,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaaz-bin-Muaaz Ambarii ne kaha : humein Shoba ne Waleed bin Aizaar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Amr Shaibaanii ko kehtey huey suna ke mujhey us ghar ke Malik ne hadis sunai (aur Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki taraf ishara kiya ( unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : Allah ko kon sa amal zyada pasand hai? aap ne farmaya : Namaz ko uske waqt par padhna . maine puchha : phir kon sa ? farmaya : phir waalidain ke sath husne sulook karnaa.' maine puchha : phir kon sa ? farmaya : phir Allah ki raah mein jihad karnaa.' ( ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ne mujhey ye baatein bataaeen aur agar main mazeed sawal karta to aap mujhey mazeed bataatey."
255,Shoba se unke aik shagird Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne isi sanad se yahi riwayat bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kiya : abu Amr Shaibaanii ne Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki taraf ishara kiya lekin hamarey samney unka naam na liya.
256,Abu Amr Shaibaanii se unke aik shagird Hasan-bin- Ubaidullah ne yahi riwayat bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : sabse afzal aamaal (ya amal ( waqt par Namaz padhna aur waalidain se husne sulook karna hain.
257,"Mansoor ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne Amr bin Shurehbil se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : Allah ke yahan sabse bada gunah kon sa hai? aap ne farmaya : ye ke tum Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik banao jabke tumhen usi ( Allah ( ne paida kiya hai. maine kaha : waqei ye bahut bada ( gunah ( hai, kaha : maine puchha : phir kon sa ? farmaya : ye ke tum us dar se apne bachchey ko qatl karo ke wo tumharey sath khaaeyga . kaha : maine puchha : phir kon sa ? farmaya : phir ye ke apne padosi ki biwi ke sath zina karo."
258,"(Mansoor ke bajaey) Aamash ne abu-Waail se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah ke yahan sabse bada gunah kon sa hai? aap ne farmaya : ye ke tum Allah ke sath koi Sharik ( bana kar) pukaaro , halanke usi ( Allah ( ne tumhen paida kiya hai. us ne puchha : phir kon sa ? farmaya : ye ke tum apne bachchey ko us dar se qatl karo ke wo tumharey sath khaaeyga . us ne puchha : phir kon sa ? aap ne farmaya : ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo. Allah Taala ne us ( baat ( ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil farmai : jo log Allah ke sath kisi aur ko maabood ( bana kar) nahi pukaartey aur kisi jaan ko jisey ( qatl karna ( Allah ne haram thehraayaa hai, haq ke baghair qatl nahi kartey aur jo zina nahi kartey ( wahi Rehman ke momin bandey hain. (aur jo in ( kaamon (ka irtikaab karega, wo sakht gunah (ki saza ( se  dochaar hoga."
259,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they, to aap ne farmaya : kya main tumhen kabeera gunahon mein sabse badey gunahon ki khabar na dun? (aap ne ye teen baar kaha ( phir farmaya : Allah Taala ke sath shirk karnaa, waalidain ki nafarmani karna aur jhooti gawahi dena (ya Farmaya : jhoot bolnaa ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (pahley ( tek laga kar baithey huey they, phir aap seedhey ho kar baith gaey aur is baat ko dohraatey rahe yahan tak ke ham ne (dil mein) kaha : kash! ! aap mazeed na dohraaein .`"
260,"Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : humein Ubaidullah -bin-abii-Bakr ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kabeera gunahon ke barey mein khabar di, aap ne farmaya : Allah ke sath shirk karnaa, waalidain ki nafarmani karnaa, kisi jaan ko) nahaq ( qatl karna aur jhoot bolnaa ."
261,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujh se Ubaidullah -bin-abii-Bakr ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badey gunahon ka tazkira farmaya (ya aap se badey gunahon ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya) to aap ne farmaya : Allah ke sath shirk karnaa, kisi ko nahaq qatl karna aur waalidain ki nafarmani karnaa.' ( phir (aap ne farmaya : kya tumhen kabeera gunahon mein sabse bada gunah na bataaoon? , farmaya : jhoot bolnaa (yaa farmaya : jhooti gawahi dena ( Shoba ka qaul hai : mera zanne ghalib ye hai ke wo , jhooti gawahi , hai."
262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saat (7) tabah kun gunahon se bacho . puchha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool! wo kon se hain? farmaya : Allah ke sath shirk , jaadoo , jis jaan ka qatl Allah ne haram thehraayaa hai usey nahaq qatl karnaa, yateem ka maal khana , sood khana , ladai ke din dushman ko pusht dikhaana ( bhag jana (aur paak daman , bekhabar momin aurton par ilzam tarashi karnaa.'"
263,"( Yazeed bin-Abdullah ( ibne-Haad ne Sad bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadmi ka apne waalidain ko gali dena kabeera gunahon mein se hai. ( sahaba ( kehney lagey : aey Allah ke rasool! kya koi aadmi apne waalidain ko gali deta hai? farmaya : haan ! insan kisi ke bap ko gali deta hai to wo uske bap ko gali deta hai. jab ye kisi ki maa ko gali deta hai to wo uski maa ko gali deta hai.'"
264,Shoba aur Sufiyan ne bhi Sad bin Ibrahim se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki hai.
265,"Yahya bin Hammad ne kaha : humein Shoba ne Aban bin Taghlib se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Fuzel bin-Amr Fuqaimii se, unhon-ne Ibrahim Nakhai se, unhon-ne Alqama se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jiske dil mein zarra barabar takabbur hoga, wo jannat mein dakhil na hoga. aik aadmi ne kaha : insan chahta hai ke uske kapdey achchhey hon aur uske jootey achchhey hun. aap ne farmaya : Allah khud jameel hai, wo jamaal ko pasand farmata hai. takabbur, haq ko qabool na karna aur logon ko haqeer samajhnaa hai."
266,"Aamash ne Ibrahim Nakhai se pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi insan jiske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman hai, aag mein dakhil na hoga aur koi insan jiske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar takabbur hai, jannat mein dakhil na hoga."
267,( Yahya ke bajaey) Shoba ke aik aur shagird Abu-Dawud ne pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abdullah (bin-masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisa shakhs jannat mein dakhil na hoga jiske dil mein zarra barabar takabbur hoga.
268,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki (Wakee' ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna (aap farma rahe they : jo shakhs us haalat mein maraa ke wo Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik thehraataa tha, wo aag mein dakhil hoga. aur main (Abdullaah) ne kaha : jo us haalat mein maraa ke wo Allah ke sath shirk na karta tha, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga."
269,"Abu Sufiyan ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! wajib karne wali 2 baatein kon si hain? aap ne jawab diya : jo kisi cheez ko Allah ke sath Sharik na karta hua maraa , wo jannat mein dakhil hoga aur jo Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko thehratey huey maraa, wo dozakh mein dakhil hoga. yani tauheed jannat ko wajib kar deti hai aur shirk dozakh ko."
270,"Abu Ayub Ghailaanii Sulaiman-bin Ubaidullah aur Hajjaj-bin Shaair ne kaha : humein Abdul-Malik bin-Amr ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qurra ne abu-Zubair ke waastey se Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jo koi us haalat mein Allah se miley ke wo uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi thehraataa tha, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga aur jo Allah se us haalat mein mila ke uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik thehraataa tha, wo aag mein dakhil hoga. abu Ayub ki hadis ke alfaz mein : abu-Zubair ne ( (حدثنا جابر )) Jaabir ne hamein hadis sunai, , ke bajaey) (عن جابر ) , Jaabir se riwayat hai, ke alfaz se hadis bayan ki."
271,"(Qurra ke bajaey) Hisham ne abu-Zubair ke waastey se Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis sunai : beshak Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . . .) aagey ( pichhli riwayat ki tarah hai."
272,"Ma'roor bin Suwed ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere paas Jibreel aaey aur mujhey khushkhabri di ke aap ki ummat ka jo fard us haalat mein mareyga ke usne Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thehraayaa , wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. main ( Abu-Zar ( ne kaha : chahey us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agarche us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho."
273,"Abu Aswad  ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se hadis bayan ki ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aap aik safaid kapda odhey huey so rahe they. main phir haazire-khidmat hua to ( abhi (aap so rahe they, main phir ( teesri baar ( aaya to aap bedaar ho chukey they. main aap ke paas baith gaya, aap ne farmaya : koi banda nahi jisne ( لا إله إلا الله ( kaha aur phir usi par maraa magar wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. maine puchha : agarche us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho? , aap ne jawab diya : agarche us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho. maine phir kaha : agarche us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho? aap ne farmaya : agarche us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ka irtikaab kiya ho. aap ne teen baar yahi jawab diya, phir chothi martaba aap ne farmaya : chahey Abu-Zar ki naak khaak aalud ho. abu Aswad ne kaha : Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) (aap ki majlis se) nikley to kehtey jatey they : chahey Abu-Zar ki naak khaak aalud ho."
274,"Lais ne ibne-Shihaab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Laisii se riwayat ki ke Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ubaidullah bin Adii-bin Khiyaar ko khabar di ke unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mujhey bataiye ke agar kaafiron mein se kisi shakhs se mera saamnaa ho, wo mujh se jang karey aur mere aik hath par talwaar ki zarb lagaey aur usey kaat daaley, phir mujh se bachao ke liye kisi darakht ki aadh ley aur kahey : maine Allah ke liye Islam qabool kar liya to aey Allah ke rasool! kya ye kalima kehney ke baad main usey qatl kar dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey qatl na karo. unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! us ne mera hath kaat diya aur usey kaat dalney ke baad ye kalima kahey to kya main usey qatl kar dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey qatl na karo. agar tum ne usey qatl kar diya to wo tumharey us maqam par hoga jis par tum usey qatl karne se pahley they aur tum us jagah hogey jahan wo kalima kehney se pahley tha."
275,"Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne Mamar , Auzai aur ibne-Juraij ki alag alag sanadon ke sath Zohri se pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki, Auzai aur ibne-Juraij ki riwayat main ( Lais ki) pichhli hadis ki tarah ( أسلمت لله ( main Allah ke liye Islam ley aaya, , ke alfaz hain jabke Mamar ki riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : jab maine chaha ke usey qatl kar dun to usne ( لا إله إلا الله ( keh diyaa.' ( donon ka hasil aik hai.)"
276,"Yunus ne ibne-Shihaab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ata-bin-Yazeed Laisii Jundaii ne bayan kiya ke Ubaidullah bin Adii-bin Khiyaar ne usey khabar di ke Hazrat Miqdad bin-Amr ( ibne- Aswad ( Kindii (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jo bano Zohra ke haleef they aur un logon mein shamil they jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( ghazwa ( badr mein shirkat ki thi, kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! bataiye agar kaafiron mein se aik aadmi se mera saamnaa ho jaey. . . . . aagey aisey hi hai jaisey Lais ki (riwaayat ki hui ( pichhli hadis hai."
277,"Abu-Bakr bin abi Shaiba ne kaha : humein abu-Khalid Ahmar ne hadis sunai aur abu-Kuraib aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne abu-Muawiya se aur un donon ( abu-Muawiya aur abu-Khalid ( ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Tibyaan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki) hadis ke alfaz ibne-abi Shaiba ke hain) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne humein aik chhotey lashkar main ( jang ke liye) bheja , ham ne subah subah qabila Juhaina ki shaakh Haruqaat par hamla kiya, maine aik aadmi par qaabu pa liya to usne ( لا إله إلا الله ( keh diya lekin maine usey neza mar diya, is baat se mere dil mein khatkaa paida hua to maine iska tazkira Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiya, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya us ne ( لا إله إلا الله ( kaha aur tum ne usey qatl kar diya ? , maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! us ne aslahey ke dar se kalima padha , aap ne farmaya : tu ney uska dil cheer kar kyon na dekh liya taake tumhen malum ho jata ke usne (dil se) kaha hai ya nahi. phir aap mere samney musalsal ye baat dohraatey rahe yahan tak ke maine tamanna ki ke) kash! ( mein aaj hi Islam laya hota (aur Islam laney ki wjah se us kalima bhale hi ke qatl ke azeem gunah se barii ho jata. ( abu Tibyaan ne kaha : (us par) Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aur main Allah ki qism ! kisi Islam laney waley ko qatl nahi karunga jab tak Zul-batan , yani Usama usey qatl karne par taiyaar na hun. abu Tibyaan ne kaha : is par aik aadmi kehney laga : kya Allah ka ye farman nahi : aur unse jang lado yahan tak ke fitna baqi na rahe aur Deen Sara Allah ka ho jaey. , to Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : ham fitna khatm karne ki khaatir jang ladtey they jabke tum aur tumharey sathi fitna barpa karne ki khaatir ladna chahtey ho."
278,"Husain ne kaha : humein abu Tibyaan ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Usama-bin-Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne humein Juhaina ki shaakh (ya aabadi ( Hirqa ki taraf bheja , ham ne un logon par subah ke waqt hamla kiya aur unhein shikast de di, jang ke doran mein aik Ansari aur main unmein se aik aadmi tak pahunch gaey jab ham ne usey gher liya (aur wo hamley ki zad mein aa gaya) to usne ( لا إله إلا الله ( keh diya. unhon-ne kaha : Ansari is par hamla karne se ruk gaya aur maine apna neza mar kar usey qatl kar diya. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke jab ham wapas aaey to ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunch gaee, is par aap ne mujh se farmaya : aey Usama ! kya tu ney uske ( لا إله إلا الله ( kehney ke baad usey qatl kar diya ? kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! wo to (is kalimey ke zariey se) mahz panah hasil karna chahta tha. kaha : to aap ne farmaya : kya tu ney isey ( لا إله إلا الله ( kehney ke baad qatl kar diya ? Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap baar-baar ye baat dohraatey rahe yahan tak ke maine aarzoo ki) kash! ( mein aaj ke din se pahley musalman na hua hotaa."
279,"safwaan-bin-mohrriz ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne fitney ke zamaney mein jundub-bin-abdullaah-bajlii (Raziallahu anhu) ne as'as-bin-Sulaamaa ko paigham bheja aur kaha : mere liye apne sathiyon mein aik nafri (log : teen se das tak ki jama'at) jama karo taake main unse baat karun. chunanche as'as ne apne un sathiyon ki taraf aik qaasid bheja jab wo jama ho gaey to Jundub aik zard rang ki lambi topii pahney huey aaey aur kaha : jo baatein tum kar rahe they, wo kartey raho. yahan tak ke baat cheet ka daur chal padaa. jab baat un tak pahunchi (unke bolney ki baari aaii) to unhon-ne apne sar se lambi topii utaar di aur kaha : main tumharey paas aaya tha aur mera irada ye na tha ke tumhen tumharey Nabi se koi hadis sunaun (lekin ab ye zaroori ho gaya hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmaanon ka aik lashkar mushrekeen ki aik qaum ki taraf bheja aur unka aamnaa-saamnaa hua. mushrikon ka aik aadmi tha, wo jab musalmaanon ke kisi aadmi par hamla karna chahta to is par hamla karta aur usey qatl kar deta aur musalmaanon ka aik aadmi tha jo us (mushrik) ki be-dhyaanii ka khoojii tha. (jundub-bin-abdullaah ne) kaha : ham aik doosrey se kehtey they ke wo Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) hain. jab unki talwaar maarney ki baari aai to usne (لا إله إلا الله) keh diya. lekin unhon-ne usey qatl kar diya. fateh ki khush-khabrii dene wala Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahuncha to aap ne us se (haalaat ke mutaalliq) poochha, us ne aapko halaat bataaey yahan tak ke us aadmi (hazrat Usama (rz)) ki khabar bhi de di ke unhon kya kyaa. aap ne unhein bula kar puchha aur farmaya : tum ne usey kyon qatl kya? unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! us ne musalmaanon ko bahut takleef pahunchai thi aur falan-falan ko qatl kya tha, unhon-ne kuchh logon ke naam ginwaaey. (phir kaha) maine is par hamla kya, us ne jab talwaar dekhi to (لا إله إلا الله) keh diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""kya tum ne usey qatl kar diyaa?"" (Usaama (Raziallahu anhu)) kaha, ji haan ! farmaya : ""qiyaamat ke din jab (لا إله إلا الله) (tumhaarey saamney) aayega to uska kya karogey?"" (Usaama (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mere liye bakhshish talab keejiye. aap ne farmaya : ""qiyaamat ke din (tumhaarey samney kalima) (لا إله إلا الله) aayega to uska kya karogey?"" (jundub-bin-abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse mazeed koi baat nahi kar rahe they, yahi keh rahe they : ""qiyaamat ke din (لا إله إلا الله) (tumhaarey saamney) aayega to uska kya karogey?"""
280,"Ubaidullah aur Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""jisne hamarey khilaf aslaha uthaayaa, wo ham mein se nahi hai."""
281,"ayaas-bin-Salma ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""jisne ham par talwaar soontii , wo ham mein se nahiin."""
282,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ""jisne hamarey khilaf aslaha uthaya , wo ham mein se nahiin."""
283,"Suhail-bin-abii-Saaleh ne apne walid Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""jisne hamarey khilaf hathiyar uthaya , wo ham mein se nahi aur jisne hamein dhokaa diya, wo ham mein se nahiin."""
284,"Alaa ne apne walid Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-ya'qoob se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghalley ki aik dheri ke paas se guzrey to aap ne apna hath usmein dakhil kya, aap ki ungliyon ne nami mehsus ki to aap ne farmaya : ""ghalley ke Malik ! ye kya hai?"" usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! is par barish pad gaee thi. aap ne farmaya : ""to tum ne us (bheegey huey ghalley) ko uper kyon na rakha taake log usey dekh letey? jisne dhokaa kya, wo mujh se nahiin."" (un logon mein se nahi jinhein mere sath waabastaa honey ki izzat hasil hai.)"
285,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne hadis bayan ki, isi ke sath (Muhammad-bin-Abdullaah) ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, in sab (abu-Muaawiya, Wakee aur ibne-Numair) ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-murra se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""jisne rukhsar peetey ya garebaan chaak kya ya ahale jahiliyat ki tarah pukaaraa, wo ham mein se nahiin."" ye Yahya ki hadis hai (jo unhon-ne abu-Muawiya ke waastey se bayan ki) albatta ( Muhammad ( ibne-Numair aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba (jinhon ne abu-Muawiya aur Wakee donon se riwayat ki) ne, (او) ke bajaey (الف) kaha hai. ((aur)ke bajaey (yaa) kaha hai.)"
286,"Jarir aur Esa ne Aamash se usi (pichlii) sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur donon ne kaha : ""aur garebaan chaak kya aur pukaaraa."""
287,"qaasim-bin-mukhaimira ne bayan kya ke mujhey abu-burda-bin-abii-Moosaa (asharii) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne farmaya : Hazrat abu-Musa (ash-arii) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne farmaya : Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌aisey shadeed bimar huey ke un par ghashii taarii ho gaee, unka sar unke gharwaalon mein se aik aurat ki god mein tha, (is mauqe par) unke gharwaalon se aik aurat cheekhney lagii, Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌(shadeed kamzori ki wjah se) usey koi jawab na de sakey. jab fayda hua to kehney lagey : main is baat se barii hon jis se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne barii honey ka izhar farmaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chilaa kar maatam karne waali, sar mundaaney wali aur garebaan chaak karne wali (aurton) se la ta'lluqii ka izhar farmaya tha."
288,"abu-sakhra ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Yazeed aur abu-Barda-bin-abii-Moosaa se (hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein) zikr kya, un donon ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ par ghashii taarii hui aur unki biwi umme-abdullaah cheekhtey huey roney ki awaz nikaaltii aaeiin, kaha : phir unhein fayda hua to usey hadis sunatey huey boley : kya to nahi janti ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""bila shubah main us se barii hon jo (gham ke izhar ke liye) sar moondey, cheekhey chillaey aur kapdey phaadey."""
289,"Imam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne teen doosreii sanadon se Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki uper zikr ki huii  riwayat bayan ki jin mein ayaaz Ash-ari ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ki bevi se, unhon-ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur baqi do sanadon mein Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat karne waley safwaan-bin-mohariiz aur Rabai-bin-Hirash hain jabke ayaaz Ash-ari ki hadis mein : ""barii hoon"" ke bajaey ""ham mein se nahin"" ke alfaz hain."
290,"abu-Waeil ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis riwayat ki ke unko pata chala ke aik aadmi (logon ki aapsii) baat cheet ki chughlii khata hai to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ""chughal khor jannat mein dakhil na hoga."""
291,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Hammaam-bin-Haaris se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke aik aadmi (logon ki) baatein Hakim tak pahunchata tha, ham masjid mein baithey huey they, to logon ne kaha : ye unmein se hai jo baatein Hakim tak pahunchaata hain. (Hammaam ne) ne kaha : wo shakhs aaya aur hamarey paas baith gaya. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke, ""chughal khor jannat mein dakhil na hoga."""
292,"Aamash ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Hammaam-bin-Haaris se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath masjid mein baithey huey they, to aik aadmi aa kar hamarey paas baith gaya. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya gaya ke ye shakhs (logon ki) baatein hukmaraan tak pahunchata hai to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey sunaney ki gharaz se kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ""chughal khor jannat mein dakhil na hoga."""
293,"abu-Zura ne kharshaa-bin-hur se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ""teen (qism ke log) hain Allah unse guftgu nahi karega, na qiyamat ke roz unki taraf dekhega aur na unhein (gunaahon se) paak karega aur unke liye dardnak azab hoga.""  Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ne usey teen baar padha . Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : naakaam ho gaey aur nuqsan se do char huey, aey Allah ke rasool! ye kon hain? farmaya : ""apnaa kapda (takhnon se) nichey latkaaney waalaa, ehsan jataaney wala aur jhooti qism se apne saman ki maang badhaney waalaa."""
294,"Sufiyan ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Aamash ne Sulaiman-bin mus'hiir se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kharsha-bin-hur se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ""teen (qism ke log) hain, qiyamat ke din Allah unse baat nahi karega : mannaan, yani jo ehsan jatlaaney ke liye kisi ko koi cheez deta hai. wo jo jhooti qism ke zariey se apne saman ki maang badhata hai aur jo apna tehband (takhnon se neechey) latkaataa hai."""
295,"(Sufiyaan ke bajaey) Shoba ne Sulaimaan-bin-Aa'mash se yahi riwayat unhi ki sanad se bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""teen (logon) se Allah guftgu nahi karega, na unki taraf dekhega aur na unhein paak karega aur unke liye dardnak azab hoga."""
296,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""teen (qism ke log) hain jin se Allah qiyamat ke din baat nahi karega aur na unko paak farmaeyga (abu Muaawiya) ne kaha : na unki taraf dekhega aur unke liye dardnak azab hai : boodha zaanii, jhoota hukmaraan aur takabbur karne wala khandan wala mohtaaj."""
297,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-kuraib donon ne kaha ke hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki (aur ye alfaz Abu-Bakar ki hadis ke hain) unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""teen (qism ke log) hain jin se qiyamat ke din Allah Taala baat nahi karega na unki taraf dekhega aur na unhein paak saaf karega aur unke liye dardnak azab hai. (eik) wo aadmi jo biyaabaan mein zarurat se zayed pani rakhta hai lekin wo musaafir ko us se roktaa hai, (doosraa) wo jisne kisi aadmi ke sath Asr ke baad (theek insanon ke aamaal Allah ke huzoor pesh kiye janey ke waqt) saman ka saudaa kya aur Allah ki qism khaaii ke maine ye saman itni raqam mein liya hai jabke us ne itney ka nahi liya aur khareedaar uski baat maan leta hai. aur (tesraa) wo aadmi jisne hukmaraan ki bait ki aur sirf duniya ke liye ki (deen ki sarbulandi maqsud na thi) agar us ne usey is (duniyaa) mein se kuchh de diya to (is ne) wafaa ki aur agar nahi diya to wafaadaar na rahaa.''"
298,"Jarir aur absar donon ne apni-apni sanad se Aamash se uper zikr ki hui riwayat bayan ki, albatta Jarir ki riwayat main (''saudaa kiya'' ke bajaey) ye alfaz hain : ""eik aadmi jisne doosrey aadmi ke sath saman ka bhaaw kya.''"
299,"Amr ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki (unho-ne (abu-Saaleh) ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unho-ne (abu-Huraira (rz)) ne ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se siidhey taur per) riwaayat ki) aap ne farmaya : ""teen (qism ke log) hain jin se Allah baat karega na unki taraf dekhega aur unke liye dardnak azab hai, aik aadmi jisne Asr ke baad musalman ke maal ke liye qism uthai aur uska haq mar liyaa.'' hadis ka baqi hissey Aamash ki hadis jaisa hai."
300,"Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisne apne aapko lohey (ke hathiyaar) se qatl kya to wo hathiyar uske hath mein hoga wo hamesha-hamesha ke liye jahannam ki aag mein rahega, usey apne pet mein ghonptaa rahega. jisne zahar pi kar khud-kushii ki, wo hamesha-hamesha ke liye jahannam ki aag mein usey ghoont-ghoont peetaa rahega aur jisne apne aapko pahaad se gira kar khud-kushii ki, wo hamesha hamesha ke liye jahannam ki aag mein pahaad se girtaa rahega.''"
301,"Jareer, abser-bin-qaasim aur Shoba se bhi, pichlii sanad ke saath, uper zikr ki hui riwayat bayan ki gaee hai. Shoba ki riwayat mein hai : Sulaiman (Aamash) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Zakwan se suna, (unhon-ne abu Saaleh-zakwaan se apne samaa, ki (sun'ney ki) wazaahat ki hai.)"
302,Muaawiya-bin-salaam-dimashqii ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat ki ke abu-qiilaaba ne unhein khabar di ke Hazrat saabit-bin-zuh'haak (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khabar di ke unhon-ne (Hudaibiya ke maqam par) darakht ke nichey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki aur ye ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Islam ke ilawa kisi aur mazhab par honey ki pukhta qism khaaii aur (jis baat par us ne qism khaaii us mein) wo jhoota tha to wo waisaa hi hai jaisa usne kaha (uska amal waisaa hi hai) aur jisne apne aapko kisi cheez se qatl kya qiyamat ke din usko usi cheez se azab diya jaeyga aur kisi shakhs par us cheez ki nazar poori karna lazim nahi jiska wo Malik nahiin.''
303,"Hishaam-dustwaaii ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se pichlii sanad ke sath hadis sunai ke Hazrat saabit-bin-zuh'haak (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ''jis cheez ka insan Malik nahi hai, uske barey mein (maanii hui) nazar uske zimmey nahi hai. momin par laanat bhejna (gunaah ke eitibaar se) uske qatl jaisa hi hai aur jisne kisi cheez se apne aapko qatl kya, qiyamat ke din usi cheez se usko azab diya jaeyga aur jisne (maal mein) izaafey ke liye jhoota dawa kya, Allah Taala us (ke maal) ki qillat hi mein izafa karega aur jisne kisi faisley ke mamley mein jhootii qasam khaaii (uska bhi yahi haal hoga).''"
304,"Shoba ne Ayub se, unhon-ne abu-qiilaaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat saabit-bin-zuh'haak Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi ke sath Sufiyaan-soury ne bhi Khalid hazz'aa se, unhon-ne abu-qiilaaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat saabit-bin zuh'haak (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisne jaan-bojh kar Islam ke siwa kisi aur millat mein honey ki jhooti qism khaaii to wo apne qaul ke mutabiq (usi mazhab se) hoga aur jisne apne aapko kisi cheez se qatl kya, Allah usko jahannam ki aag mein usi cheez se azab dega.'' ye Sufiyan ki bayan ki hui hadis hai. aur Shoba ki riwayat yun hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisne Islam ke siwa kisi aur millat mein honey ki jhooti qism khaaii (is riwayat mein, ''jaan-bojh kar'' ke alfaz nahin) to wo isi tarah hai jis tarah usne kaha hai aur jisne apne aapko kisi cheez se zabah kar daalaa, usey qiyamat ke din usi cheez se zabah kya jaaeyga.''"
305,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Hunain mein Sharik huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ke barey mein, jisey musalman kaha jata tha, farmaya : ""ye jahannamiyon mein se hai.'' jab ham ladai mein gaey to us aadmi ne badi zor daar jang ladii jiski wjah se usey zakhm lag gaey is par aap ki khidmat mein kaha ki : aey Allah ke rasool! wo aadmi jiske barey mein aap ne abhi farmaya tha : wo jahannamiyon mein se hai, us ne to aaj badi shadeed jang ladii hai aur wo mar chuka hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""aag ki taraf (jaaeyga).'' kuchh musalman aap ke is farman ke barey mein shak aur shuba mein mubtala honey lagey, (ke aisa jaan-nisaar kaisey dozakhi ho sakta hai) log usi haalat mein they ke bataya gaya : wo maraa nahi hai lekin usey shadeed zakhm lagey hain. jab raat padi to wo (apne) zakhmon par sabr na kar sakaa, us ne khud-kushii kar li. aapko uski itlaa di gaee to aap ne farmaya : ""Allaah sabse bada hai, main gawahi deta hun ke main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hoon.''  phir aap ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhon-ne logon mein elaan kya : ''yaqeenan us jaan ke siwa koi jannat mein dakhil na hoga jo Islam par hai aur bila shubah Allah burey logon se bhi is Deen ki taaiid karaataa hai.''"
306,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sa'd-saaidii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mushrikon ka aamnaa-saamnaa hua aur jang shuru ho gaee, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni lashkar gaah ki taraf paltey aur doosra giroh bhi apni lashkar gaah ki taraf mudaa . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sath dainey walon mein se aik aadmi tha. jo dushmanon (ki safon) se alag reh janey walon ko na chhodtaa, unka peechaa karta aur unhein apni talwaar ka nishana bana detaa, logon ne kaha : aaj ham mein se falan ne jo kar dikhaya kisi aur ne nahi kya, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lekin waqia ye hai ke ye shakhs jahannam-walon mein se hai.'' logon mein se aik aadmi kehney laga : main mustaqil taur par iske sath rahoonga. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : wo aadmi uske sath niklaa. jahan wo thahrtaa wahin ye thahar jata aur jab wo apni raftaar tez karta to uske sath ye bhi tez chal padtaa. (aakhir kaar) wo aadmi shadeed zakhmi ho gaya, us ne jald mar jana chaha to usne apni talwaar ka uper ka hissa (talwaar ka dasta) zamin par rakha aur uski dhaar apni chhaatii ke darmyan rakhii, phir apni talwaar per apna pura wazan daal kar khud-kushii kar li. wo (peechhaa karne wala) aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain. aap ne puchha : ""kya hua?""   to usne kaha, wo aadmi jiske barey mein aap ne abhi bataya tha ke wo dozakhi hai aur logon ne usey ghair maamooli baat samjha tha. is par maine (logon se) kaha : main tumharey liye iska pata lagaaun ga. main uske peechhey nikla yahan tak ke wo shadeed zakhmi ho gaya aur us ne jaldi mar jana chaha to usne apni talwaar ka uper ka hissa (dasta) zamin par aur uski dhaar chhaatii ke darmyan rakhi , phir is par apna pura bojh daal diya aur khud ko mar dala. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ko nazar aata hai ke koi aadmi jannatiyon ke se kaam karta hai, halanke wo dozakhi hota hai aur logon ko nazar aata hai ke koi aadmi dozkhiyon ke se kaam karta hai. halanke (anjaam kaar) wo jannati hota hai.''"
307,"sheibaan ne bayan kya ke maine Hasan (Basrii ( ko kehtey huey suna : tum se pahley logon mein se aik aadmi tha, usey phodaa nikla , jab us ne usey takleef di to usne apne tarkash se aik teer nikala aur us phodey ko cheer diya, khoon band na hua, yahan tak ke wo mar gaya. Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''maine is par jannat haram kar di hai.'' (kyonke us ne khud-kushii ke liye aisa kya thaa.) phir Hasan ne masjid ki taraf se apna hath uncha kya aur kaha : haan, Allah ki qism ! ye hadis mujhey Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (riwaayat kartey huey) isi masjid mein sunai thi."
308,"(sheibaan ke bajaey) Jarir ne bayan kya ke maine Hasan ko kehtey huey suna : hamein jundub-bin-abdullaah-bajlii (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi masjid mein ye hadis sunai, na ham bhooley hain aur na hamein ye dar hai ke Jundub ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jhoot baandha hai. Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum se pahley logon mein se aik aadmi ko phodaa nikla ..... .''  phir usi (pichlii hadis) jaisi hadis bayan ki."
309,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : khaibar (ki jang (ka din tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba aaey aur kehney lagey : falan Shahid hai, falan Shahid hai, yahan tak ke aik aadmi ka tazkira hua to kehney lagey : wo Shahid hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hargiz nahi, maine usey aik dhaarii daar chadar ya abaa ( chori karne) ki bina par aag mein dekha hai, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Khattab ke betey ! ja kar logon mein ailaan kar do ke jannat mein mominon ke siwa koi dakhil na hoga. unhon-ne kaha : meine bahar nikla aur (logon mein) elaan kya : khabardaar! jannat mein mominon ke siwa aur koi dakhil na hoga."
310,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki taraf nikley, Allah ne hamein fateh inayat farmai, ghaneemat mein hamein sona ya chandi na mila, ghaneemat mein saman , ghalla aur kapdey miley, phir ham wadi (Quraa) ki taraf chal padey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ka aik ghulam tha jo juzaam qabeeley ke aik aadmi ne, jisey Rifaa bin Zaid kaha jata tha aur) juzaam ki shaakh ( banu- zubaib se iska talluq tha, aapko hiba kya tha. jab ham ne us wadi mein padao kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka (ye ( ghulam aap ka paalaan kholney ke liye utha , usey ( door se) teer ka nishana banaya gaya aur usi se uskii maut ho gaee. ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! usey shahadat Mubarak ho. aap ne farmaya : hargiz nahi ! us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! odhney ki wo chadar is par aag ke sholey barsa rahi hai jo usney khaibar ke din iske taqseem honey se pahley uthai thii.' ye sun kar log khof-zada ho gaey, aik aadmi aik ya 2 tasmey ley aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke rasool! khaibar ke din maine liye they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aag ka aik tasma hai ya aag ke 2 tasmey hain."
311,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Tufail-bin-Amr dosii (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aapko aik mazbut qil'ey aur tahaffuz ki zarurat hai? (riwaayat karne waley ne kaha : ye aik qil'a tha jo jahiliyat ke daur mein banu- dos ki milkiyat tha) aap ne us (ko qabool karne) se inkar kar diya. kyonke ye khush-naseebi Allah ne Ansar ke hissey mein rakhi thi, phir jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hijrat karke Madina tashrif le gaey to Tufail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hijrat karke aap ke paas aa gaey, unke sath unki qaum ke aik aadmi ne bhi hijrat ki, unhon-ne Madina ki aab w hua na-muwaafiq paai to wo aadmi bimar hua aur ghabraa gaya, us ne apne chaudey phal waley teer liye aur unse apni ungliyon ke androonii taraf ke jod kaat daaley, iske donon hathon se khoon baha yahan tak ke wo mar gaya. Tufail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey khuwab mein dekha, unhon-ne dekha ke uski haalat achi thi aur (ye bhi) dekha ke usne apne donon hath dhaanpney huey they. Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne (aalime-khuwaab mein) us se kaha : tumharey rab ne tumharey sath kya mamla kiya? usne kaha is ne apne Nabi ki taraf meri hijrat ke sabab mujhey bakhsh diya. unhon-ne puchha : main tumhen donon hath dhaanpey huey kyon dekh raha hoon? usne kaha : mujh se kaha gaya : (apnaa) jo kuchh tum ne khud hi kharaab kya hai, ham usey durust nahi karengey. Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye khuwab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sunaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! iske donon hath ko bhi bakhsh de.'"
312,"Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad aur abu-Alqama farwii ne kaha : hamein Safwaan-bin-Sulaim ne Abdullah-bin Salman ke waastey se unke walid ( Salman ( se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala Yaman se aik hawa bhejeyga jo resham se zyada narm hogi aur kisi aisey shakhs ko na chhodegii jiske dil main ( abu-Alqama ne kaha : aik daney ke barabar aur Abdul-Azeez ne kaha : aik zarrey ke barabar bhi) eman hoga magar uski Rooh qabz kar leygii.' (eik zarra bhi ho lekin eman ho to nafa bakhsh hai.)"
313,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un fitnon se pahley pahley jo taareek raat ke hisson ki tarah ( chhaa janey waale) hongey, ( nek ( aamaal karne mein jaldi karo. (un fitnon mein) subah ko aadmi momin hoga aur Sham ko kaafir ya Sham ko momin hoga to subah ko kaafir , apna Deen (eman ( duniyawii saman ke iwaz bechtaa hoga."
314,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Sabit Bunani se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ye aayat utri : ( يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا لَا تَرْفَعُوا أَصْوَاتَكُمْ فَوْقَ صَوْتِ النَّبِيِّ ( , 'aey eman waalo! apni aawaazein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz se unchi mat karo. aayat ke aakhir tak. to Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar mein baith gaey aur kehney lagey : main to jahannami hun. unhon-ne ( khud ko) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki khidmat mein hazir honey) se bhi rok liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : abu Amr ! Sabit ko kya hua? kya wo bimar hain? Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : wo mere padosi hain aur mujhey unki kisi bimari ka pata nahi chala . Hazrat Anas ne kaha : iske baad Sad , Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat batai to Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : ye aayat utar chuki hai aur tum jantey ho ke tum sab mein meri awaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz se zyada buland hai, is bina par main jahannami hun. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne us ( jawab (ka zikr Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : balke wo to ahle-jannat mein se hai."
315,Jafar bin Sulaiman ne kaha : hamein Sabit (Bunaanii ( ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Sabit bin Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) Ansar ke khateeb they. jab ye aayat utri . . . . . aagey Hammad ki (pichhli ( hadis ki tarah hai lekin usmein Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi hai.
316,(Ja'far bin Sulaiman ke bajaey) Sulaimaan-bin-mugheera ne Sabit (Bunaanii) se naql kartey huey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis riwayat ki ke jab ye aayat utri : لَا تَرْفَعُوا أَصْوَاتَكُمْ فَوْقَ صَوْتِ النَّبِيِّ unhon-ne bhi Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya.
317,Motamir ke walid Sulaiman-bin-Tarkhan ne Sabit ke waastey se Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat bayan ki ke jab ye aayat utri (aagey pichhli hadis bayan ki) lekin Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya aur ye izafa kya : ham unhein (is tarah) dekhtey ke hamarey darmyan ahle-jannat mein se aik fard chal phir raha hai.
318,"Mansoor ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya jahiliyat ke aamaal par hamari poochhgachh hogii? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jisne Islam laney ke baad achchhey amal kiye, uska jahiliyat ke aamaal ke barey mein poochhgachh nahi hogi aur jisne burey aamaal kiye, uska jahiliyat aur Islam donon ke aamaal ke mutalliq poochh-gachh hogi.'"
319,"Wakee ne Aamash ke waastey se abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham ne jahiliyat mein jo amal kiye, kya unki wjah se hamari pakad hogii? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Islam laney ke baad achchhey amal kiye, uska un aamaal par pakad nahi hogi jo usney jahiliyat mein kiye aur jisne Islam mein burey kaam kiye, wo agley aur pichhley donon tarah ke amalon par pakda jaeyga,"
320,Aamash ke aik aur shagird Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki.
321,"ibne-Shaamaasa mehrii (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir huey, wo maut ke safar par rawaana they, rotey jatey they aur apna chehra diwar ki taraf kar liya tha. unka betaa kehney laga : abba jaan ! kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aapko falan cheez ki basharat na di thi? kya falan baat ki basharat na di thi? unhon-ne hamari taraf rukh kya aur kaha : jo kuchh ham (aainda ke liye) taiyaar kartey hain, yaqinan usmein se behtreen ye gawahi hai ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain. main teen darjon ( marhalon ( mein raha ( pahlaa ye ke) maine apne aapko us haalat mein paya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath mujh se zyada bughz kisi ko na tha aur na uski nisbat koi aur baat zyada pasand thi ke main aap par qaabu pa kar aapko qatl kar dun. agar main us haalat mein mar jata to yaqinan dozakhi hota. (doosrey marhaley mein) jab Allah Taala ne mere dil mein Islam ki mohabbat paida kar di to main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : apna dayan hath badhaaiye taake main aap ki bait karun aap ne dayan hath badhaayaa, kaha : to maine apna hath ( peechhey ( kheench liya. aap ne farmaya : Amr! tumhen kya hua hai? maine kaha : main aik shart rakhna chahta hun. farmaya : kya shart rakhna chahtey ho? maine kaha : ye ( shart (ke mujhey maafi mil jaey. aap ne farmaya : Amr ! kya tumhen malum nahi ke Islam un tamam gunahon ko saaqit kar deta hai jo us se pahley ke they? aur hijrat un tamam gunahon ko saaqit kar deti hai jo us ( hijrat ( se pahley kiye gaey they aur Haj un sab gunahon ko saaqit kar deta hai jo us se pahley ke they.' us waqt mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada mahboob koi na tha aur na aap se badh kar meri nazar mein kisi ki azmat thi, mein aap ki azmat ki bina par aankh bhar kar aapko dekh bhi na sakta tha aur agar mujh se aap ka huliya puchha jaey to main bata na sakunga kyonke main aapko aankh bhar kar dekhta hi na tha aur agar main us haalat mein mar jata to mujhey ummeed hai ke main jannati hota, phir ( tesraa marhala ye aaya ( ham ne kuchh chizon ki zimme-dari ley li, main nahi janta unmein mera haal kaisa raha ? jab main mar jaun to koi nauha karne wali mere sath na jaey, na hi aag sath ho aur jab tum mujhey dafn kar chuko to mujh par ahista-ahista mitti daalnaa , phir meri qabr ke gird itni der ( dua kartey huey) thaharnaa, jitni der main oont zabah karke uska gosht taqseem kya ja sakta hai taake main tumhari wjah se (apni nai manzil ke saath) maanoos ho jaun aur dekh loon ke main apne rab ke firistaadon ko kya jawab deta hun."
322,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke) jaahilii daur mein) mushrekeen mein se kuchh logon ne qatl kiye they, to bahut kiye they aur zina kya tha to bahut kya tha, phir wo Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kehney lagey : aap jo kuchh farmatey hain aur jis ( rastey ( ki dawat detey hain, yaqinan wo bahut achchha hai. agar aap hamein bata dein ke jo kaam ham kar chukey hain, unka kaffara ho sakta hai (to ham eman ley aaeingey) is par ye aayat nazil hui : jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur maabood ko nahi pukaartey , Allah ki haram ki hui kisi jaan ko nahaq halaak nahi kartey, aur na zina kartey hain aur ye kaam jo koi karey wo apne gunah ka badla paaeyga. (har musalman par un abdii ehkaam ki pabandi zaroori hai) aur ye aayat nazil hui : aey mere bando! jo apne uper zyadti kar chukey ho, Allah ki rehmat se maayoos na ho. (jo Islam se pahley ye kaam kar chukey unke barey mein wo Allah ki rehmat se maayoos na hoon.)"
323,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhein Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : un kaamon ke barey mein aap kya farmatey hain jo main jahiliyat ke daur mein Allah ki ibadat ki khaatir karta tha? mujhey unka kuchh ajr milega? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo nek kaam pahley kar chukey ho tum ne un samet Islam qabool kya hai.'"
324,"( Yunus ke bajaey) Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap un aamaal ke barey mein kya farmatey hain jo main jahiliyat ke daur mein Allah ki ibadat ke taur kya karta tha yani sadqa w khairaat, ghulaamon ko aazad karna aur sila rehmii, kya unka ajr hoga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo bhalai ke kaam tum pahley kar chukey ho tum un samet Islam mein dakhil huey ho. (tumhaarey Islam ke sath wo bhi qabooliyat ka maqam hasil kar chukey hain)."
325,"ibne-Shahab Zohri ke aik aur shagird Mamar ne usi (pichhli (sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki, neez (eik dusri sanad ke saath) abu-Muawiya ne hamein khabar di : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : wo ( bhalai ki) cheezein ( kaam ( jo main jahiliyat ke daur mein kya karta tha? ( Hisham ne kaha : unki murad thi ke main neki ke liye karta tha) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum us bhalai samet Islam mein dakhil huey jo tum ne pahley ki.' maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine jo ( nek ( kaam jahiliyat mein kiye they, unmein se koi amal nahi chhodunga magar us jaisey kaam Islam mein bhi karunga."
326,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Hisham se pichhli sanad se riwayat ki ke Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne daure-jaahiliyat mein so ghulam aazad kiye they aur so oont sawari ke liye ( mustahiqeen ko) diye they, phir Islam laney ke baad) dobara ( so ghulam aazad kiye aur 100 oont sawari ke liye diye, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. . . . . aagey uper zikr ki gaee hadis ke mutabiq bayan kya."
327,"Abdullah-bin-Idris , abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se aur unhoney Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab ye aayat utri : jo log eman laey aur unhon-ne apne eman ke sath zulm ki aamezish (milawat) nahi ki. , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba par ye aayat nagawar guzri aur unhon-ne guzarish ki : ham mein se kon hai jo apne nafs par zulm na karta ho? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is aayat ka matlab wo nahi jo tum samajhtey ho. zulm wo hai jis tarah luqman ne apne betey se kaha tha : aey betey ! Allah ke sath shirk na karnaa, shirk yaqinan bahut bada zulm hai."
328,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Ali-bin-khashram ne kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di, neez minjaab-bin-Haaris tamimi ne kaha : hamein ibne-Mus-hir ne khabar di, neez abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein ibne-Idrees ne khabar di, phir un teenon (Eisaa , ibne-Mus-hir aur ibne-Idrees ( ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki. abu-Kuraib ne kaha : ibne-Idrees ne kaha : pahley mujhey mere walid ne Abaan-bin-Taghlab se aur unhon-ne Aamash se riwayat ki, phir maine ye riwayat khud unhi (Aamash) se suni."
329,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat utri : aasmanon aur zamin mein jo kuchh hai, Allah hi ka hai aur tumharey dilon mein jo kuchh hai usey zahir karo ya chhipaao , Allah Taala is par tumhara muhaasba karega, phir jisey chaahega bakhsh dega aur jisey chaahega azab dega aur Allah har cheez par qaadir hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon par ye baat intihai nagawar guzri. kaha : wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur ghutnon ke bal baith kar kehney lagey : aey Allah ke rasool! (pahley ( hamein aisey aamaal ka paaband kya gaya jo hamari taqat mein hain : namaaz, roza, jihad aur sadqa aur ab aap par ye aayat utri hai jiski ham taqat nahi rakhtey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum wahi baat kehna chahtey ho jo tum se pahley donon ahle-kitab ne kahi : ham ne suna aur nafarmani ki ! balke tum kaho : ham ne suna aur itaat ki. aey hamarey rab! teri bakhshish chahtey hain aur teri hi taraf lautnaa hai. jab sahaba ye alfaz dohraney lagey aur unki zabaanein un alfaz par rawaan ho gain , to iske baad Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us ( hidayat ( par eman laey jo unke rab ki taraf un par nazil ki gaee aur sarey momin bhii. sab eman laey Allah par, uske farishton par, uski kitaabon par aur uske rasulon par, (aur kaha : ( ham (eman laney mein) iske rasulon ke darmyan farq nahi kartey aur unhon-ne kaha : ham ne suna aur ham ne itaat ki, aey hamarey rab! teri bakhshish chahtey hain aur teri hi taraf lot kar aana hai. chunanche jab unhon-ne ye ( maan kar is par amal ( kya to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne is aayat (ke shuruati mana ( mansukh kartey huey ye aayat nazil farmai : Allah kisi shakhs par uski taqat se zyada bojh nahi daaltaa. us ne jo ( neki ( kamaaii aur jo ( buraaii) kamaaii (uska wabaal) usi par hai, aey hamarey rab! agar ham bhool jayen ya ham khata karein to hamara muwaakhiza na karnaa.' ( Allah ne) farmaya : haan. (unhon-ne kahaa:), 'aey hamarey parwardigaar! aur ham par aisa bojh na daal jaisa tu ney un logon par daala jo ham se pahley (guzar chukey) hain. ( Allah ne) farmaya : haan ! ( phir kaha : ( , 'aey hamarey rab! ham se wo cheez na uthwa jiske uthaney ki ham mein taqat nahiin.' ( Allah ne) farmaya : haan ! ( phir kaha : (aur ham se darguzar farma aur hamein bakhshish de aur ham par meherbani farmaa. tu hi hamara kaarsaaz hai, to to kaafiron ke muqaabley mein hamari madad farmaa. , ( Allah ne) farmaya : haan."
330,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha : jab ye aayat nazil hui : tumharey dilon mein jo kuchh hai, usko zahir karo ya chhipaao , Allah is par tumhara muwaakhiza karega.' (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha is se sahaba ke dilon mein aik cheez (shadeed khof ki kaifiyat ke ehkaame-Ilaahii ke us taqazey par amal na ho sakega) ghus gaee jo kisi aur baat se nahi ghusii thi. tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kaho : ham ne suna aur ham ne itaat ki aur ham ne taslim kya.' Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : is par Allah Taala ne unke dilon mein eman daal diya aur ye aayat utari : Allah Taala kisi nafs par uski taqat se zyada bojh nahi daalta . usi ke liye hai jo usney kamaayaa aur usi par) wabaal ( padta hai (us par burai ka ( jo us ne kiya. aey hamarey rab! agar ham bhool jayen ya chook jayen to hamari pakad na karnaa.' Allah ne farmaya : maine aisa kar diya. 'aey hamarey rab! ham par aisa bojh na daal jaisa ke tu ney un logon par daala jo ham se pahley they. farmaya : maine aisa kar diyaa.' hamein bakhsh de aur ham par raham farma, tu hi hamara Maula hai. Allah ne farmaya : maine aisa kar diya."
331,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala ne meri ummat ki un baton se darguzar farmaya hai jo wo (dil mein) apne aap se karein jab tak wo unko zaban par na laaein ya un par amal na karein.'"
332,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala ne meri ummat ki un baton se darguzar farmaya hai jo wo dil main apne aap se karein, jab tak is par amal ya kalam na karein.'"
333,"Misar , Hisham aur Sheban sab ne Qatada se pichhli sanad ke sath usi hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
334,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : jab mera banda kisi burai ka irada karey to usko (iske naamaae-aa'maal mein) na likho . agar wo usko kar guzrey to usey aik burai likho aur jab kisi neki ka irada karey to usko aik neki likh lo, phir agar is par amal karey to das nekiyan likho ."
335,"Alaa ke walid Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne kaha : Allah Taala ne farmaya : jab mera banda kisi neki ka irada karey aur usko amal mein na laey to main uske liye aik neki likhunga, phir agar wo usey kar ley to main usko das se saat so guna tak likhunga aur jab mera banda kisi burai ka irada karey aur usko amal mein na laey to usmein us bandey ke khilaf nahi likhunga, phir agar wo is par amal karey to main aik burai likhunga.'"
336,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne riwayat kartey huey kaha : ye wo hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunaiin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadison zikr kin, unmein se aik ye hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya : Allah Taala ne farmaya : jab mera banda (dil mein) ye baat karta hai ke wo neki karega to main uske liye aik neki likh deta hun, jab tak amal na karey, phir agar usko amal mein ley aaey to main usey das guna likh leta hun aur jab (dil mein) burai karne ki baat karta hai to main usey maaf kar deta hun jab tak is par amal na kare. jab wo usko amal mein ley aaey to main usey uske barabar (eik hi buraaii) likhtaa hun. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : farishton ne kaha : aey rab! ye tera banda hai, burai karna chahta hai aur Allah usko khub dekh raha hota hai, Allah farmata hai : is par nazar rakho, to agar wo burai karey to iske barabar (eik buraaii) likh lo aur agar usko chhod de to uske liye usey aik neki likho (kyonke) us ne meri khaatir usey chhoda hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se aik insan apne Islam ko khalis kar leta hai to har neki jo wo karta hai, das guna se lekar saat so guna tak likhi jati hai aur har burai jo wo karta hai, usey uske liye aik hi likha jata hai yahan tak ke wo Allah se ja milta hai."
337,"Ibne-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kisi neki ka irada kya, phir is par amal nahi kya, uske liye aik neki likhi jati hai aur jisne kisi neki ka irada karke is par amal bhi kya, uske liye das se saat so guna tak nekiyan likhi jati hain aur jisne kisi burai ka irada kya lekin usko kiya nahi to wo nahi likhi jati aur agar usko kya to wo likhi jati hai."
338,"Abdul-Waris ne Jaad abu-Usmaan se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu -Rijaa Utaridi ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki (un hadison mein se jinhein wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne izzat w jalaal waaley rab se riwayat kartey hain) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala ne nekiyan aur buraaiyaan likhi hain, phir unki tafseel batai hai ke jisne kisi neki ka irada kya, phir wo neki nahi ki to Allah ne usey apne yahan aik poori neki likh di aur agar neki ka irada kya, phir wo neki kar dali to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne usey apne yahan das se saat so guna (ya (us se zyada guna tak likh liya aur agar us ne burai ka irada kya, phir usko nahi kiya to Allah ne usey apne yahan aik poori neki likhi aur agar us ne ( burai ka ( irada kya aur usko kar daala to Allah ne aik burai likhi. ,"
339,Ja'far-bin-Sulaimaan ne Ja'ad-abu-Usman se Abdul-Waris ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya : ya Allah ne usey mitaa diya aur Allah ke yahan sirf wahi halaak hota hai jo (khud) halaak honey wala hai (ke Allah ke is qadr Fazal aur karam ke bawajud tabahi se na bach sakaa.)
340,"Suhel ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kuchh log hazir huey aur aap se puchha : ham apne dilon mein aisi cheezein mehsus kartey hain ke ham mein se koi unko zaban par lana bahut sangeen samajhta hai, aap ne puchha : ""kya tum ne waqei apne dilon mein aisa mehsus kya hai?'' unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. aap ne farmaya : ''yahii saaf-saaf eman hai.''"
341,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis riwayat ki."
342,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se was-wasey ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap ne farmaya : ''yahii to khalis eman hai.''"
343,"Sufiyan ne Hisham se hadis sunai, unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log hamesha aik doosrey se (fuzool) sawalat kartey raheingey yahan tak ke ye sawal bhi hoga ke Allah ne sab makhlooq ko paida kya hai to phir Allah ko kis ne paida kya hai?'' jo shakhs aisi koi cheez dil mein paaey to kahey : ''mein Allah par eman laya hoon.''"
344,abu-Saeed-mu'addib ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ke paas shaitan aata hai aur kehta hai : aasman ko kis ne paida kiya? zamin ko kis ne paida kya to wo (jawaab mein) kehta hai Allah ne. . . . . ''  phir uper wali riwayat ki tarah bayan ki. aur ''uske rasulon par (eman laayaa) ke alfaz ka izafa kya.''
345,"ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey (Muhammad-bin-Abdullaah-bin-muslim) ne apne chacha (Muhammad-bin-muslim-Zohrii) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ke paas shaitan aa kar kehta hai ke falan-falan cheez ko kis ne paida kiya? yahan tak ke us se kehta hai : tumharey rab ko kis ne paida kiya? jab baat yahan tak pahunchey to wo Allah se panah maangey aur (mazeed sochney se) ruk jaaey.''"
346,aqeel-bin-Khalid ne kaha ke ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bandey ke paas shaitan aata hai aur kehta hai : falan-falan cheez ko kis ne paida kiya? yahan tak ke us se kehta hai : terey rab ko kis ne paida kiya? so jab baat yahan tak pahunchey to Allah ki panah maangey aur ruk jaaey.'' (ye hadis) ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ki bayan ki hui hadis ke jaisi hai.
347,"abd waaris-bin-Abdus-Samad ke dada Abdul-waris-bin-Saeed ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Siiriin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log tum se hamesha ilm ke barey mein sawal karengey yahan tak ke ye kahengey : Allah ne hamein paida kya hai to Allah ko kis ne paida kiya?'' Ibne-Sirin ne kaha is waqt Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aik aadmi ka hath pakdey huey they, to kehney lagey : Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sach farmaya, mujh se do (aadmiyon) ne (yahii) sawal kya tha aur ye tesraa hai (ya kaha) mujh se aik (aadmi) ne (pahley ye) sawal kya tha aur ye doosra hai."
348,"Ismaaeel-bin-Ulaih ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Muhammad se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ''log hamesha sawal kartey raheingey . . . . ''  baqi hadis Abdul waaris  ki hadis ki jaisi hai. fiir bhii unhon-ne sanad main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr nahi kya, lekin aakhir mein ye kaha hai : ''Allah aur uske rasool ne sach farmaayaa.''"
349,"abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! log hamesha ''tum se sawal kartey raheingey yahan tak ke kahengey : ye (har cheez ka khaaliq) Allah hai to Allah ko kis ne paida kiya?'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir (eik baar) jab main masjid mein tha to mere paas kuchh baddhoo (deihaatii) aaey aur kehney lagey : aey Abu-Hurera ! ''ye Allah hai, phir Allah ko kis ne paida kya hai?'' ( abu-Salma ne) kaha : tab unhon-ne muththii mein kankar pakdey aur un par phainkey aur kaha : utho-utho ! (yahaan se jaao) mere khaleel (dost) (Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne bilkul sach farmaya tha."
350,"Yazeed-bin-as'amm ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yaqeenan log tum se har cheez ke barey mein sawal karengey yahan tak ke kahengey : Allah ne har cheez ko paida kya, phir usko kis ne paida kiya?''"
351,"Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne Mukhtar-bin-fulful se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne kaha : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : ''aap ki ummat ke log kehtey raheingey : ye kaisey hai? wo kaisey hai? yahan tak ke kahengey : ye Allah hai, us ne makhlooq ko paida kya, phir Allah Taala ko kis ne paida kiya?''"
352,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne khabar di, isi ke sath abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin-Ali ne Zayda se hadis sunai aur un donon (Jareer aur zaayda) ne Mukhtar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, fiir bhii Ishaq ki riwayat mein ye alfaz nahi hain : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : ''be shak aap ki ummat ......   .''"
353,"ma'bad-bin-Ka'b Salma ne apne bhai Abdullaah-bin-Ka'b se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu umaama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisne apni qism ke zariey se kisi musalman ka haq maaraa, Allah ne uske liye aag wajib kar di aur is par jannat haram thahraaii.'' aik shakhs ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : agarche wo maamooli si cheez ho, aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : ''chaahey wo peelu ke darakht ki aik shaakh ho.''"
354,"Muhammad-bin-Kab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne bhai Abdullaah-bin-Ka'b se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke abu umaama-haarisii (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko bataya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki jaisi hadis sunii."
355,"Aamash ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne hazrat  Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ''jisne musalman ka maal dabaaney ke liye aisi qism khaaii jiske liye adaalat ne usey paaband kya aur wo usmein jhoota hai, wo Allah ke samney is haalat mein hazir hoga ke Allah is par naraz hoga.'' unhon (wayel) ne kaha is mauqe par Hazrat ash'as-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) (majlis mein) dakhil huey aur kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman (Abdullah-bin-Masood (rz)) tumhen kya hadis bayan kar rahe hain? logon ne kaha : is-is tarah (bayaan kar rahe hain) unhon-ne kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman ne sach kaha, ye aayat mere hi mamley mein nazil hui. mere aur aik aadmi ke darmyan Yaman ki aik zamin ka mamla tha. main iske sath jhagdaa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan ley gaya to aap ne puchha : kya tumharey paas koi daleel (ya saboot) hai? maine kaha : nahi. aap ne farmaya : ''to phir  faisla qism par hoga.''  maine kaha : tab wo qism kha lega. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisne kisi musalman ka maal dabaaney ke liye aisi qism khaaii jiska faisla karne waley ne us se maang ki thi aur wo is qism mein jhoota hai to wo Allah ke samney is haalat mein hazir hoga ke Allah is par naraz hoga.'' is par ye aayat utri : ''bila shubah jo log Allah ke sath kiye gaey waadey aur apni qasmon ka saudaa thodi qeemat par kartey hain...... .'' (aaley-Imraan aayat-77) aayat ke aakhir tak."
356,"(Aamash ke bajaey) Mansoor ne abu-Waeil se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jo shakhs aisi qism uthata hai jiski bina par wo maal ka haq daar thahrtaa hai aur wo is qism mein jhoota hai to wo Allah ko us haalat mein milega ke Allah Taala is par naraz hoga, phir Aamash ki tarah riwayat bayan ki albatta (is mein) unhon-ne kaha : mere aur aik aadmi ke darmyan kuwein ke barey mein jhagdaa tha. ham hi jhagdaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhaarey do gawah hon ya iski qism (ke sath faisla hoga).''"
357,"jaame'-bin-abii-raashid aur Abdul-maalik-bin-aa'yen ne ( abu-Waail ( Shaqeeq-bin-Salma se suna, keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisne kisi musalman shakhs ke maal par, haq na hotey huey, qism khaai, wo Allah se us haalat mein milega ke Allah Taala us se naraz hoga.'' Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey samney kitabullah se iska misdaaq (jis se baat ki tasdeeq ho jaey) padha : ''bila shubah jo log Allah ke sath kiye gaey ahad (meesaaq) aur apni qasmon ka saudaa thodi si qeemat par kartey hain........  .''  (aaley-Imraan aayat-77) aakhir aayat tak."
358,"siimaak ne alqama-bin-waayel se, unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat waayel-bin-hajr (rz)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi hizrey-maut se aur aik kanda se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya. Hizrami (hizrey-maut ke niwasii) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ye meri zamin par qabza kiye betha hai jo merey bap ki thi aur Kandi ne kaha : ye meri zamin hai, mere qabzey mein hai, main is par khaitii karta hun, iska is (zameen) mein koi haq nahi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hizrami se kaha : ''kya tumhari koi daleel (gawaahii wghaira) hai?'' usne kaha : nahi. aap ne farmaya : ''phir tumharey liye uski qism hai.'' usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! bila shubah ye aadmi badkirdaar hai, usey koi parwah nahi ke kis cheez par qism khata hai aur ye kisi cheez se parhez nahi karta. aap ne farmaya : ''tumhein us se is (qasam) ke siwa kuchh nahi mil saktaa.'' wo qism khaney chala aur jab us ne peeth pherii to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baat ye hai ke agar is ne zulm aur zyadti se us shakhs ka maal khaney ke liye qism khaaii to bila shubah ye shakhs Allah se is haalat mein milega ke Allah ne us se apna rukh pher liya hoga.''"
359,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim donon ne abu-Waleed se hadis sunai ( Zuhair ne (abu-Waleed sey) ke bajaaey, hamein Hisham bin Abdul-Malik ne hadis sunai, kaha) Hisham bin Abdul-Malik ne kaha : hamein abu-Awana ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Alqama-bin-Waail se aur unhon-ne (apne waalid) hazrat-Waail-bin hijr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tha, aap ke paas 2 aadmi (eik qat'aa) zamin par jhagadtey aaey, donon mein aik ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! us ne daure-jaahiliyat mein meri zamin par qabza kya tha, wo umraul-Qais-bin-Aabis Kandi tha aur uska dushman Rabee bin abdaan tha. aap ne farmaya : (sab se pahley) tumhara saboot (shahaadat),' usne kaha : mere paas saboot nahi hai. aap ne farmaya : ( tab faisla ( uski qism (par hoga),' usne kaha : tab to wo zamin ley jaeyga aap ne farmaya : iske ilawa kuchh nahiin.' Hazrat Waail (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab wo qism khaney ke liye utha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne zulm kartey huey koi zamin chheenii, wo us haalat mein Allah se milega ke Allah is par naraz hoga. Ishaq ne apni riwayat main (doosrey fareeq ka naam) rabee'a-bin-Eidaan bataya hai."
360,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap ki kya raey hai agar koi aadmi aa kar mera maal chheennaa chahey (to mein kya karun? (aap ne farmaya : usey apna maal na do. usne kaha : aap ki kya raey hai agar wo mere sath ladai karey to? farmaya : tum us se ladai karo. us ne puchha : aap ki kya raey hai agar wo mujhey qatl kar de to? aap ne farmaya : tum Shahid hogey. us ne puchha : aap ki kya raey hai agar main usey qatl kar dun? farmaya : wo dozakhi hoga."
361,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Sulaiman ahwal ne khabar di ke Umar-bin Abdur-Rehman ke aazad karda ghulam Sabit ne unhein bataya ke Abdullah-bin-Amr (ibne-Aas) (Raziallahu anhu) aur Anbasaa-bin-Abii Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan wo (jhagdaa) hua jo hua to wo ladai ke liye taiyaar ho gaey, us waqt (unke chachaa) Khaalid-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Sawar ho kar Abdullah-bin-Amr (bin Aas ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur unhein nasihat ki. Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : kya aapko malum nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai : jo apne maal ki hifazat mein qatl kar diya gaya, wo Shahid hai."
362,(ibne-Juraij ke doosrey shaagirdon) Muhammad-bin-Bakr aur abu-Aasim ne usi mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
363,"abu-Ash'hab ne Hasan ( Basri) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad ne Hazrat Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) ke maut ke marz mein unki iyaadat ki to Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : main tumhen aik hadis sunaney laga hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni. agar main janta ke main bhi aur zinda rahunga to tumhen ye hadis na sunaataa. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : koi aisa banda jisey Allah kisi riaya ka nigraan banata hai aur marney ke din wo is haalat mein martaa hai ke apni raiyat se dhokaa karne wala hai to Allah is par jannat haram kar deta hai."
364,"( abu-Ash'hab ke bajaey) Yunus ne Hasan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad Hazrat Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya, wo us waqt bimar they aur unka haal poochha, to wo kehney lagey : main tumhen aik hadis sunaney laga hun jo maine pahley tumhen nahi sunai thi, bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala kisi bandey ko kisi raiyat ka nigraan banata hai aur maut ke din wo us haalat mein martaa hai ke raiyat ke huquq mein dhokey bazi karne wala hai to Allah is par jannat haram kar deta hai. Ubaidullah ne kaha : kya aap ne pahley mujhey ye hadis nahin sunaaii? Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine tumhen nahi sunai ya main tumhen nahi suna sakta tha."
365,"(eik aur sanad se) Hisham se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hasan ne kaha : ham Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan unki iyaadat kar rahe they ke Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad aa gaya. Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : main tumhen aik hadis sunaney laga hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi. . . . . . phir Hisham ne baqi hadis un donon (abu-Ash'hab aur Yoonus) ki hadis ke mafhoom ke mutabiq bayan ki."
366,"abu-Maleeh (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se riwayat hai ke Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad ne Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimari mein unki iyaadat ki to Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : main maut (ki raah ( mein na hota to tumhen ye hadis na sunaataa. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : koi ameer jo musalmanon ke maamlaat ki zimme-dari uthata hai, phir wo un (ki bahbood (ke liye koshish aur khair-khahi nahi karta, wo unke sath jannat mein dakhil na hoga."
367,"abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Zaid-bin Wahab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 baatein bataaein, aik to main dekh chuka hun aur dusri ka intizar kar raha hun, aap ne hamein bataya : amanat logon ke dilon ke andaroon mein utrii, phir Quran utraa, unhon-ne Quran se seekha aur sunnat se jaanaa. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein amanat utha liye janey ke barey mein bataya, aap ne farmaya : aadmi aik baar soeyga to uske dil mein amanat samet li jaeygi aur iska nishan pheekey rang ki tarah reh jaeyga phir wo aik neend lega to ( Baqiiya ( amanat iske dil se samet li jaeygi aur iska nishan aik aabley ki tarah reh jaeyga jaisey tum angaarey ko apne paon par ludhkaao to (wo hissey ( phool jata hai aur tum usey ubhraa hua dekhtey ho, halanke uske andar kuchh nahi hotaa.' phir aap ne aik kankari li aur usey apne paon par ludhkaayaa.' phir log khareed w farokht karengey lekin koi bhi poori tarah amanat ki adaaeygi na karega, yahan tak ke kaha jaeyga : falan khandan mein aik aadmi amanat daar hai. naubat yahan tak pahuncheygii ke kisi aadmi ke barey mein kaha jaeyga, wo kis qadr mazbut hai, kitna laaiq hai, kaisa aqlmand hai! jabke uske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar (bhi) eman na hoga. (phir Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha :) mujh par aik daur guzraa, mujhey parwaa nahi thi ke main tum se kis ke sath lein-dein karun agar wo musalman hai to uska Deen usko mere paas wapas ley aayega aur agar wo Yahudi ya Esai hai to uska Hakim usko mere paas ley aayega lekin aaj main falan aur falan ke siwa tum mein se kisi ke sath lein-dein nahi kar sakta."
368,"(Aamash ke doosrey shaagirdon) Abdullaah-bin-Numair, Wakee aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne bhi isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee hadis bayan ki."
369,"abu-Khalid Sulaiman-bin-Hayyan ne Sad-bin-Tariq se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Rabaii se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they, unhon-ne puchha : tum mein se kis ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fitnon ka zikr kartey huey sunaa? kuchh logon ne jawab diya : ham ne ye zikr suna. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : shayad tum wo aazmaish murad ley rahe ho jo aadmi ko uske ahal, maal aur padosi (ke baarey) mein pesh aati hai? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is fitney ( ahal, maal aur padosi ke mutaalliq umur (baton) mein ho janey wali kotaahiyon) ka kaffara namaaz, roza aur sadqa bin jatey hain. lekin tum mein se kis ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us fitney ka zikr suna hai jo samandar ki tarah mojazan hoga? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : is par sab log khamosh ho gaey to maine kaha : maine (sunaa hai) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to ne? tera bap Allah hi ka ( banda ( hai (ke usey tum sa betaa ata hua) Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : fitney dilon par daley jaaeinge, chatai (ki bantii) ki tarah tinkaa tinkaa (eik eik) karke aur jo dil unse sairaab kar diya gaya (is ne unko qabool kar liya aur apne andar basaa liya ( , usmein aik siyah nuqta pad jaeyga aur jis dil ne unko radd kar diya usmein safaid nuqta pad jaeyga yahan tak ke dil 2 tarah ke ho jaeinge : (eik dil) safaid, chikney patthar ki tarah ho jaeyga jab tak aasman w zamin qaaim rahengey, koi fitna usko nuqsan nahi pahunchaaeyga. doosra kala matyaley rang ka aundhey lotey ki tarah (jis par pani ki boond bhi nahi tiktii ( jo na kisi neki ko pahchaaneygaa aur na kisi burai se inkar karega, siwaey is baat ke jiski khahish se wo (dil ( labrez hoga. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke aap ke aur un fitnon ke darmyan band darwaza hai, qareeb hai ke usey tod diya jaeyga umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : tera bap na rahe ! kya tod diya jaaeyga? agar usey khol diya gaya to mumkin hai ke usey dobara band kya ja sakey. maine kaha : nahi ! balke tod diya jaeyga aur maine unhein bata diya : wo darwaza aadmi hai jisey qatl kar diya jaeyga ya faut ho jaeyga (Huzaifa ne kaha : maine unhein) hadis (sunaaii koii), mughaaltey mein dalney wali baatein nahi. abu-Khalid ne kaha : maine Sad se puchha : abu Maalik! ( أسودمرباداً ( se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha : kaley rang mein shadeed safedi (matyaaley rang) kaha : maine puchha : (الکوز مجخیا ( se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha : ulta kya hua ghada."
370,"Marwan fazari ne kaha : hamein abu-Malik Ashjai ne Hazrat Rabaii se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : jab Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis se aaey to baith kar hamein baatein sunaney lagey aur kaha : kal jab main ameerul-momeneen ki majlis mein betha to unhon-ne apne sathiyon se puchha : tum mein se kis ne fitnon ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman yad rakha hua hai? . . . . . . . phir ( Marwan fazari ne) abu-Khalid ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki lekin) مرباداً مجخیاً ( se mutaalliq abu-Malik ki tafseer zikr nahi ki."
371,"Nuaim-bin-abii-Hind ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum mein kon hamein bataaeyga (aur unmein Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they) jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fitney ke barey mein farmaya tha? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main. aagey abu-Malik ki wahi riwayat bayan ki hai jo unhon-ne Rabaii se bayan ki aur is mein Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye qaul bhi bayan kya ke maine unhein hadis sunai thi, mughaaltey mein dalney wali baatein nahi, yani wo hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se thi."
372,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Islam ka shuruat ajnabii ki haisiyat se hua aur an-qareeb phir isi tarah ajnabii ho jaeyga jaisey shuru hua tha, khush bakhtii hai ajnabiyon ke liye. ,"
373,"saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam shuru hua ghurbat main aur phir ghareeb ho jaeyga jaisey shuru hua tha aur wo simat kar donon masjidon ( makke Madiney (ke beech mein aa jaeyga jaisey sanp simat kar apne suraakh ( bal ( mein chala jata hai.''"
374,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah eman Madina ki taraf yun simat aayega jaisey sanp apne bil ki taraf simat aata hai.
375,Hammad ne kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke (wo waqt aa jaeyga jab ( zamin mein Allaah-Allaah nahi kaha ja raha hoga.
376,"Mamar ne Sabit se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi aisey shakhs par qiyamat qaaim na hogi jo Allaah-Allaah kehta hoga."
377,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, aap ne farmaya : mere liye shumaar karo ke kitney (log) Islam ke alfaz boltey hain (Islam ka kalima padhtey hain?). Huzefa ne kaha : tab ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aapko ham par (koii museebat nazil ho janey ka ( khof hai jabke ham chh saat so ke darmyan hain? aap ne farmaya : tum nahi jaantey, ho sakta hai tum kisi aazmaish mein daal diye jao. phir ham aazmaish mein daal diye gaey yahan tak ke ham mein se koi shakhs chhipey rahe baghair Namaz bhi nahi padh sakta tha."
378,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad (bin abii-waqaas ( se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne taqseem ka kuchh maal baantaa to maine arz ki, Allah ke rasool! falan ko bhi dijiye kyonke wo momin hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya musalman hai. main teen baar ye baat kehta hun aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teen baar mere samney yahi alfaz dohraatey hain, , ya musalman hai. phir aap ne farmaya : main aik aadmi ko deta hun jabke doosra mujhey us se zyada pyara hota hai, is dar se ke kahin Allah usko andhey munh aag mein) na ( daal de.'"
379,"ibne-Shahab (Zohri (ke bhatijey ne apne chacha se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ne apne walid Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko kuchh ata farmaya, Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unmein baithey they, Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se aik ko chhod diya, usey kuchh ata na farmaya, halanke un sabse wahi mujhey zyada achchha lagta tha, chunanche maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne falan se hath kyon rok liya? Allah ki qism ! main usey momin samajhta hun. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya musalmaan. Sad ne kaha : phir main thodi der ke liye chup ho gaya, phir mujh par is baat ka ghalba hua jo main uske barey mein janta tha to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! falan se aap ne hath kyon rok liya? Allah ki qism ! main to usey momin samajhta hun. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya musalmaan. to main thodi der ke liye chup ho gaya, phir mujh par is baat ka ghalba hua jo main iske barey mein janta tha, chunanche maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! falan se aap ne hath kyon rok liya? kyonke Allah ki qism ! main to usey momin samajhta hun. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya musalmaan. bila shubah mein aik aadmi ko) Atiya ( deta hun. halanke doosra mujhey us se zyada pyara hota hai, is baat se dartey huey ke usey munh ke bal aag mein daal diya jaaeyga.'"
380,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid (hazrat) Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di gaee, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko) Atiya ( diya aur main unmein betha thaa.........   . aagey ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ki apne chacha se riwayat ki tarah hai. aur itna izafa hai : ''main uth kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaya aur sargoshi kartey huey aap se kaha : falan se aap ne ea'raaz kyon farmaayaa.''"
381,"(Aamir-bin-Sa'd ke bhaaii) Muhammad-bin-Sa'd ye hadis bayan kartey hain, unhon-ne apni hadis mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri (Sa'd-bin-abii-Waqaas (Raziallahu anhu) ki) gardan aur kandhey ke darmyan apna hath maaraa, phir farmaya : ''kya ladai kar rahe ho Sad ? ke main aik aadmi ko deta hoon.........  .''"
382,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham Ibrahim se zyada shak karne ka haq rakhtey hain. jab unhon-ne kaha tha : aey mere rab! mujhey dikhaa to mardon ko kaisey zinda karega? Allah Taala ne farmaya : kya tumhen yaqin nahi? kaha : kyon nahi ! lekin (main isliye jaanna chahta hun) taake mera dil mut'ma'in ho jaaey.'' aap ne farmaya : ''aur Allah loout (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaaey, (wo kisi sahaarey ki tamanna kar rahe they) halanke unhon-ne aik mazbut sahaarey ki panah li hui thi. aur agar main qaid khaney mein Yusuf (Alaihissalam) jitna lamba arsa thahrtaa to (ho sakta hai) bulaney waley ki baat maan letaa.'' (amalan aap ne doosrey anbiya se badh kar hi sabr aur bardasht se kaam liyaa.)"
383,"Malik ne Zohri se riwayat ki ke Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Ubaida ne unhein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki jo Zohri se Yunus ki (riwaayat ki hui) hadis ki tarah hai aur Malik ki hadis main (yoon) hai : ''taake mera dil mut'ma'in ho jaaey.''  kaha : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhi yahan tak ke us se aagey nikal gaey."
384,abu-ovais ne bhi Zohri se isi tarah riwayat ki hai jis tarah Malik ne ki hai albatta us ne ((yahaan tak جازھا)) yahan tak ke us se aagey nikal gaey. ''ke bajaaey'' (yahaan tak أنجزها) (yahaan tak ke usko mukammal kya) kaha hai.
385,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''anbiyaa mein se har aik Nabi ko aisi nishaniyan (moa'jzey) di gain jin (ko dekh kar) log eman laaey, aur ''wahi'' mujhii ko di gaee, jo Allah ne mujh par nazil farmai, (wo moa'jza bhi hai, aur noor bhii) isliye main ummeed karta hun ke qiyamat ke din un sabse zyada perokar mere hongey.''"
386,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ‌: ''qasam hai uski jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai. is zamaney ka (yani merey waqt aur merey baad qiyamat tak) koi Yahudi ya nasrani (ya aur koi Deen wala) mera haal suney phir eimaan na laey is par jis ko main de kar bheja gaya hun (yani Quran to jahannam main jaey gaa .
387,"Hushaim ne Saaleh-bin-Saaleh-hamdaanii se khabar di, unhon-ne Shabi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine ahale- khuraasaan mein se aik aadmi ko dekha, us ne Shabi (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya aur kaha : aey abu-Amr ! hamari taraf ahale- khuraasaan us aadmi ke mutaalliq jo apni londi ko aazad karey, phir us se shadi kar ley (ye) kehtey hain ke wo apni qurbani ke janwar par Sawar hone-waale ki tarah hai. Shabi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey abu-Barda-bin-abii-Moosaa ne apne walid se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen aadmi hain jinhein unka ajr do baar diya jaeyga : ahle-kitab ka aadmi jo apne Nabi par eman laya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke daur) ko paya to aap par bhi eman laayaa, aap ki pairwi ki aur aap ki tasdeeq ki to uske liye do ajr hain. aur wo ghulam jo kisi ki milkiyat mein hai, us ne Allah ka jo haq is par hai, ada kya aur apne aaqa ka haq bhi ada kya to uske liye do ajr hain. aur aik aadmi jiski koi londi thi, us ne usey khuraak di to behtreen khuraak muhaiya ki, phir usey tarbiyat di to bahut achi tarbiyat di, phir usko aazad karke us se shadi kar li to uske liye bhi do ajr hain. phir Shabi ne khuraasaanii se kaha : ye hadis bila mashaqqat ley lo. pahley aik aadmi is se bhi chhoti hadis ke liye Madina ka safar karta tha."
388,"abda-bin-Sulaimaan , Sufiyan aur Shoba ne Saaleh-bin-Saaleh ke waastey se pichhli sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki."
389,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se hadis sunai unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! yaqinan qareeb hai ke Esa-ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) tum mein utrein gey, insaf karne waley Hakim hongey, isliye wo saleeb ko tod dengey, khinzeer ko qatl karengey, jiziya khatm kar dengey aur maal ki faraawaanii ho jaeygi yahan tak ke koi usko qabool na karega.''"
390,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Yunus aur Saleh ne (ibne-Shahaab) Zohri se (unkii) isi sanad se riwayat naql ki. ibne-Uena ki riwayat mein hai : ''insaaf karne waley peshwaa, aadil haakim''  aur Yunus ki riwayat mein : 'aadil haakim'' hai. unhon-ne  ''insaaf karne waley peshwa'' ka tazkira nahi kya aur Saleh ki riwayat mein Leis ki tarah hai : ''insaaf karne waley haakim'' aur ye izafa bhi hai : ''yahan tak ke aik sajda duniya aur uski har cheez se behtar hoga.'' (kyonke baqi anbiya ke sath Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par mukammal eman hoga, aur pakkey iraadey wala Nabi jo sahibe-kitab aur shariat tha. aap ki ummat mein shamil hoga aur usi ke mutabiq faisley farma raha hoga.) phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) (aakhir mein) kehtey hain : chaho to ye aayat padh lo : ''ahale-kitaab mein se koi na hoga magar Esa (Alaihissalam) ki wafat se pahley un par zaroor eman laaeyga (aur unhi ke sath ummate-muhammadiya mein shamil hoga).''"
391,"ataa-bin-meenaa ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! yaqinan Esa-bin-Maryam ‌(al) aadil Hakim (faisla karne waale) bin kar utrein gey, har sura mein saleeb ko todengey, khinzeer ko qatl karengey aur jiziya ko hata dengey, jawan oontniyon ko chhod diya jaeyga aur unse mehnat aur mashaqqat nahi li jaeygi (doosrey wasaail muyassar aaney ki wjah se unki mehnat ki zarurat na hogi) logon ke dilon se adaawat, aapsi bughz aur hasad khatm ho jaeyga log maal (ley jaaney) ke liye bulaey jaeinge lekin koi usey qabool na karega.''"
392,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : abu-Qatada-Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Naafe ne mujhey khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us waqt tum kaisey (umda haal mein) hogey jab Maryam ke betey (Eisa) tum mein utrein gey aur tumhara imam tum mein se hoga?'' (utarney ke baad pehli Namaz muqtadi ki haisiyat se padh kar ummate-muhammadiya mein shamil ho jaaengey.)"
393,"ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ne apne chacha (ibne-Shahaab) se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ye riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ""tum kaisey hogey jab Maryam (Alaihissalam) ke betey tumharey darmyan utrein gey aur tumhari peshwaai karengey?'' (jab imamat karaaeingey to bhi ummat ke aik fard ki haisiyat se karaaeingey.)"
394,"ibne-abi-Ze-ib ne ibne-Shahab se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kaisey hogey jab ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) tum mein utrein gey aur tum mein se (ho kar) tumhari imamat karaaeingey !'' main (Waleed bin muslim) ne ibne-abi-Ze-ib se puchha : Auzai ne hamein Zohri se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se is tarah bayan kya : ''aur tumhara imam tumhen mein se hoga.'' (aur aap keh rahe hain, ibne-Maryam imamat karaaeingey) ibne-abi-Ze-ib ne (jawaab mein) kaha : jantey ho, tum mein tumhari imamat karaaeingey, ka matlab kya hai? maine kaha : aap mujhey bata dijiye. unhon-ne jawab diya ke tumharey shaan-waaley-rab ki kitab aur tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat ke sath (tum mein aik fard ki haisiyat se ya tumhari ummat ka fard bin kar) tumhari qiyaadat ya imamat karengey."
395,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat ka aik giroh musalsal haq par (qaaim rahtey huey) ladta rahega, wo qiyamat ke din tak (jis bhi jang mein hongey) ghalib raheingey, kaha : phir Esa-ibne-Maryam ‌(al) utrein gey to is taaifa (garoh) ka ameer kahega : aaein hamein Namaz padhaaein, is par Esa ‌(al) ‌ jawab dengey : nahi, Allah ki taraf se is ummat ko bakhshi gaee izzat aur sharf ki bina par tum hi eik-doosrey par ameer ho.''"
396,"Ala-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak suraj maghrib se nahi nikalta, us waqt tak qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi. jab wo maghrib se nikley-ga to sab ke sab log eman ley aaeingey. us din, kisi aisey shakhs ko iska eman fayda nahi dega jo pahley eman na laya tha ya apne eman (ki haalat) mein koi neki na kamai thi.'' (amal se tasdeeq na ki thi.)"
397,"abu-Zura, Abdur-Rehman-Aaraj aur Hammam-bin-Munabbah se bhi Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se usi jaisi riwayat mazkoor hai. jo Alaa ne apne walid ke waastey se Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki."
398,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : teen cheezein hain jab wo zahir ho jaaeygi to us waqt kisi shakhs ko, jo is se pahley eman nahi laya tha ya apne eman ke doran mein koi neki na ki thi, uska eman lana fayda na dega : suraj ka maghrib se nikalna, dajjal aur daabba (zameni keeda)(zameen se aik ajeeb janwar ka nikalnaa.)"
399,"(Ismaaeel) ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Yunus ne Ibrahim-bin-Yazeed Taimi ke hawale se hadis sunai, mere ilm ke mutaabiq, unhon-ne ye hadis apne walid (Yazeed) se suni aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din puchha : ''jaantey ho ye suraj kahan jata hai?'' sahaba ne jawab diya : Allah aur uska rasool zyada aagah hain. aap ne farmaya : ''ye chalta rehta hai yahan tak ke arsh ke nichey apne rehney ki jagaah par pahunch jata hai. phir sajdey mein chala jata hai. wo musalsal usi haalat mein rehta hai yahan tak ke usey kaha jata hai : utho ! jahan se aaey they udhar lot jao to wo wapas laut'taa hai aur apne matla' se nikalta hai, phir chalta hua arsh ke nichey apni qiyam ki jagaah par pahunch jata hai, phir sajda rez ho jata hai aur usi haalat mein rehta hai yahan tak ke us se kaha jata hai : buland ho jao aur jahan se aaey they, udhar lot jao to wo wapas jata hai aur apne matla' se nikalta hai. phir (eik din sooraj) chaley ga, log usmein mamool (routine) se hatii hui koi cheez nahi paeingey yahan tak ke (jab) ye arsh ke nichey apne usii rehney ki jagaah par pahunchega to us-sey kaha jaeyga : buland ho aur apne maghrib (jis taraf ghurub hota tha, usi simt) se nikal. to wo apne maghrib se niklega.'' phir aap ne farmaya : ''kya jantey ho ye Kab hoga? ye us waqt hoga jab , kisi shakhs ko uska eman lana fayda na pahunchaeyga jo is se pahley eman nahi laya tha ya apne eman ke dauran mein neki nahi kamai thi.''"
400,Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne Yunus se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik din Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ye suraj kahan jata hai? . . . . . . . iske baad ibne-Ulaih wali hadis ke ham mana (riwaayat ( hai.
401,"abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim Taimi se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main masjid mein dakhil hua jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma they, jab suraj ghayab ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Abu-Zar ! kya tum jantey ho ye suraj kahan jata hai? kaha : maine kaha : Allah aur uska rasool behtar jaanney waley hain. farmaya : ye jata hai, phir sajdey ki ijazat mangta hai to usey sajdey ki ijazat di jati hai, ( phir yun hoga ke) jaisey us se keh diya gaya ho (is mein ishara hai ke ham haqiqat ko nahi samajh saktey , hamein tamseelan uski khabar di ja rahi hai) ke jis taraf se aaey they, udhar lot jao to ye apni ghurub honey wali samt se tuloo ho jaeyga Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir aap ne ( تَجْرِي لِمُسْتَقَرٍّ لَهَا (ke bajaey) Abdullah-bin-Masood ki riwayat ki hui qirat ke mutabiq padha : ( وذلك مستقرلها ( ye iska mustaqar hai."
402,Wakee ne Aamash se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Allah Taala ke us farman ke barey mein sawal kya : suraj apne mustaqar ki taraf chal raha hai. aap ne jawab diya : iska mustaqar arsh ke nichey hai.
403,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne hadis sunai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf wahi ka shuruat sabse pahley neend mein sachey khuwab aaney se hua. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo khuwab bhi dekhtey uski tabeer subah ke roshan honey ki tarah samney aa jaatii, phir tanhai aapko mahboob ho gaee, aap ghaare-hira mein khilwat ikhtiyar farmatey aur ghar wapas ja kar) dobara ( usi gharaz ke liye zaade-raah laney se pahley ( muqarrara ( tadaad mein raatein ( tahannus ( mein masroof rahtey, ( tahannus ( ibadat guzari ko kehtey hain, (iske baad) aap phir Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas wapas aa kar, itni hi raaton ke liye khaaney-peeney ka saman ley jatey, (ye silsila chalta raha) yahan tak ke achcha aap ke paas haq (ka paigham ( aa gaya, us waqt aap ghaare-hira hi mein they, chunanche aap ke paas farishta aaya aur kaha : padhiye ! aap ne jawab diya : main padh sakney wala nahi hun, aap ne farmaya : to us ( Farishtey ( ne mujhey pakad kar zor se bheencha yahan tak ke (iska dabaaw) meri bardasht ki aakhiri had ko pahunch gaya, phir usne mujhey chhod diya aur kaha : padhiye ! maine kaha : main padh sakney wala nahi hun, phir usne mujhey pakda aur dobara bheencha yahan tak ke meri bardasht ki aakhiri had aa gaee, phir usne mujhey chhod diya aur kaha : padhiye ! maine kaha : main padh sakney wala nahi hun, phir us ne teesri baar mujhey pakad kar poori quwwat se bheencha yahan tak ke meri bardasht ki aakhiri had aa gaee, phir mujhey chhod diya aur kaha : apne rab ke naam se padhiye jisne paida kya, us ne insan ko gosht ke jonk jaisey lothdey se paida kya, padhiye aur aap ka rab sabse badh kar Karim hai jisne qalam ke zariey se taleem di aur insan ko sikhaya jo wo na janta tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un aayatein ke sath wapas lautey , (is waqt) aap ke kandhon aur gardan ke darmyan ke gosht ke hissey laraz rahe they yahan tak ke aap Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas pahunchey aur farmaya : mujhey kapda odhaao, mujhey kapda odhaao.' unhon (ghar waalon) ne kapda odha diya yahan tak ke aap ka khof jata raha to aap ne Hazrat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : khadeeja! ye mujhey kya hua hai? Khadija ne jawab diya : hargiz nahi ! ( balke) aapko khush khabrii ho Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala aapko hargiz ruswa na karega, Allah ki qism ! aap sila rehmii kartey hain, sachchii baat kehtey hain, kamzoron ka bojh uthatey hain, usey kamaa kar detey hain jiske paas kuchh na ho, mehman nawazi kartey hain, haq ke liye pesh aaney wali mushkilaat mein iaa'nat kartey hain, phir Khadija (Raziallahu anha) aapko lekar Warqa-bin-naufal-bin-Asad-bin-abdul-Uzza ke paas pahunchiin, wo Hazrat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke chacha zaad , unke walid ke bhai ke betey they, wo aisey aadmi they jo jahiliyat ke daur mein Esai ho gaey they, arabii khat mein likhtey they, aur jis qadr Allah ko manzoor tha, Injeel ko arabii zaban mein likhtey they, bahut boodhey they aur beenaaii jati rahi thi. Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha : chachaa! apne bhatijey ki baat suniye, Warqa-bin Nofal ne puchha : bhateejey! aap kya dekhtey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo kuchh dekha tha, uska haal bataya to Warqa ne aap se kaha : ye wahi namus ( raazon ka muhafiz) hai jisey Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ki taraf bheja gaya tha, kash! us waqt mein jawan hota, kash! mein us waqt zinda ( maujood ( hon jab aap ki qaum aapko nikal degi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ? to kya yahi log mujhey nikalney waley hongey ? Warqa- ne kaha : haan , kabhi koi aadmi aap jaisa paigham lekar nahi aaya magar us se dushmanii ki gaee aur agar aap ka (wo ( din meri zindagi mein aa gaya to main aap ki bharpur madad karunga."
404,"hamein Mamar ne khabar di ke unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf wahi ki shuruaat . . . . . . aagey Yunus ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, siwaey iske ke Mamar ne (laa yahzun-k abadan) aapko Allah kabhi ghamgeen na karega,' kaha, unhon-ne (ye bhi) kaha ke Hazrat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne ye alfaz kahey : chacha ke betey ! apne bhatijey ki baat sunein."
405,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne bayan kya ke ibne-Shahab ne kaha : maine Urwa-bin-Zubair ko ye kehtey huey suna : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey, aap ka dil shiddat se dhadak raha tha. . . . . phir ( Aqeel ne) Yunus aur Mamar ki tarah hadis bayan ki. aur un donon ki riwayat ka shuruati hissa, yani unka ye qaul ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf wahi ka shuruat sachchey khuwabon ki soorat mein hua, bayan nahi kya. ye bhi ke Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne Yunus ke un alfaz ""Allaah ki qasam! Allah aapko hargiz ruswa na karega."" mein mutabiat (pairavi) karne ke sath Hazrat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ka ye qaul bhi zikr kya hai : chacha ke betey ! apne bhatijey ki baat sunein."
406,"Yunus ne (apni sanad ke saath) ibne-Shahab se bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf ne khabar di ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) jo Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se they, ye hadis sunaya kartey they, kaha : wahi ke ruk janey ka waqia bayan kartey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is doran mein jab main chal raha tha, maine aasman se aik awaz suni, is par maine apna sar uthaya to achcha (dekha) wahi farishta tha jo merey paas ghaare-hira mein aaya tha, aasman w zamin ke darmyan kursi par betha tha. aap ne farmaya : iske khof ki wjah se mujh par ghabraahat taarii ho gaee aur main ghar wapas aa gaya aur kaha : mujhey kapda odhaao, mujhey kapda odhaao to unhon (ghar waalon) ne mujhey kambal odha diya. is par Allah tabarak w taala ne ye aayatein utaariin : aey odh lapet kar letney waley utho aur khabardaar karo aur apne rab ki badaai ka elaan kijiye aur apne kapdey paak rakhiye aur gandagi se door rahiye. aur is ((الرجز) yani gandagi) se murad but hain. farmaya : phir wahi musalsal nazil honey lagi"
407,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ko ye kehtey huey suna ke mujhey Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : phir wahi ka silsila aik waqfey (kuchh dinon) ke liye mujh se rok liya gaya tha, usi doran mein jab main chal raha tha. . . . . phir ( Aqeel ne) Yunus ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne ( mazeed ye ( kaha : to khof se mujh par ghabraahat taarii ho gaee yahan tak ke main zamin par gir padaa, (ibne-Shahaab ne kaha : abu-Salma ne bataya : ( الرجز ( se but murad hain) kaha : phir nuzoole-wahi (ki raftaar) mein garmi aa gaee aur musalsal nazil honey lagi"
408,"Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath Yunus ki tarah hadis bayan ki (is mein ye ( kaha : to Allah tabarak w taala ne : (ya ayyuhal muddassir) se lekar (war-rujza-fahjur) tak (ki aayatein) nazil farmain (namaz farz honey se pahley ka waqia hai) aur us ( الرجز Mina ( se but murad hain, neez Mamar ne Aqeel ki tarah, mujh par khof taarii ho gayaa."
409,"Auzai ne kaha : maine Yahya se suna, kehtey they : maine abu-Salma se sawal kya : Quran ka kon sa hissey pahley nazil hua? kaha : ( يٰٓاَيُّهَا الْمُدَّثِّرُ ( maine kaha : ya (iqra)? abu-Salma ne kaha : maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Quran ka kon sa hissey pahley utara gayaa? unhon-ne jawab diya : ( يٰٓاَيُّهَا الْمُدَّثِّرُ ( maine kaha : ya (iqra(?) Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tumhen wahi baat bataataa hun jo hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataaii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine hira mein aik maah aetikaf kya. jab maine apna aetikaf khatm kya to main utra, phir main wadi ke darmyan pahuncha to mujhey awaz di gaee, is par maine apne aagey peechhey daaein-baaein nazar daudai to mujhey koi nazar na aaya, mujhey phir awaz di gaee maine dekha, mujhey koi nazar na aaya, phir (teesrii baar) mujhey awaz di gaee to maine sar uper uthaya to wahi ( farishta ( fiza mein takht ( kursi ( par betha hua tha (yani Jibreel ‌ (Alaihissalam) ( uski wjah se mujh par sakht larza taari ho gaya. main Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aa gaya aur kaha : mujhey kambal odha do, mujhey kambal odha do, unhon-ne mujhey kambal odha diya aur mujh par pani dala. to us (mauqe) par Allah Taala ne ye aayatein utarin : aey kambal odhney wale! uth aur dara aur apne rab ki badaai bayan kar aur apne kapdey paak rakh."
410,Ali bin-Mubarak ne bhi Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : to wo aasman w zamin ke darmyan aik kursi par baithey huey they.
411,"saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere samney burraaq laya gaya aur wo aik janwar hai safaid rang ka gadhey se uncha aur khachchar se chhotaa. apne sum wahan rakhta hai, jahan tak uski nigaah pahunchti hai (to aik lamhe mein aasman tak ja sakta hai) main is par Sawar hua aur baitul-maqdis tak aaya. wahan us janwar ko halqe se baandh diya. jis se aur paighambar apne apney janwaron ko baandha kartey they (ye halqa masjid ke darwazey par hai aur baandh deney se malum hua ke insan ko apni chizon ki ehtiyat aur hifazat zaroori hai aur ye twakkul ke khilaf nahi ( phir main masjid ke andar gaya aur 2 rakatein Namaz padhein baad iske bahar nikla to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) 2 bartan lekar aaey aik mein sharab thi aur aik mein doodh. maine doodh pasand kya. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath aasman par chadhey (jab wahan pahunchey) to farishton se kaha : darwaza kholney ke liye, unhon-ne puchha kon hai? Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Jibreel hai. unhon-ne kaha : tumharey sath doosra kon hai? Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. farishton ne puchha : kya bulaey gaey they. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : haan bulaey gaey hain, phir darwaza khola gaya hamarey liye aur ham ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko dekha. unhon-ne marhaba kaha aur mere liye dua ki behtri ki. phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath chadhey doosrey aasman par aur darwaza khulwaayaa, farishton ne puchha : kon hai. unhon-ne kaha : Jibreel. farishton ne puchha : tumharey sath doosra kon shakhs hai? unhon-ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain farishton ne kaha : kya unko hukm hua tha bulaney kaa. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : haan unko hukm hua hai, phir darwaza khula to maine donon khala zaad bhaiyon ko dekha yani Eisaa-bin-Maryam aur Yahya-bin-Zakarya (Alaihissalam) ko un donon ne marhaba kaha aur mere liye behtri ki dua ki phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath teesrey aasman par chadhey aur darwaza khulwaayaa. farishton ne kaha : kon hai? Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Jibreel. farishton ne kaha : doosra tumharey sath kon hai. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. farishton ne kaha : kya unko paigham diya gaya tha bulaney ke liye? Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : haan unko paigham diya gaya tha phir darwaza khula to maine Yosuf (Alaihissalam) ko dekha Allah ne Husn (khoobsoortii) ka aadha hissey unko diya tha. unhon-ne marhaba kaha mujh ko aur nek dua ki phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ham ko lekar chauthey aasman par chadhey aur darwaza khulwaya farishton ne puchha : kon hai? kaha : Jibreel. puchha : tumharey sath doosra kon hai? kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain farishton ne kaha : kya bulwaaey gey hain? Jibreel ne kaha : haan bulwaaey gaey hain, phir darwaza khula to maine Idrees (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, unhon-ne marhaba kaha aur achi dua di mujh ko, Jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : ham ne utha liya Idrees ko unchi jagah par (to unchi jagah se yahi chotha aasman murad hai) phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath paanchwein aasman par chadhey . unhon-ne darwaza khulwaya. farishton ne puchha : kaun? kaha Jibreel. puchha tumharey sath kon hai? kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. farishton ne kaha : kya bulaey gaey hain. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha haan bulwaaey gaey hain, phir darwaza khula to maine Harun (Alaihissalam) ko dekha unhon-ne marhaba kaha aur mujhey nek dua di. phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath chhatey aasman par pahunchey aur darwaza khulwaya farishton ne puchha kon hai? kaha : Jibreel. puchha aur kon hai tumharey sath ? unhon-ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. farishton ne kaha : kya Allah ne unko paigham bheja aa milney ke liye? Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : haan bhejaa, phir darwaza khula to maine Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, unhon-ne kaha : marhaba aur achi dua di mujh ko, phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath saatwein aasman par chadhey aur darwaza khulwaya farishton ne puchha : kon hai? kaha : Jibreel, puchha : tumharey sath aur kon hai? kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. farishton ne puchha : kya wo bulwaaey gaey hain? unhon-ne kaha : haan bulwaaey gaey hain. phir darwaza khula to maine Ibrahim ko dekha wo takiya lagaey huey they apni peeth ka baitul-ma'moor ki taraf (is se ye malum hua ke qible ki taraf peeth karke baithna durust hai) aur is mein har roz 70 hazaar Farishtey jatey hain jo phir kabhi nahi aatey phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) mujh ko) sidratul-muntaha (ke paas ley gaey. iske pattey itney badey they jaisey haathii ke kaan aur uske beir jaisey aik bada ghadaa jis mein 2 mashk ya zyada pani aata hai phir jab us darakht ko Allah ke Hakam ne dhanka to uska haal aisa ho gaya ke koi makhlooq uski khoobsoortii bayan nahi kar sakti phir Allah ne daala mere dil mein jo kuchh daala aur pachaas namazein har raat aur din mein mujh par farz kin, jab main utra aur Musa (Alaihissalam) tak pahuncha to unhon-ne puchha : tumharey parwardigar ne kya farz kya tumhari ummat par. maine kaha : pachaas namazein farz kin. unhon-ne kaha : phir lot jao apne parwardigar ke paas aur kami karoo, kyonke tumhari ummat ko itni taqat na hogi aur maine Bani-Israeel ko aazmaya hai aur unka imtihaan liya hai. main lot gaya apne parwardigar ke paas aur arz kya : aey parwardigar ! kami kar meri ummat par Allah Taala ne panch namazein ghataa din. main lot kar Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke panch namazein Allah Taala ne mujhey maaf kar din. unhon-ne kaha : tumhari ummat ko itni taqat na hogi tum phir jao apne rab ke paas aur kami karaao. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main is tarah barabar apne parwardigar aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ke darmyan aata jata raha yahan tak ke Allah ne farmaya : aey Muhammad ! wo panch namazein hain, har din aur har raat main aur har aik Namaz mein das Namaz ka sawab hai, to wahi pachaas namazein huin (Subhan-Allaah! Malik ki kaisi inayat apne ghulaamon par hai ke padhein to panch namazein aur sawab miley pachaas ka (aur jo koi shakhs niyat karey kaam karne ki nek, phir usko na karey to usko aik neki ka sawab milega aur jo karey to das nekiyon ka aur jo shakhs niyat karey burai ki phir usko na karey to kuchh na likha jaeyga aur agar kar baithey to aik hi burai likhi jaeygi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir main utra aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya. unhon-ne kaha : phir jao apne parwardigar ke paas aur kami chaho Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main apne parwardigar ke paas baar-baar gaya yahan tak ke main sharma gaya us se."
412,"Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere paas ( Farishtey ( aaey aur mujhey zamzam ke paas le gaey, mera Sina chaak kya gaya, phir zamzam ke pani se dhoya gaya, phir mujhey ( wapas apni jagah ( utaar diya gaya. (ye meraaj se fauran pahley ka waqia hai.)"
413,"(Sulaimaan-bin Mughira ke bajaey) Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Sabit ke waastey se Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Jibreel aaey jabke aap bachchon ke sath khel rahe they, unhon-ne aapko pakda, nichey litaya, aap ka Sina chaak kya aur dil nikal liya, phir us se aik lothdaa nikala aur kaha : ye aap (ke dil mein) se shaitan ka hissa tha, phir us (dil ( ko soney ke tasht mein zamzam ke pani se dhoya, phir usko joda aur uski jagah par lota diya, bachchey daudtey huey aap ki waalida, yani aap ki dudh-sharik maa ke paas aaey aur kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko qatl kar diya gaya hai. (ye sun kar log daudey) to aapko samney se aatey huey paya, aapka rang badla hua tha, Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main us silai ka nishan aap ke seeney par dekha karta tha. (ye bachpan ka shaqe-sadr hai.)"
414,"Shareek-bin-Abdullaah-bin-abii-Namir ne hadis sunai (kaha ( : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hamein us raat ke barey mein hadis suna rahe they jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjide-Kaba se raat ke safar par ley jaya gaya ke aap ki taraf wahi kiye janey se pahley aap ke paas teen log ( Farishtey ( aaey, us waqt aap masjide-haraam mein soey huey they. Sharik ne, waqia Israa, Sabit Bunani ki hadis ki tarah sunaya aur is mein kuchh chizon ko aagey peechhey kar diya aur) kuchh mein) kami beshi ki. (Imam Muslim ne ye tafseel bata kar poori riwayat naql karne ki zarurat mehsus nahi ki.)"
415,"ibne-Shahab ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya : main Makka mein tha to mere ghar ki chhat kholi gaee, Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ utrey, mera Sina chaak kya, phir usey zam zam ke pani se dhoya , phir soney ka tasht laey jo hikmat aur eman se labrez tha, usey mere seeney mein undel diya, phir usko jod diya, phir mera hath pakad ا aur mujhey lekar aasman ki taraf buland huey, jab ham sabse nichley (pahley ( aasman par pahunchey to Jibreel ne (is ( nichley aasman ke darbaan se kaha : darwaza kholo. usne kaha : ye kon hain? kaha : ye Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ hai. puchha : kya terey sath koi hai? kaha haan , mere sath Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. us ne puchha : kya unko bulaya gaya hai? kaha haan , phir us ne darwaza khola Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke jab ham aasmaane-duniyaa par pahunchey to dekha ke aik aadmi hai uske daain taraf bhi bahut si makhlooq hai aur uske baain taraf bhi bahut si makhlooq hai jab wo aadmi apne daain taraf dekhta hai to hanstaa hai aur apne baain taraf dekhta hai to rotaa hai. usne kaha : khush aamadeed ! nek Nabi aur nek betey ko . maine Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) se kaha : ke ye kon hain? Hazrat Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke ye Adam (Alaihissalam) hain aur unke daain taraf jannati aur baain taraf waley dozakhi hain isliye jab daain taraf dekhtey hain to hanstey hain aur baain taraf dekhtey hain to rotey hain. phir Hazrat Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) mujhey doosrey aasman ki taraf le gaey aur uske pahrey daar se kaha : darwaza kholo . iske khaazin ne bhi pahley aasman waley ki tarah baat ki aur darwaza khol diya. Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya ke mujhey aasmanon par Adam , Idrees , Musa aur Ibrahim miley ( ikhtisar se bataatey huey) unhon ( Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ye ta'yun nahi ki ke unki manzilein kaisey thiin? albatta ye bataya ke Adam ‌(al) aapko pahley aasman par miley aur Ibrahim chhatey aasman par (ye kisi rawi ka waham hai. Hazrat Ibrahim se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mulaqat saatwen aasman par hui ( , farmaya : jab Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Idrees (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzrey to unhon-ne kaha : Saleh Nabi aur Saleh bhai ko khush aamadeed, phir wo aagey guzrey to maine puchha : ye kon hain? to (Jibriil ne) kaha : ye Idrees (Alaihissalam) hain, phir main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra to unhon-ne kaha : Saleh Nabi aur Saleh bhai ko khush aamadeed, farmaya : maine puchha : ye kon hain? unhon-ne kaha : ye Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ hain, phir main Esa ‌(al) ‌ ke paas se guzraa, unhon-ne kaha : Saleh Nabi aur Saleh bhai ko khush aamadeed, maine puchha : ye kon hain? kaha : Esa bin Maryam hain. aap ne farmaya : phir main Ibrahim ke paas se guzra to unhon-ne kaha : Saleh Nabi aur Saleh betey, marhabaa! maine puchha : ye kon hain? kaha : ye Ibrahim hain. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey ibne- Hazam ne bataya ke Ibne-Abbas aur abu hiba Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir ( Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ( mujhey (aur ( uper le gaey yahan tak ke main aik unchi jagah ke samney namudaar hua, main uske andar se qalmon ki awaz sun raha tha. ibne- Hazam aur Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne meri ummat par pachaas namazein farz kin, mainye (hukm) lekar wapas hua yahan tak ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne puchha : aap ke rab ne aap ki ummat par kya farz kya hai? aap ne farmaya : maine jawab diya : un par pachaas namazein farz ki hain. Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ne mujh se kaha : apne rab ki taraf rujoo karein kyonke aap ki ummat uski taqat nahi rakheygii. farmaya : is par maine apne rab se rujoo kya to usne iska aik hissey mujh se kam kar diya. aap ne farmaya : main Musa (Alaihissalam) ki taraf wapas aaya aur unhein bataya . unhon-ne kaha : apne rab ki taraf rujoo karein kyonke aap ki ummat uski ( bhi) taqat nahi rakhey gii . aap ne farmaya : maine apne rab ki taraf rujoo kya to usne farmaya : ye panch hain aur yahi pachaas hain, mere yahan hukm badla nahi karta. aap ne farmaya : main lot kar Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ki taraf aaya to unhon-ne kaha : apne rab ki taraf rujoo karein. to maine kaha : (baar-baar sawal karne par) main apne rab se sharminda hua hun. aap ne farmaya : phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) mujhey lekar chaley yahan tak ke ham sidratul-muntaha par pahunch gaey to usko ( aisey aisey ( rangon ne dhanp liya ke main nahi janta wo kya they? phir mujhey jannat ke andar ley jaya gaya, usmein gunbad motiyon ke they aur uski mitti mushk thi."
416,"Saeed ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki) unhon-ne ghaaliban ye kaha (ke Malik bin Sasa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai (jo unki qaum ke fard they) ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Baitullah ke paas neend aur bedaarii ki darmyani kaifiyat mein tha, is beech mein aik kehney waley ko maine ye kehtey suna : teen aadmiyon mein se eik, 2 ke darmyan waalaa, phir mere paas aaey aur mujhey ley jaya gaya, iske baad mere paas soney ka tasht laya gaya jis mein zamzam ka pani tha, phir mera Sina khol diya gaya, falan se falan jagah tak (Qataada ne kaha : maine apne sath waley se puchha is se kya murad ley rahe hain? us ne kaha, pet ke nichey ke hissey tak) phir mera dil nikala gaya aur usey zam zam ke pani se dhoya gaya, phir usey dobara uski jagah par rakh diya gaya, phir usey eman w hikmat se bhar diya gaya. iske baad mere paas aik safaid janwar laya gaya jisey burraaq kaha jata hai, gadhey se bada aur khachchar se chhotaa, iska qadam wahan padta tha jahan uski nazar ki aakhiri had thi, mujhey is par Sawar kya gaya, phir ham chal padey yahan tak ke ham sabse nichley (pahley ( aasman tak pahunchey. Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ne darwaza kholney ke liye kaha : to puchha gaya : ye (darwaza khulwaney wala) kon hai? kaha : Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hun. kaha gaya : aap ke sath kon hai? kaha Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. puchha gaya : kya ( aasmanon par laney ke liye) unki taraf kisi ko bheja gaya tha? kaha : haan. to usne hamarey liye darwaza khol diya aur kaha : marhaba ! aap behtreen tareeqey se aaey ! farmaya : phir ham Adam (Alaihissalam) ke samney pahunch gaey. aagey poorey qissey samet hadis sunai aur bataya ke doosrey aasman par aap Esa aur Yahya ‌ (Alaihissalam) se, teesrey par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) se aur chauthey par Idrees (Alaihissalam) se, paanchwein par Harun (Alaihissalam) se miley, kaha : phir ham chaley yahan tak ke chhatey aasman tak pahunchey, main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas pahuncha aur unko salam kya, unhon-ne kaha : Saleh bhai aur Saleh Nabi ko marhaba , jab main unse aagey chala gaya to wo roney lagey, unhein awaz di gaee aapko kis baat ne rulaa diya ? kaha : aey mere rab! ye naujawaan hain jinko tu ney mere baad bheja hai inkii ummat ke log meri ummat ke logon se zyada tadaad mein jannat mein dakhil hongey. aap ne farmaya : phir ham chal padey yahan tak ke saatwen aasman tak pahunch gaey to main Ibrahim ke samney aaya. aur unhon-ne hadis mein kaha ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya ke unhon-ne char nehrein dekhiin, unke manba' se 2 zahiri nehrein nikalti hain aur 2 posheeda nahrein. maine kaha : aey Jibriil! ye nehrein kya hain? unhon-ne kaha : jo 2 posheeda hain to wo jannat ki nehrein hain aur 2 zahiri nehrein neel aur Furaat hain, phir baite-ma'moor mere samney buland kya gaya maine puchha : aey Jibreel ! ye kya hai? kaha : ye Baite-Mamoor hai, usmein har roz 70 hazaar Farishtey dakhil hotey hain, jab us se nikal jatey hain, to us (zamaaney) ke aakhir tak jo unke liye hai dobara usmein nahi aa saktey, phir mere paas 2 bartan laey gaey aik sharab ka aur doosra doodh ka, donon mere samney pesh kiye gaey to maine doodh ko pasand kya, is par kaha gaya, aap ne theek ( faisla ( kya, Allah Taala aap ke zariey se (sab ko) sahi (faisle) tak pahunchaaey, aap ki ummat ( bhi) fitrat par hai, phir mujh par har roz pachaas namazein farz ki gain . . . . . phir (pichhli ( hadis ke aakhir tak ka Sara waqia bayan kya."
417,"Hisham ne Qatada se hadis sunai, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( hamein Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Malik bin Sasa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . phir pichhli hadis ki tarah bayan kya aur is mein izafa kya : to mere paas hikmat aur eman se bharaa soney ka tasht laya gaya aur (meri ( gardan ke qareeb se pet ke patley hissey tak chira gaya, phir zam zam ke pani se dhoya gaya, phir usey hikmat aur eman se bhar diya gaya, (wazaahat kitaabul-eimaan ke Taaruf : main dekhiye)"
418,"Shoba ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu Aaliya se suna, wo keh rahe they : mujhey tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha ke betey , yani Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Israa ka waqia bayan kya aur farmaya : Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ gehunwey rang ke oonchey lambey they jaisey wo qabila shanu ke mardon mein se hon aur farmaya : Esa ‌ (Alaihissalam) gatthey huey jism ke miyaanaa qaamat they. aur aap ne dozakh ke darogha Malik aur dajjal ka bhi zikr farmaayaa."
419,"Sheban bin Abdur-Rehman ne Qatada ke hawale se pichhli sanad ke sath hadis sunai ke hamein tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha zaad (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Israa ki raat Moosaa-bin-Imraan (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra, wo gehunwey rang key, lambe qd ke gatthey huey jism ke insan they, jaisey qabila shanu ke mardon mein se hon aur maine Esa ibne-Maryam ‌(al) ko dekha, unka qad darmyaana, rang surkh w safaid aur sar ke baal seedhey they. (safar meraaj ke doran mein) un bahut si nishaniyon mein se jo aapko Allah Taala ne dikhain aapko 2 rukh ka darogha Malik aur dajjal bhi dikhaya gaya. aap un ( Musa ( se mulaqat ke barey mein shak mein na rahen. Sheban ne kaha : Qatada us aayat ki tafseer bataya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yaqinan Musa (Alaihissalam) se miley they. (ye mulaqat haqiqi thi, meraaj mahz khuwab na tha. ("
420,"Ahmad-bin-Hanbal aur Suraij-bin-Yoonus ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Daawood-bin-abii-Hind ne abu-Aaliya se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wadi azraq se guzrey to aap ne puchha : ye kon se wadi hai? logon ne kaha : ye wadi azraq hai. aap ne farmaya : mujhey aisa lagta hai ke main Musa (Alaihissalam) ko wadi ke mod se utartey dekh raha hun aur wo buland awaz se talbiya kehtey huey Allah ke samney ro rahe hain. phir aap har cheez ki ghaati par pahunchey to puchha : ye kon si ghaati hai? logon ne kaha : ye har cheez ki ghaati hai. aap ne farmaya : jaisey mein Yonus-bin-Matti ‌ (Alaihissalam) ko dekh raha hun jo surkh rang ki mazbut badan ontni par Sawar hain, unke jism par ooni jubba hai, unki ontni ki nakel khajoor ki chhaal ki hai aur wo labbaik keh rahe hain. ibne- hanbal ne apni hadis mein bayan kya ke Hushaim ne kaha : ( خلبة ( se ( لیف ( , yani khajoor ki chhaal murad hai."
421,"ibne-abi-Adi ne Dawud se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-aaliya se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka aur Madina ke darmyan raat ke waqt safar kya, ham aik wadi se guzrey to aap ne puchha : ye kon si wadi hai? logon ne kaha : wadi azraq hai. aap ne farmaya : ''jaisey main Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekh raha hun (aap ne Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ke rang aur baalon ke barey mein kuchh bataya jo Dawud ko yad nahi raha) Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ne apni do ungliyan apne (donon) kanon mein dali hui hain. is wadi se guzartey huey, buland awaz se talbiya (labbaik) kehtey ja rahe hain.''  Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir ham chaley yahan tak ke ham aik (aur ( ghaati par pahunchey to aap ne puchha : ye kon si ghaati hai? logon ne jawab diya : 'harshaa' ya 'lift' hai. to aap ne farmaya : ''jaisey main Yunus (Alaihissalam) ko surkh ontni par Sawar dekh raha hun, unke badan par ooni jubba hai, unki ontni ki nakel khajoor ki chhaal ki hai, wo talbiya kehtey huey is wadi se guzar rahe hain.''"
422,"Mujahid se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha : ham Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they, to logon ne dajjal ka tazkira chhed diya, (is par kisi ne) kaha : uski donon aankhon ke darmyan kaafir likha hoga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna ke aap ne ye kaha ho lekin aap ne ye farmaya : ''jahan tak Hazrat Ibrahim ka talluq hai to apne sahib (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ko dekh lo aur Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ gehunwey rang , gatthey huey jism ke mard hain, surkh oont par Sawar hain jiski nakel khajoor ki chhaal ki hai jaisey main unhein dekh raha hun ke jab wadi mein utrey hain to talbiya keh rahe hain.''"
423,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Rumhe ne Leis se unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''anbiyaae- kiram mere samney laey gaey. Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ phurteeley badan ke aadmi they, jaisey qabila shanu ke mardon mein se aik hon aur maine Esa-ibne-Maryam ‌(al) ko dekha, mujhey unke sath sabse qaribi mushabihat (similarity) Urwa-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) mein nazar aati hai, maine Ibrahim ko dekha, mujhey unke sath sabse qaribi mushabihat (similarity) tumharey sahib (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) mein nazar aai, yani khud aap. aur maine Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ko (insani shakl mein) dekha, maine unke sath sabse zyada mushabihat (similarity) Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) mein dekhi.'' ibne-Rumhe ki riwayat mein, 'dahiya-bin-khalifa' hai."
424,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab mujhey Israa karwaya gaya to main Musa (Alaihissalam) se mila (aap ne unka huliya bayan kya : mera khayal hai aap ne farmaya : ( wo aik muztarib ((beqaraar) kuchh lambey aur phurteeley) mard hain, lataktey baalon waale, jaisey wo qabila shanu ke mardon mein se hon. (aur aap ne farmaya : ( meri mulaqat Esa ‌(al) ‌ se hui (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka huliya bayan farmaya :) wo darmiyaney qad, surkh rang ke they maano abhi diimaas (yani Hammaam) se nikley hon. aur farmaya : main Ibrahim se mila, unki aulad mein se main unke sath sabse zyada un jaisa hun. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya) mere paas do bartan laey gaey, aik mein doodh aur doosrey mein sharab thi, mujh se kaha gaya : inmein se jo chaahein ley lein. maine doodh liya aur usey pi liya. (Jibril ‌(Alahissalam) ‌ ne) kaha ke aapko fitrat ki raah par chalaya gaya hai (ya aap ne fitrat ko pa liya hai) agar aap sharab pi letey to aap ki ummat rastey se hat jati.''"
425,"Malik (bin-Anas) ne Naafe se aur  unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine aik raat apne aapko Kaba ke paas dekha to maine aik gehunwey rang ka shakhs dekha, gehunwey rang ke logon mein se sabse khoobsurat tha jinhein tum dekhtey ho, unki lambi-lambi laten thin jo un laton mein se sabse khoobsurat thin jinhein tum dekhtey ho, unko kanghi ki hui thi aur unmein se pani ke qatrey tapak rahe they, do aadmiyon ka (ya do-aadmiyon ke kandhon ka ( sahara liya hua tha. wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they. maine puchha : ye kon hain? kaha gaya : ye Masih ibne-Maryam ‌ (Alaihissalam) hain. phir achcha maine aik aadmi dekha, uljhey huey ghungariyaley baalon waalaa, daain aankh kaani thi, jaisey angoor ka ubhraa hua daana ho, maine puchha : ye kon hai? to kaha gaya : ye Maseehe-dajjaal (jhootaa ya banawti maseeh) hai.''"
426,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din logon ke samney Masih dajjal ka tazkira kya aur farmaya : Allah tabarak w taala kaana nahi hai, khabardaar rehna ! Masih dajjal daain aankh se kaana hai jaisey angoor ka be noor daana ho. kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine raat apne aapko neend ke aalim mein Kaba ke paas dekha to maine aik gehunwey rang ke shakhs ko dekha, gehunwey rang ke logon mein sabse zyada khoobsurat tha jinhein tum dekhtey ho. iske sar ki latein kandhon ke darmyan tak latak rahi hain, baal kanghi kiye huey, sar se pani tapak raha hai aur apne donon hath 2 aadmiyon ke kandhon par rakhey huey aur un donon ke darmyan Baitullah sharif ka tawaaf kar raha hai, maine puchha : ye kon hain? to unhon ( jawab deney waalon) ne kaha : ye Masih ibne-Maryam ‌ (Alaihissalam) hain. maine unke peechhey aik aadmi dekha, iske baal uljhey huey ghungariyaaley they, daain aankh se kaanaa, jin logon ko maine dekha hai unmein wo sabse zyada (abdul-uzza) ibne-qatan ke mushabeh (similar) tha, wo apne donon hath 2 aadmiyon ke kandhon par rakhey huey Baitullah ka tawaaf kar raha tha, maine puchha : ye kon hai? unhon-ne kaha : ye jaali Masih hai."
427,"Hanzala ne Salim ke waastey se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine Kaba ke paas aik gehunwey rang ke , sar ke seedhey khuley baalon waley aadmi ko dekha jo apne donon hath 2 aadmiyon par rakhey huey tha, iske sar se pani bah raha tha (ya iske sar se pani ke qatrey gir rahe they) maine puchha : ye kon hain? to unhon ( jawab deney walon ( ne kaha : Esa ibne-Maryam ya maseeh-ibne-Maryam ( rawi ko yad na tha ke (donon mein se) kon sa lafz kaha tha) (Alaihissalam) aur unke peechhey maine aik aadmi dekha : surkh rang ka, sar ke baal ghungariyaaley aur daain aankh se kaanaa, maine jin logon ko dekha hai, unmein sabse zyada ibne-qatan iske mushabeh (similar) hai. maine puchha : ye kon hai? unhon-ne kaha : Masih dajjal hai."
428,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Quraish ne mujhey jhutlaayaa , main hijr ( Hateem ( mein khada ho gaya, Allah Taala ne baitul-maqdis mere samney achi tarah numaayaan kar diya aur maine usey dekh kar uski nishaniyan unko bataanii shuru kar dein."
429,"ibne-Shahab ne Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr se, unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jab main neend mein tha, maine apne aapko Kaba ka tawaaf kartey dekha aur dekha ke aik aadmi hai jiska rang gehunwa hai, baal seedhey hain, aur 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan hai, uska sar pani tapkaa raha hai (ya iska sar pani gira raha hai) maine puchha : ye kon hain? (jawaab deney walon ne) kaha : ye ibne-Maryam hain. phir main dekhta gaya to achcha aik surkh rang ka aadmi ( samney ( tha, jism ka bhari , sar ke baal ghungariyaaley , aankh kaani , jaisey ubhraa hua angoor ka daana ho, maine puchha : ye kon hai? unhon-ne kaha : dajjal hai, logon mein iske sath sabse zyada mushabeh (similar) ibne- qatan hai."
430,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apne aapko hijr ( Hateem ( mein dekha, Quraish mujh se mere raat ke safar ke barey mein sawal kar rahe they, unhon-ne mujh se baitul-maqdis ki kuchh chizon ke barey mein puchha jo maine ghaur se na dekhi thin, main is qadr pareshani mein mubtala hua ke kabhi itna pareshan na hua tha, aap ne farmaya : is par Allah Taala ne us ( baitul-maqdis ( utha kar mere samney kar diya main uski taraf dekh raha tha, wo mujh se jis cheez ke barey mein bhi poochhtey, main unhein bata deta aur maine khud ko anbiya ki aik jamat mein dekha to wahan Musa (Alaihissalam) they khadey ho kar Namaz padh rahe they, jaisey qabila shanu ke aadmiyon mein se aik hon aur Esa ibne-Maryam ( (Alaihissalam) ( ko dekha, wo khadey Namaz padh rahe they, logon mein sabse zyada unke mushabeh (similar) Urwa-bin-Masood Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) hain. aur) wahan ( Ibrahim bhi khadey Namaz padh rahe they, logon mein sabse zyada unke mushabeh (similar) tumharey sahib hain, aap ne apni zaat murad li, phir Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to maine un sab ki imamat ki. jab main Namaz se farigh hua to aik kehney waley ne kaha : aey Muhammad ! ye Malik hain, jahannam ke darogha, unhein salam kahey : main unki taraf mutwajjeh hua to unhon-ne pahal karke mujhey salam kya.'"
431,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin-masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko , Israa , karwaya gaya to aapko sidratul-muntaha tak ley jaya gaya, wo chhatey aasman par hai, ( jabke uski shakhein saatwen aasman ke uper hain) wo sab cheezein jinhein zamin se uper ley jaya jata hai, us tak pahunchti hain aur wahan se unhein ley liya jata hai aur wo cheezein jinhein uper se nichey laya jata hai, wahan pahunchti hain aur wahin se unhein wsool kar liya jata hai. Allah Taala ne farmaya : jab dhanp liya, sidra ( berii ke darakht ( ko jis cheez ne dhanpa. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : soney ke patingon ne aur kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko teen cheezein ata ki gain : panch namazein ata ki gain, sura Baqra ki aakhiri aayatein ata ki gain aur aap ki ummat ke) aisey ( logon ke (jinhon ne Allah ke sath shirk nahi kya ( jahannam mein pahunchaney waley (badey-badey) gunah maaf kar diye gaey."
432,"ibaad-bin-awaam ne kaha : hamein Shebani ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine zirr-bin-Hubaish se Allah Taala ke us farman ke barey mein sawal kya : wo 2 kamaan ke barabar faasley par they ya us se bhi zyada qareeb they. zar ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ko dekha, unke chh so par they."
433,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Shebani se hadis sunai, unhon-ne zar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne aayat : jhoot na dekha dil ne, jo dekha, padhi, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko dekha unke chh so par they."
434,"Shoba ne Sulaiman Shebani se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne zirr-bin-Hubaish se suna kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat, aap ne apne rab ki badi nishaniyan dekhiin, padhi, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko unki ( asl ( sura mein dekha, unke chh so par they."
435,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke) Allah ke farman (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey aik aur baar utartey huey dekha (ke barey mein kaha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko dekha
436,"Ata ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ( rab taala ko) dil se dekha."
437,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ziyaad-bin-Husain abu jahma se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu Aaliya se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne aayat : ""jhoot na dekha dil ne jo dekhaa,"" aur) وَلَقَدْ رَآهُ نَزْلَةً أُخْرَى (aur aap ne usey aik baar utartey huey dekha, (ke barey mein) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey (rab taala ko) apne dil se 2 baar dekha."
438,"(Wakee' ke bajaey) Hafs ibne-Ghiyaas ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu jahma (Ziyaad-bin-Husain) ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis sunai."
439,"Ismaaeel-bin-Ibraaheem ne Dawud se, unhon-ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein tek lagaey huey betha tha ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : abu Aaisha! (ye Masruq ki kunniyat hai) teen cheezein hain jisne unmein se koi baat kahi , us ne Allah Taala par bahut bada bohtan baandhaa, maine puchha : wo baatein kon si hain? unhon-ne farmaya : jisne ye guman kya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne rab ko dekha hai to usne Allah Taala par bahut bada bohtan baandhaa. unhon-ne kaha : main tek lagaey huey tha to (ye baat suntey hi ( seedha ho kar baith gaya aur kaha : Ummul-Momenin ! mujhey ( baat karne ka ( mauqa dijiye aur jaldi na keejiye, kya Allah Taala ne ye nahi kaha : be-shak unhon-ne usey roshan kinarey par dekha, , (usi tarah) , aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey aik baar utartey huey dekha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : main is ummat mein sabse pehli hun jisne iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya to aap ne farmaya : wo yaqinan Jibreel (Alaihissalam) hain, maien unhein us shakl mein, jis mein paida kiye gaey, 2 baar ke ilawa kabhi nahi dekha : aik baar maine unhein aasman se utartey dekha, unke wujood ki badaai ne aasman w zamin ke darmyan ki wusat ko bhar diya tha, phir Ummul-Momenin ne farmaya : kya tum ne Allah Taala ka farman nahi suna : aankhen usko dekh nahi saktin aur wo aankhon ko dekh leta hai aur wo baareek dekhnewaalaa har cheez ki khabar rakhney wala hai, aur kya tum ne ye nahi suna ke Allah Taala farmata hai : aur kisi Bishr mein taqat nahi ke Allah Taala us se kalam karey magar wahi ke zariey se ya pardey ki ot se ya wo kisi paigham laney waaley (farishtey) ko bhejey to wo uske hukm se jo chahey wahi karey bila shubah wo bahut buland aur daanaa hai. (ummul-momeneen ne) farmaya : jo shakhs ye samajhta hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah Taala ki kitab mein se kuchh chipa liya to usne Allah Taala par bahut bada bohtan baandhaa, kyonke Allah Taala farmata hai : aey rasool! pahuncha dijiye jo kuchh aap ke rab ki taraf se aap par nazil kya gaya aur agar (bil-farz) aap ne aisa na kya to aap ne uska paigham na pahunchaya (fareeza risalat ada na kya.) (aur) unhon-ne farmaya : aur jo shakhs ye kahey ke aap is baat ki khabar de detey hain ke kal kya hoga to usne Allah Taala par bahut bada jhoot baandhaa, kyonke Allah Taala farmata hai : (aey nabii!) farma diijiye! koi aik bhi jo aasmanon aur zamin mein hai, ghaib nahi janta, siwaey Allah ke."
440,"(Ismail ke bajaey) abdul-wahaab ne kaha : hamein Dawud ne isi tarah hadis sunai (Ismail bin Ibrahim) ibne-Ulaih se bayan ki aur is mein izafa kya ke (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi aik cheez ko jo aap par nazil ki gaee, chhipaney waley hotey , to aap ye aayat chipa letey : aur jab aap us shakhs se keh rahe they jis par Allah ne inaam farmaya aur aap ne ( bhi) inaam farmaya ke apni biwi ko apne paas rokey rakho aur Allah se daro aur aap apne ji mein wo har cheez chipa rahe they jisey Allah zahir karna chahta tha, aap logon (ke taan w tashnee (taaney aur kataksh) ( se dar rahe they, halanke Allah hi sabse zyada haqdaar hai ke aap us se darein."
441,"Ismail (bin abi Khalid ( ne (Aamir-bin-Sharaaheel) Shabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne rab ko dekha hai? unhon-ne kaha : Subhan-Allah ! jo tum ne kaha us se mere raungtey khadey ho gaey hain. phir (Ismail ne) poorey qissey samet hadis bayan ki lekin Dawud ki riwayat zyada kaamil aur lambi hai."
442,"( Saeed bin-Amr ( ibne-Ashwa ne Aamir ( Shabi ( se, unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : Allah Taala ke is qaul ka kya matlab hoga : phir wo qareeb hua aur utar aaya aur do kamaanon ke barabar ya us se kam faasley par tha, phir usne uske bandey ki taraf wahi ki jo wahi ki? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : wo to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) they, wo hamesha aap ke paas insanon ki shakl mein aatey they aur is baar wo aap ke paas apni asl shakl mein aaey aur unhon-ne aasman ke ufuq ko bhar diya."
443,"Yazeed-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-Shaqeeq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : kya aap ne apne rab ko dekha? aap ne jawab diya : wo noor hai, main usey kahan se dekhun !"
444,"Hisham aur Hammam donon ne 2 mukhtalif sanadon ke sath Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : agar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhta to aap se sawal karta. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum unse kis cheez ke barey mein sawal kartey ? Abdullah-bin Shaqiq ne kaha : main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal karta ke kya aap ne apne rab ko dekha hai. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine aap se ( yahi ( sawal kya tha to aap ne farmaya tha : maine noor dekha."
445,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Amr bin-Murra se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu Ubeda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey darmyan khadey ho kar panch baton par mushtamil khutba diya, farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala sota nahi aur na sona uske shayane-shan hai, wo mizan ke paldon ko jhukata aur uper uthata hai, raat ke aamaal din ke aamaal se pahley aur din ke aamaal raat se pahley uske samney pesh kiye jatey hain, uska parda noor hai (abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein noor ki jagah naar hai) agar wo us ( pardey ( ko khol de to uske chehrey ke anwaar jahan tak uski nigaah pahunchey uski makhlooq ko jalaa daalein. Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : Aamash se riwayat hai, ye nahi kaha : Aamash ne hamein hadis sunai."
446,"Aamash ke aik aur shagird Jarir ne usi (mazkura (uper zikr) (sanad se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey darmyan khadey ho kar char baton par mushtamil khutba diya. . . . . phir Jarir ne abu-Muawiya ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya aur , makhlooqat ko jalaa daaley, ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye aur kaha : uska parda noor hai."
447,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra ke hawale se abu Ubeda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aap ne hamarey darmyan khadey ho kar char baton par mushtamil khutba diya : Allah Taala sota nahi hai, sona uske laaiq nahi, meezaan ko uper uthata aur nichey karta hai. din ka amal raat ko aur raat ka amal din ko uske huzoor pesh kya jata hai."
448,"Abdullah-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : 2 jannatein chandi ki hain, unke bartan bhi aur jo kuchh unmein hai (wo bhii. (aur 2 jannatein soney ki hain unke bartan bhi aur jo kuchh unmein hai. jannate-adn mein logon ke aur unke rab ko dekhney ke darmyan uske chehrey par azmat w badai ki jo chadar hai us chadar ke siwa koi cheez nahi hogi."
449,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Sabit Bunani se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Laila se, unhon-ne Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jab jannat waley jannat mein dakhil ho jaaeinge, (us waqt) Allah tabarak w taala farmaeyga tumhen koi cheez chahiye jo tumhen mazeed ata karun? wo jawab dengey : kya tu ney hamarey chehrey roshan nahi kiye ! kya tu ney hamein jannat mein dakhil nahi kya aur dozakh se nijat nahi di ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : chunanche is par Allah Taala parda utha dega to unhein koi cheez aisi ata nahi hui hogi jo unhein apne rab azz-w-jall ke deedaar se zyada mahboob ho"
450,(Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Mehdii ke bajaey) Yazid-bin-Harun ne Hammaad-bin-Salma se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. usmein ye izafa hai : phir aap ne ye aayat padhi : ( لِلَّذِينَ أَحْسَنُوا الْحُسْنَى وَزِيَادَةٌ ( jin logon ne bhalai ki unke liye khoobsurat ( jazaa (aur mazeed ( deedaar ilahi ( hai.
451,"Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mere walid ne hamein ibne-Shahab Zohri se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi se riwayat ki ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya : kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke Allah ke rasool! kya ham qiyamat ke din apne rab ko dekhengey ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhen poorey chaand ki raat ko chaand dekhney mein koi diqqat mehsus hoti hai? logon ne kaha : nahi, aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : jab badal beech mein na hon to kya suraj dekhney main tumhen koi diqqat mehsus hoti hai? sahaba ne kaha : nahi, aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : tum usey ( Allah ko) isi tarah dekhogey , Allah Taala qiyamat ke din tamam logon ko jama karega, phir farmaeyga : jo shakhs jis cheez ki ibadat karta tha usi ke peechhey chala jaey, chunanche jo suraj ki puja karta tha wo suraj ke peechhey chala jaeyga, jo chaand ki parastish karta tha wo uske peechhey chala jaeyga aur jo taghuton ( shaitanon , buton wghaira) ki puja karta tha wo taghuton ke peechhey chala jaeyga aur sirf ye ummat , apne munaafiqon samet , baqi reh jaeygi. is par Allah tabarak w taala unke paas apni is sura se mukhtalif suraton mein aayega jis ko wo pehchan saktey hongey, phir farmaeyga : main tumhara rab hun. wo kahengey : ham tujh se Allah ki panah chahtey hain, ham usi jagah thahrey raheingey yahan tak ke hamara rab hamarey paas aa jaey, jab hamara rab aayega ham usey pehchan lengey. iske baad Allah Taala unke paas is sura mein aayega jis mein wo usko pehchantey hongey aur farmaeyga : main tumhara parwardigar hun. wo kahengey, to ( hi ( hamara rab hai aur uske sath ho jaaeinge, phir ( pul ( siraat jahannam ke darmyani hissey par rakh diya jaeyga to main aur meri ummat sabse pahley hongey jo us se guzrengey. us din rasulon ke siwa koi bol na sakega aur rasulon ki pukar (bhi) us din yahi hogi : aey Allaah! salamat rakh, salamat rakh aur dozakh mein Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah mudey huey saron waley aankdey hongey, kya tum ne Sadan dekha hai? sahaba ne jawab diya : ji haan , aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : wo ( aankdey ( Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah ke hongey lekin wo kitney badey hongey usko Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta, wo logon ko unke aamaal ki buniyad par uchak lengey. unmein se kuchh halaak kiye janey waley hongey, yani apne amal ki wjah se. aur unmein se kuchh aisey hongey jinhein nijat diye janey tak aamaal ka badla chukana hoga. yahan tak ke jab Allah Taala bandon ke darmyan faisley se farigh ho jaeyga aur irada farmaeyga ke apni rehmat se, jin dozkhiyon ko chahta hai, aag se nikaley to wo farishton ko hukm dega ke un logon mein se jo Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi thehratey they, laa-Ilaah illallaah kehney walon mein se jin par Allah Taala rehmat karna chaahega unhein aag se nikal lein. Farishtey unko aag mein pehchan lengey. wo unhein sajdon ke nishan se pahchaanengey. aag sajdey ke nishanat ke siwaa, Adam ke betey (ki har cheez ( ko kha jaeygi. (kyonke) Allah Taala ne aag par sajdey ke nishanat ko khana haram kar diya hai, chunanche wo us haal mein aag se nikaley jaeinge ke jal kar koila ban gaey hongey, un par aabe-hayaat daala jaeyga to wo iske zariey se is tarah ug aaeingey, jaisey sailaab ki laai hui mitti mein ghaas ka beej phoot kar ug aata hai. phir Allah Taala apne bandon ke darmyan faisley se farigh ho jaeyga bas aik shakhs baqi hoga, jisne aag ki taraf munh kya hua hoga, yahi aadmi , tamam ahle-jannat mein se, jannat mein dakhil honey wala aakhiri shakhs hoga. wo arz karega : mere rab! mera chehra aag se pher de kyonke uski bdboo ne meri saanson mein zahar bhar diya hai aur uski tapish ne mujhey jalaa daala hai, chunanche jab tak Allah ko manzoor hoga, wo Allah ko pukarta rahega phir Allah tabarak w taala farmaeyga : kya aisa hoga ke agar main tumharey sath ye (husne-sulook) kar dun to tum kuchh aur maangna shuru kar doge? wo arz karega : main tujh se aur kuchh nahi maangonga. wo apne rab azz-w-jall ko jo ahad w paiman wo ( lena ( chaahega, dega, to Allah uska chehra dozakh se pher degaa jab wo jannat ki taraf rukh karega aur usey dekhega to jitni der Allah chaahega ke wo chup rahe (utni der) chup rahega, phir kahega : mere rab! mujhey jannat ke darwazey tak aagey kar de, Allah Taala us se kahega : kya tum ne ahad w paiman nahi diye they ke jo kuchh maine tumhen ata kar diya hai uske siwa mujh se kuchh aur nahi maangogey? tujh par aafsos hai! Adam ke betey ! tum kis qadr ahad todneywaaley ho! wo kahega : aey mere rab! aur Allah se dua karta rahega yahan tak ke Allah us se kahega : kya aisa hoga ke agar maine tumhen ye ata kar diya to iske baad to aur kuchh maangna shuru kar dega? wo kahega : teri izzat ki qism ! (aur kuchh ( nahi ( mangunga) wo apne rab ko, jo Allah chaahega, ahad w paiman dega, is par Allah usey jannat ke darwazey tak aagey kar dega , phir jab wo jannat ke darwazey par khada hoga to jannat uske samney khul jaeygi. usmein jo khair aur suroor hai wo usko (apni aankhon se) dekhega . to jab tak Allah ko manzoor hoga wo khamosh rahega , phir kahega : mere rab! mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar de, to Allah Taala us se kahega, kya tu ney pukhta ahad w paiman na kiye they ke jo kuchh tujhey de diya gaya hai uske siwa aur kuchh nahi maangeyga? ibne-Aadam tujh par afsos ! to kitna bada wada khilaafii karneywaalaa hai. wo kahega : aey mere rab! main teri makhlooq ka sabse zyada bad-naseeb shakhs na banoon, wo Allah Taala ko pukarta rahega yahan tak ke izzat aur jalaal wala Allah is par hansega aur jab Allah Taala hansega (to) farmaeyga : jannat mein dakhil ho jaa. jab wo usmein dakhil ho jaeyga to Allah Taala farmaeyga, tamanna kar ! to wo apne rab se maangey ga aur tamanna karega yahan tak ke Allah usey yad dilaaeyga, falan cheez ( maang ( falan cheez ( maang ( yahan tak ke jab uski tamam aarzuein khatm ho jaeyngi to Allah Taala farmaeyga : ye sab kuchh tera hai aur uske sath itna hi aur bhii. Ata-bin-Yazeed ne kaha ke Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath maujood they, unhon-ne unki kisi baat ki tardeed na ki lekin jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bayan kya ke Allah Taala us aadmi se farmaeyga : ye sab kuchh tera hua aur uske sath itna hi aur bhi, to abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : abu-Huraira! iske sath us se das guna (aur bhi), Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey to aap ka yahi farman yad hai : ye sab kuchh tera hai aur uske sath itna hi aur bhii. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun kar aap ka ye farman yad rakha hai : ye sab tera hua aur us se das guna aur bhii. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye jannat mein dakhil honey wala sabse aakhiri shakhs hoga."
452,"Shuaib ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : ata aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne mujhey khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne un donon ko khabar di ke logon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya ham qiyamat ke din apne rab ko dekhengey ? . . . . . . aagey Ibrahim bin Sad ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
453,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( sun kar) bayan kin, phir (Hammaam ne) bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein ye hadis bhi thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi ki jannat mein kam se kam jagah ye hogi ke Allah Taala us se farmaeyga : tamanna kar. to wo tamanna karega, phir tamanna karega, Allah us se poochhega : kya tum tamanna kar chukey? wo kahega : haan. Allah Taala farmaeyga : wo sab kuchh tera hua jiski tu ney tamanna ki aur us ke sath itna hi (aur bhi.)"
454,"Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein (aap se) kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya ham qiyamat ke din apne rab ko dekhengey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. ( phir ( farmaya : kya do-pahar ke waqt jab aasmaan mein badal na hon, suraj ko dekhtey huey tumhen koi zahmat hoti hai? aur kya poorey chaand ki raat ko jab aasman saaf ho aur badal na hon to chaand ko dekhney mein koi takleef mehsus kartey ho?  sahaba ne kaha : Allah ke rasool nahin! farmaya : qiyamat ke roz Allah tabarak w taala ko dekhney mein us se zyada diqqat na hogi jitni in donon mein se kisi aik ko dekhney mein hoti hai. jab qiyamat ka din hoga, aik elaan karne wala ye elaan karega : har ummat uske peechhey chaley jiski wo ibadat kya karti thi. koi aadmi aisa na bachega jo Allah ke siwa buton aur pattharon ko pujtaa tha magar wo aag mein ja gireyga yahan tak ke jab unke siwa jo Allah ki ibadat kartey they, wo nek hon ya bad, aur ahle-kitab ke baqiya ( baad ke dor ke) logon ke siwa koi na bachega to yahood ko bulaya jaeyga aur unse kaha jaeyga : tum kis ki ibadat kartey they? wo kahengey : ham Allah ke betey Uzer ki ibadat kartey they, to kaha jaeyga : tum ne jhoot bola, Allah Taala ne na koi biwi banai na betaa , to ( ab ( kya chahtey ho? kahengey : parwardigaar! hamein piyaas lagi hai hamein pani pilaa. to unko ishara kya jaeyga ke tum pani (ke ghaat) par kyon nahi jaatey? phir unhein ikattha karke aag ki taraf haank diya jaeyga wo saraab ki tarah hogi, iska aik hissey doosrey hissey ko tod raha hoga aur wo sab (eik doosrey ke peechhey) aag mein girtey chaley jaaeinge, phir nasara ko bulaya jaeyga aur unse kaha jaeyga : tum kis ki ibadat kartey they? wo kahengey : ham Allah ke betey Masih ko poojtey they. unse kaha jaeyga : tum jhoot boltey ho, Allah ne na koi biwi banai na koi betaa , phir unse kaha jaeyga ! ( ab ( tum kya chahtey ho? wo kahengey : ham piyaasey hain hamarey parwardigar ! hamein pani pilaa, aap ne farmaya : unko ishara kya jaeyga, tum pani (ke ghaat ( par kyon nahi jaatey? phir unhein ikattha karke jahannam ki taraf haankaa jaeyga wo saraab ki tarah hogi (aur ( iska aik hissey (shiddate-ishtiaa'l se) doosrey ko tod raha hoga, wo (eik doosrey ke peechhey) aag mein girtey chaley jaaeinge, yahan tak ke jab unke siwa koi na bachcheyga jo Allah Taala (hii) ki ibadat kartey they, nek hon ya bad, (to) sab jahaanon ka rab sub'haanahu w taala unki dekhi hui sura se kam tar (ya mukhtalif) sura mein aayega (aur ( farmaeyga : tum kis cheez ka intizar kar rahe ho? har ummat iske peechhey ja rahi hai jiski wo ibadat karti thi, wo (saamney zahir honey wali sura ke bajaey apne parwardigar ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar) iltijaa karengey : aey hamarey rab! ham duniya mein sab logon se, jitni shadeed bhi hamein unki zarurat thi, alag ho gaey, ham ne unka sath na diya. wo kahega : main tumhara rab hun, wo kahengey : ham tum se Allah ki panah mein aatey hain, ham Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraaeingey (2 ya teen baar yahi kahengey) yahan tak ke unmein kuchh log badalney ke qareeb hongey to wo farmaeyga : kya tumharey aur uske darmyan koi nishani ( tay ( hai jis se tum usko pehchan sako ? wo jawab dengey : haan ! to pindlii zahir kar di jaeygi phir koi aisa shakhs na bacheyga jo apne dil se Allah ko sajda karta tha magar Allah usey sajdey ki ijazat dega aur koi aisa na bacheyga jo jaan bachaney ke liye ya dikhawey ke liye sajda karta tha magar Allah Taala uski pusht ko aik hi mohra bana dega, jab bhi wo sajda karna chaahega apni guddi ke bal gir padega, phir wo (sajdey se) apne sar uthaaeingey aur Allah Taala apni is sura mein aa chuka hoga jis mein unhon-ne usko (sab se) pehli martaba dekha tha aur wo farmaeyga : main tumhara rab hun. to wo kahengey : ( haan ( tu hi hamara rab hai, phir jahannam par pul laga diya jaeyga aur sifarish ka darwaza khul jaeyga, aur (sab rasool ( keh rahe hongey : aey Allah ! salamat rakh, salamat rakh. puchha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool! jasar ( pul ( kya hai? aap ne farmaya : bahut phislnii, dagmagaa dene wali jagah hai, usmein uchak leney waley aankdey aur kai-kai nokon waley kundey hain aur is mein kaantey daar paudey hain jo Najad mein hotey hain jinhein Sadan kaha jata hai. to momin aankh ki jhapak ki tarah aur bijli ki tarah aur hawa ki tarah aur parindon ki tarah aur tez raftaar ghodon aur sawaariyon ki tarah guzar jaaeinge, koi sahi Salim nijat paaney wala hoga aur koi zakhmi ho kar chhod diya janey wala aur kuchh jahannam ki aag mein teh-b-teh laga diye janey waale, yahan tak ke jab momin aag se khulaasii pa leingey to us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! tum mein se koi pooraa-pooraa haq wsool karne (ke muaamley) mein is qadr Allah se mannat aur aah wazaarii nahi karta jis qadr qiyamat ke din momin apne un musalman bhaiyon ke barey mein karengey jo aag mein hongey. wo kahengey : aey hamarey rab! wo hamarey sath rozey rakhtey, namazein padhtey aur Haj kartey they. to unse kaha jaeyga : tum jinko pehchantey ho unhein nikal lo, unki sooratein aag par haram kar di gaee hongi . to wo bahut se logon ko nikal laaengey jinki aadhi pindliyon tak ya ghutnon tak aag pakad chuki hogi, phir wo kahengey : hamarey rab! jinhein nikalney ka tu ney hukm diya tha unmein se koi dozakh mein nahi raha. to wo farmaeyga : wapas jao, jiske dil mein Dinar bhar khair (eman ( paao usko nikal lao to wo badi taadaad ko nikal laaengey , phir kahengey : hamarey rab! jinhein nikalney ka tu ney hukm diya tha unmein se kisi ko ham ne dozakh mein nahi chhoda . wo phir farmaeyga : wapas jao, jiske dil mein aadhey Dinar ke barabar khair paao usko nikal lao to wo ( phir se) badi taadaad ko nikal laaengey , phir wo kahengey , hamarey rab! jinhein nikalney ka tu ney hukm diya tha ham ne unmein kisi ko dozakh mein nahi chhoda . wo phir farmaeyga : wapas jao, jiske dil mein aik zarrey ke barabar khair paao usko nikal lao to wo Kasir taadaad ko nikal laaengey , phir wo kahengey : hamarey rab! ham ne usmein kisi saahibe-khair ko nahi chhodaa. (eman aik zarrey ke barabar bhi ho sakta hai.) Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : agar tum is hadis mein meri tasdeeq nahi kartey to chaho to ye aayat padh lo : be-shak Allah aik zarra barabar zulm nahi karta aur agar koi neki ho to usko badhata hai aur apni taraf se ajre-azeem deta hai. phir Allah Taala farmaeyga : farishton ne sifarish ki, anbiya ne sifarish ki, aur momineen ne sifarish ki, ab ar-hamur-raahemeen ke siwa koi baqi nahi raha to wo aag se aik muththii bharey ga aur aisey logon ko usmein se nikal lega jinhoney kabhi bhalai ka koi kaam nahi kya tha aur wo (jal kar) koila ho chukey hongey, phir wo unhein jannat ke dahaanon par (bahney waali) aik nehar mein daal dega jisko nahare-hayaat kaha jata hai, wo is tarah (ug kar) nikal aaeingey jis tarah ( ghaas ka ( chhota sa beej sailaab ke khaso-khaashaak mein phoot'taa hai, kya tum usey dekhtey nahi ho ke kabhi wo patthar ke sath laga hota hai aur kabhi darakht ke saath, jo suraj ke rukh par hota hai wo zard aur sabz hota hai aur jo saaey mein hota hai wo safaid hota hai? sahaba ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aisa lagta hai ke aap jangal mein janwar charaayaa kartey they? aap ne farmaya : to wo log ( nehar se) motiyon ki tarah niklengey, unki gardanon mein mohrein hongii, ahle-jannat (azaan ke baad) unko (is tarah) pahchaanengey ke ye log Allah Taala ke aazad kiye huey hain, jinko Allah Taala ne baghair kisi amal ke jo unhon-ne kya ho aur baghair kisi neki ke jo unhon-ne aagey bheji ho, jannat mein dakhil kya hai. phir wo farmaeyga : jannat mein dakhil ho jao aur jo tumhen nazar aaey wo tumhara hai, is par wo kahengey : aey hamarey rab! tu ney hamein wo kuchh diya hai jo jahan walon mein se kisi ko nahi diya. to wo farmaeyga : tumharey liye mere paas is se badh kar bhi hai. wo kahengey : aey hamarey rab is se badh kar kon si cheez (ho saktii) hai? to wo farmaeyga : meri razaa, ke iske baad main tum se kabhi naraz na hoonga."
455,"Imam Muslim ne kaha : maine shafaat ke barey mein ye hadis Eisaa-bin-Hammaad zughba Misri ke samney padhi aur unse kaha : (kya) ye hadis main aap ke hawale se bayan karun ke aap ne usey Lais-bin-Sad se suna hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan! (Imam Muslim ne kaha :) maine Eisaa-bin-Hammaad se kaha : aapko Lais-bin-Sad ne Khalid-bin Yazeed se khabar di, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-abi-Hilal se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se, unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya ham apne rab ko dekh sakengey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab chamaktaa hua be-abr (baadal) din ho to kya tumhen suraj ko dekhney mein koi zahmat hoti hai? ham ne kaha : nahi. (Imam Muslim ne kaha : ( main hadis padhta gaya yahan tak ke wo khatm ho gaee aur (Saeed-bin-abii-Hilaal ki) ye hadis Hafs-bin-Maisra ki) mazkura (uper zikr) ( hadis ki tarah hai. unhon ( Saeed ( ne ( hadis ke alfaz ( baghair kisi amal ke jo unhon-ne kya aur baghair kisi qadam ke jo unhon-ne aagey badhaya , ke baad ye izafa kya : chunanche unse kaha jaeyga : tumharey liye wo sab kuchh hai jo tum ne dekha hai aur uske sath itna hi aur. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke pul baal se zyada baareek aur talwaar ki dhaar se zyada tez hoga. Leis ki riwayat mein ye alfaz : to wo kahengey : aey hamarey rab! tu ney hamein wo kuchh diya hai jo jahan walon mein se kisi ko nahi diya, aur uske baad ke alfaz nahi hain. chunanche Eisaa-bin-Hammaad ne iska iqrar kya (ke unhon-ne uper bayan ki gaee sanad ke sath Leis se ye hadis suni.)"
456,Zaid-bin-Aslam ke aik aur shagird Hishaam-bin-Sad ne bhi un donon (hafs aur Saeed) ki mazkura (uper zikr) sanadon ke sath Hafs-bin-Maisra jaisi hadis (454) aakhir tak bayan ki aur kuchh kami w zyadti bhi ki.
457,"Malik-bin-Anas ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne mujhey Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ahle-jannat mein se jisey chaahega apni rehmat se jannat mein dakhil karega, aur dozkhiyon ko dozakh mein daalega , phir farmaeyga : dekho (aur ( jiske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman paogey usko nikal lo, (aisey) log us haal mein nikaley jaaeynge ke wo jal-bhun kar koila ho chukey hongey. unhein zindagi ya shadabi ki nehar mein daala jaeyga to usmein wo is tarah ugeingey jis tarah ghaas-phoons ka chhota sa beej sailaab ke kinarey mein ugtaa hai tum ne usey dekha nahi kis tarah zard, liptaa hua, ugtaa hai?"
458,Wuhaib aur Khalid donon ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki. usmein hai : unhein aik nehar mein daala jaeyga jisey ( الحیاۃ ( kaha jata hai. aur donon ne (pichhli riwayat ki tarah us lafz mein) koi shak nahi kya. Khalid ki riwayat main ( aagey ( ye hai : jis tarah koodaa-karkat (sailaab mein beh kar aaney waley mukhtalif qism ke beej) sailaab ke kinarey ugtey hain. aur Wuhaib ki riwayat mein hai : jis tarah chhota sa beej siyah gaarey mein ya sailaab ke khas w khaashaak mein ugtaa hai.
459,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne abu-Muslima se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jahan tak dozakh walon ki baat hai to wo log jo ( hamesha ke liye) iske baashindey hain na to usmein marengey aur na jiengey . lekin tum ( eman walon ( mein se jin logon ko gunahon ke badley (ya aap ne farmaya : khataaon ki bina par) aag ki museebat laagu hogi to Allah Taala un par aik tarah ki maut taarii kar dega yahan tak ke jab wo koila ho jaeinge to sifarish ki ijazat de di jaeygi, phir unhein garoh-dar-garoh laya jaeyga aur unhein jannat ki nehron par phaila diya jaeyga phir kaha jaeyga : aey ahale-jannat! un par pani dalo to usmein beej ki tarah ug aaeingey jo sailaab ke khas w khaashaak mein hota hai. logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : aisa lagta hai jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sehraaii aabadi mein rahe hain."
460,"(Bishr ke bajaey) Shoba ne abu-Muslama se hadis sunai kaha, maine abu-Nazara se suna, (unhon-ne) Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi jaisi riwayat main 'sailaab ke khaso-khashak mein' (ke jumley) tak bayan ki aur baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya."
461,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Ubeda se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak main usey janta hun jo dozakh walon mein sabse aakhir mein us se niklega aur jannat walon mein se sabse aakhir mein jannat mein jaeyga wo aisa aadmi hai jo hathon aur pet ke bal ghisat'ta hua aag se niklega . Allah tabarak w taala us se farmaeyga : ja jannat mein dakhil ho jaa. wo jannat mein aayega to usey ye khayal dilaya jaeyga ke jannat bhari hui hai. wo wapas aa kar arz karega : aey mere rab! mujhey to wo bhari hui mili hai. Allah tabarak w taala us se farmaeyga : ja jannat mein dakhil ho jaa. aap ne farmaya : wo ( dobara ( jaeyga to usey yahi lageyga ke wo bhari hui hai. wo wapas aa kar) phir ( kahega : aey mere rab! maine to usey bhari hui paya hai. Allah Taala us se farmaeyga : ja jannat mein dakhil ho jaa. terey liye (wahan) poori duniya ke barabar aur us se das guna zyada jagah hai (ya terey liye duniya se das guna zyada jagah hai) aap ne farmaya : wo shakhs kahega : kya to mere sath mazah karta hai (ya meri hansi udaataa hai) halanke tu hi badshah hai? Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap hans diye yahan tak ke aap ke pichhley daant zahir ho gaey. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : chunanche ye kaha jata tha ke ye shakhs sabse kam martaba jannati hoga."
462,"(Mansoor ke bajaey) Aamash ne Ibrahim se, pichhli sanad ke sath , Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main yaqinan dozakh walon mein se sabse aakhir mein nikalney waley ko janta hun. wo pet ke bal ghisat'ta hua usmein se niklega. us se kaha jaeyga : chal jannat mein dakhil ho jaa. aap ne farmaya : wo jaeyga aur jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyga to wo dekhega ke sab manzilein log sanbhaal chukey hain. us se kaha jaeyga : kya tujhey wo zamana yad hai jis main to tha? wo kahega : haan! to us se kaha jaeyga : tamanna kar, wo tamanna karega to usey kaha jaeyga : tum ne jo tamanna ki wo tumhari hai aur poori duniya se das guna mazeed bhi (tumhara hai) wo kahega : to badshah ho kar mere sath mazaq karta hai? (Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap hansey yahan tak ke aap ke pichhley daant nazar aaney lagey."
463,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein sabse aakhir mein wo aadmi dakhil hoga jo kabhi chalega , kabhi chehrey ke bal gireyga aur kabhi aag usey jhulsa degi. jab wo aag se nikal aaeyga to palat kar usko dekhega aur kahega : badi barkat wali hai wo zaat jisne mujhey tujh se nijat de di. Allah ne mujhey aisi cheez ata farma di jo usney aglon pichhlon mein se kisi ko ata nahi farmai . usey bulandi par aik darakht dikhaya jaeyga to wo kahega : aey mere rab mujhey us darakht ke qareeb kar de taake main uske saaey mein dhoop se nijat hasil karun aur uske pani se piyaas bujhaun is par izzat aur jalaal wala Allah farmaeyga : aey ibne-Aadam! ho sakta hai ke main tumhen ye darakht de dun to tum mujh se iske siwa kuchh aur maango. wo kahega : nahi, aey mere rab! aur Allah ke sath ahad karega ke wo us se aur kuchh na mangega. uska parwardigar uska uzr qabool kar lega kyonke wo aisi cheez dekh raha hoga jis par wo sabr kar hi nahi sakta. to Allah Taala usey us ( darakht (ke qareeb kar dega aur wo iske saaey mein dhoop se mehfooz ho jaeyga aur iska pani piyega, phir usey uper aik aur darakht dikhaya jaaeygaa jo pahley darakht se zyada khoobsurat hoga to wo kahega : aey mere rab! mujhey us darakht ke qareeb kar de taake main iske pani se sairaab hun aur uske saaey mein aaraam karun mein tujh se iske siwa kuchh nahi mangunga. Allah Taala farmaeyga : aey Adam ke betey! kya tum ne mujh se wada na kya tha ke tum mujh se kuchh aur nahi mangogey? aur farmaeyga : mujhey lagta hai agar main tumhen uske qareeb kar dun to tum mujh se kuchh aur bhi maangogey. wo Allah Taala se wada karega ke wo iske ilawa aur kuchh nahi mangega, uska rab taala uska uzr qabool kar lega, kyonke wo aisi cheez dekh raha hoga jiske samney us se sabr nahi ho sakta. is par Allah usey us darakht ke qareeb kar dega. wo uske saaey ke nichey aa jaeyga aur uske pani se piyaas bujhaega aur phir aik darakht jannat ke darwazey ke paas dikhaya jaeyga jo pahley donon darakhton se zyada khoobsurat hoga to wo arz karega : aey mere rab! mujhey us darakht ke qareeb kar de taake main iske saaey se fayda uthaun aur uske pani se piyaas bujhaun , main tum se aur kuchh nahi mangunga. Allah Taala farmaeyga : aey Adam ke betey ! kya tum ne mere sath wada nahi kya tha ke aur kuchh nahi mangogey? wo kahega : kyon nahi mere rab! ( wada kya tha) bas yahi , iske ilawa aur kuchh nahi mangunga. uska rab uska uzr qabool kar lega kyonke wo aisi cheez dekh raha hoga jis par wo sabr kar hi nahi sakta. to wo us shakhs ko us ( darakht (ke qareeb kar dega to wo ahle-jannat ki aawazein sunega. wo kahega : aey mere rab! mujhey usmein dakhil kar de, Allah Taala farmaeyga : aey Adam ke betey ! wo kya cheez hai jo tujhey razi karke hamarey darmyan sawalat ka silsile khatm kar de? kya tum us se razi ho jaogey ke main tumhen saari duniya aur uske barabar aur de dun? wo kahega : aey mere rab! kya to meri hansi udata hai jabke to sarey jahaanon ka rab hai. is par ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hans padey aur kaha : kya tum mujh se ye nahi poochhogey ke main kyon hansa? saamein ne puchha : aap kyon hansey ? kaha : isi tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansey they, to sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha tha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap kyon hans rahe hain? aap ne farmaya : rabbul-aalameen ke hans padney par, jab usne kaha ke to sarey jahanon ka rab hai, meri hansi udata hai? Allah farmaeyga : main teri hansi nahi udata balke main jo chahun kar sakta hun."
464,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ahle-jannat mein sabse kam darjey par wo aadmi hoga jiske chehrey ko Allah Taala dozakh ki taraf se hata kar jannat ki taraf kar dega aur usko aik saaya daar darakht ki sura dikhai jaeygi, wo kahega : aey mere rab! mujhey us darakht ke qareeb kar de taake main uske saaey mein ho jaun. . . . . aagey unhon-ne ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah riwayat bayan ki lekin ye alfaz zikr nahi kiye : Allah Taala farmaeyga : aey Adam ke betey ! kya cheez hai jo tujhey razi karke hamarey darmyan sawalat ka silsile khatm kar de. . . . . albatta unhon-ne usmein ye izafa kya : aur Allah Taala usey yad dilata jaeyga : falan cheez maang , falan cheez talab kar aur jab uski aarzuein khatm ho jaeyngi to Allah Taala farmaeyga : ye sab kuchh tumhara hai aur us se das guna aur bhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir wo apne ghar mein dakhil hoga aur khoobsurat aankhon wali hooron mein se uski 2 beeviyan uske paas aaeingi aur kahengi : Allah ki hamd jisne tumhen hamarey liye zinda kya aur hamein tumharey liye zindagi di. aap ne farmaya : to wo kahega : jo kuchh mujhey inayat kya gaya hai aisa kisi ko nahi diya gaya."
465,"hamein Saeed-bin-Umar w ash-asii ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Mutarrif aur) Abdul-Malik ( ibne-Abjar se, unhon-ne Shabi se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se, insha-Allah ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki hui ( riwayat ke taur par suna, isi ke sath ibne-abii-Umar ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Mutarrif aur abdul-Malik-bin-Saeed se aur un donon ne Shabi se sun kar hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se khabar di, kaha : maine unse member par suna, wo is baat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf mansub kar rahe they, neez Bishr-bin-hakam ne mujh se bayan kya (riwaayat ke alfaz unhein ke hain) Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Mutarrif aur ibne-Abjar ne hadis bayan ki, un donon ne Shabi se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Mughira-bin-Shoba se suna, wo member par logon ko (ye ( hadis suna rahe they. Sufiyan ne kaha : un donon ( ustaadon ( mein se aik ( mera khayal hai ibne-Abjar ( ne is riwayat ko marfooan (jisey sahabi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ho ( bayan kya, aap ne farmaya : Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ne rab taala se puchha : jannat mein sabse kam darjey ka (jannatii) kon hoga? Allah Taala ne farmaya : wo (aisaa) aadmi hoga jo tamam ahle-jannat ko jannat mein bhej diye janey ke baad aayega to us se kaha jaeyga : jannat mein dakhil ho ja , wo kahega : mere rab! kaisey? log apni apni manzilon mein thahar chukey hain aur jo lena tha sab kuchh ley chukey hain. to us se kaha jaeyga : kya tum is par razi ho jaogey ke tumhen duniya ke baadshaahon mein se kisi badshah ke mulk ke barabar mil jaaey? wo kahega : mere rab! main razi hun, Allah farmaeyga : wo (mulk) tumhara huaa, phir itna aur, phir itna aur, phir itna aur, phir itna aur, phir itna aur, paanchwiin baar wo aadmi (be ikhtiyaar) kahega : mere rab! main razi ho gaya. izzat aur jalaal wala Allah farmaeyga : ye (sab bhi) tera aur us se das guna mazeed bhi tera , aur wo sab kuchh bhi tera jo tera dil chahey aur jo teri aankhon ko bhaaey . wo kahega : aey mere rab! mein razi hun, phir ( Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ne) kaha : parwardigar ! to wo jo sabse oonchey darjey ka hai? Allah Taala ne farmaya : yahi log hain jo meri murad hain, unki izzat w karaamat ko maine apne hathon se parwaan chadhaayaa aur is par mohar laga di (jiske liye chaha mehfooz kar liyaa.) (izzat ka ( wo (maqaam) na kisi aankh ne dekha aur na kisi kaan ne suna aur na kisi insan ke dil mein iska khayal tak guzraa. farmaya : iska misdaaq izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki kitab mein maujood hai : koi zi Rooh nahi janta ke unke liye aankhon ki kaisi thandak chipa ke rakhi gaee hai."
466,"(Sufiyaan ke bajaey) Ubaidullah Ashjai ne abdul-Malik-bin-Abjar se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Shabi se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo member par keh rahe they : be-shak Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ne izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah se ahle-jannat mein se sabse kam hissey paaney waley ke barey mein poochha. . . . . . . aur pichhli hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
467,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hamein apne walid se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ma'roor-bin-Suwed se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main ahle-jannat mein se sab ke baad jannat mein janey waley aur ahale-dozakh mein sabse aakhir mein us se nikalney waley ko janta hun, wo aik aadmi hai jisey qiyamat ke din laya jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : uske samney uske chhotey gunah pesh karo aur uske badey gunah utha rakho (eik taraf hata do) to uske chhotey gunah uske samney laey jaeinge aur kaha jaeyga : falan-falan din tu ney falan-falan kaam kiye aur falan-falan din tu ney falan-falan kaam kiye. wo kahega : haan, wo inkar nahi kar sakega aur wo apne badey gunahon ke pesh honey se khaufzada hoga, (us waqt) usey kaha jaeyga : tumharey liye har burai ke badley aik neki hai. to wo kahega : aey mere rab! maine bahut se aisey ( burey ( kaam kiye jinhein main yahan nahi dekh raha. , main ( Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap hansey yahan tak ke aap ke pichhley daant numaayaan ho gaey."
468,Aamash ke 2 shagirdon abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne apni apni sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki.
469,"abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse (jannat aur jahannam mein) waarid honey ke barey mein sawal kya ja raha tha to unhon-ne kaha : ham qiyamat ke din falan-falan (samt) se aaeingey (dekho), yani us samt se jo logon ke uper hai. kaha : sab ummatein apne apney buton aur jin (ma'boodon) ki bandagii karti thin unke sath bulaaii jaaeingii, aik ke baad eik, phir iske baad hamara rab hamarey paas aayega aur poochhega : tum kis ka intizar kar rahe ho? to wo kahengey : ham apne rab ke muntazir hain. wo farmaeyga : main tumhara rab hun. to sab kahengey : (is waqt) jab ham tumhen dekh lein. to wo hanstaa hua unke samney jalwa afroz hoga. unhon-ne kaha : wo unhein lekar jaeyga aur wo uske peechhey hongey, unmein har insan ko, munafiq ho ya momin, aik noor diya jaeyga wo us noor ke peechhey chalengey aur jahannam ke pul par kai nokon waley kundey aur lohey ke sakht kaantey hongey aur jis ko Allah Taala chaahega wo usey pakad lengey, phir munaafiqon ka noor bujhaa diya jaeyga aur momin nijat paaeingey to sabse pahlaa giroh (jo) nijat paaeyga, unke chehrey chaudahween ke chaand jaisey hongey (wo) 70 hazaar hongey, unka hisab nahi kya jaeyga phir jo log unke baad hongey, unke chehrey aasman ke sabse zyada roshan sitaarey ki tarah hongey, phir isi tarah (darja badarja) iske baad phir shafaat ka marhala aayega aur (shafa'at karne waale) shafaat karengey yahan tak ke har wo shakhs jisne (laa Ilaah illallaah) kaha hoga aur jiske dil mein jau ke wazan ke barabar bhi neki (emaan) hogi. unki jannat ko aagey ke maidan mein daal diya jaeyga aur ahle-jannat un par pani chhidaknaa shuru kar dengey yahan tak ke wo is tarah ug aaeingey jaisey koi cheez sailaab mein ug aati hai aur us (ke jism) ka jalaa hua hissey khatm ho jaeyga phir us se puchha jaeyga yahan tak ke usko duniya aur uske sath us se das guna mazeed ata kar diya jaeyga"
470,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne umr (bin Dinar ( se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : unhon-ne apne donon kanon se ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni, aap farma rahe they : Allah Taala kuchh logon ko aag se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karega."
471,Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : maine Amr-bin-Dinar se puchha : kya aap ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis bayan kartey huey suna hai ke Allah Taala kuchh logon ko shafaat ke zariey se aag mein se nikalega? to unhon-ne kaha : haan.
472,"Qais-bin Saleem Anbari se kaha : Yazeed-al-Faqeer ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah kuchh log aag mein se nikaley jaaeinge, wo apne chehron ke ilawa (poorey ke poorey) usmein jal chukey hongey yahan tak ke wo jannat mein dakhil ho jaaengey."
473,"abu-Aasim, yani Muhammad-bin abi-Ayub ne kaha : mujhey Yazeed-al-Faqeer ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : ke kharijiyon ke nazariyat mein se aik baat mere dil mein ghar kar gaee thi. ham aik jamat mein nikley jiski achi khasi tadaad thi. hamara irada tha ke Haj karein aur phir logon ke khilaf khurooj karein ( jang karein. ( ham Madina se guzrey to ham ne dekha ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (eik sutoon ke paas baithey ( logon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadison suna rahe hain, unhon-ne achcha jahannam se nikal kar jannat mein pahunchne waley logon ka tazkira kya to maine unse puchha : aey Rasulullah ke sathi! ye aap kya bayan kar rahe hain? halanke Allah farmata hai : be-shak jis ko tu ney aag mein dakhil kar diya usko ruswa kar diya. aur : wo jab bhi us se nikalney ka irada karengey, usi mein lota diye jaengey. to ye kya baat hai jo aap keh rahe hain? ( yazeed ne) kaha : unhon-ne ( jawab mein) kaha : kya tum Quran padhtey ho? maine kaha : haan ! unhon-ne kaha : kya tum ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke maqam ke barey mein suna hai, yani wo maqam jis par qiyamat ke din aapko maboos kya jaeyga ? maine kaha : haan ! unhon-ne kaha : be-shak wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka maqaame-mahmood hai jiske zariey se Allah Taala un logon ko jinhein (jahannam se) nikaalna hoga nikaaleyga, phir unhon-ne (jahannam par) pul rakhey janey aur is par se logon ke guzarney ka manzar bayan kya. (Yazeed ne) kaha : mujhey dar hai ke main usko poori tarah yad nahi rakh saka hun. siwaey iske ke unhon-ne bataya : kuchh log jahannam mein chaley janey ke baad us se niklengey, yani unhon-ne kaha : wo is tarah niklengey jaisey wo, tiilon, (ke paudon) ki lakdiyan hon, wo jannat ki nehron main se aik nehar mein dakhil hongey aur is mein nahaaeingey, phir usmein se ( korey ( kaaghazon ki tarah (ho kar) niklengey, phir (ye hadis sun kar) ham wapas aaey aur ham ne kaha : tum par afsos ! kya tum ye samajhtey ho ke ye boodha (sahabi Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jhoot baandh raha hai? aur ham ne (pichhli raey se) rujoo kar liya. Allah ki qism ! ham mein se aik aadmi ke siwa kisi ne khurooj na kya, ya jis tarah (ke alfaz mein) abu-Naeem ne kaha,"
474,"abu-Imran aur Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dozakh se char aadmi niklengey , unhein Allah Taala ki bargah mein pesh kya jaeyga unmein se aik mutwajjeh hoga aur kahega : aey mere rab! jab tu ney mujhey us se nikal hi diya hai to ab dobara usmein na daalnaa, chunanche Allah Taala usko jahannam se nijat de deyga."
475,"abu-Kamil Fuzail-bin-Husain Jahdari aur Muhammad-bin Ubaid Ghubari ne kaha : (alfaz abu-Kamil ke hain) hamein abu-Awana ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala qiyamat ke din logon ko jama karega aur wo is baat par fikr mand hongey (ke us din ki sakhtiyon se kaisey nijat paai jaaey?) (ibne- Ubaid ne kaha : unke dil mein ye baat dali jaeygi) aur wo kahengey : agar ham apne rab ke huzoor koi sifarish laaein taake wo hamein is jagah (ki sakhtiyon) se raahat ata kar de. aap ne farmaya : chunanche wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur kahengey : aap Adam hain, tamam makhlooq ke walid , Allah Taala ne aapko apne hath se paida kya aur aap main apni Rooh phoonki aur farishton ko hukm diya to unhon-ne aapko sajda kya, aap hamarey liye apne rab ke huzoor sifarish farmaein ke wo hamein is (aziyatnak) jagah se raahat de. wo jawab dengey : main us maqam par nahi, phir wo apni ghalati ko, jo unse ho gaee thi, yad karke uski wjah se apne rab se sharmindagi mehsus karengey, (aur kahengey:) lekin tum Nuh ‌(al) ke paas jao, wo pahley rasool hain jinhein Allah Taala ne ( logon ki taraf ( maboos farmaya, aap ne farmaya : to is par log Nuh ‌(al) ‌ke paas aaeingey. wo kahengey : ye mera maqam nahi aur wo apni ghalati ko, jo unse ho gayi thi, yad karkey is par apne rab ki sharmindagi mehsus karengey, (aur kahengey:) lekin tum Ibrahim ke paas jao jinhein Allah Taala ne apna khaleel ( khalis dost ( banaya hai. wo Ibrahim ke paas aaeingey to wo kahengey : ye mera maqam nahi hai aur wo apni ghalati ko yad karengey jo unse ho gaee thi aur is par apne rab se sharminda hongey, (aur kahengey:) lekin tum Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ke paas jao jin se Allah Taala ne kalam kya aur unhein Taurait inayat ki. log Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ki khidmat mein hazir hongey, wo kahengey ki main us maqam par nahi aur apni ghalati ko, jo unse ho gaee thi, yad karke is par apne rab se sharmindagi mehsus karengey (aur kahengey:) lekin tum Rooh Allah aur uske kalimey Esa ‌(al) ke paas jao. log roohullaah aur uske kalimey Esa ‌(al) ke paas aaeingey. wo (bhi ye) kahengey : ye mera maqam nahi hai, tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao, wo aisey barguzeeda bandey hain jiske agley pichhley gunah (agar hotey to bhi) maaf kiye ja chukey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir wo mere paas aaeingey , main apne rab (ke paas haziri ( ki ijazat chahunga to mujhey ijazat di jaeygi, usey dekhtey hi main sajdey mein gir jaunga, to jab tak Allah chaahega mujhey us haalat ( sajde) mein rehney dega. phir kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apna sar uthaaiye , kahey : aap ki baat suni jaeygi, maangiye , aapko diya jaeyga, sifarish kijiye , aap ki sifarish qabool ki jaeygi. main apna sar uthaunga aur apne rab taala ki aisi hamd w sataaish bayan karunga jo mera rab khud mujhey sikhaeyga, phir main sifarish karunga. wo mere liye had muqarrar kar dega, main (iske mutaabiq) logon ko aag se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karunga, phir main wapas aa kar sajdey mein gir jaaunga . Allah Taala jab tak chaahega mujhey usi haalat mein rehney dega, phir kaha jaeyga : apna sar uthaaiye, aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kahey : aap ki baat suni jaeygi, maangiye, aapko milega, sifarish kijiye aap ki sifarish qabool ki jaeygi. mein apna sar uthaunga aur apne rab ki wo hamd karunga jo mera rab mujhey sikhaeyga, phir main sifarish karunga to wo mere liye phir aik had muqarrar farma dega, main unko dozakh se nikalunga aur jannat mein dakhil karunga. (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey yad nahi, aap ne teesri ya chauthi baar farmaya) phir main kahunga : aey mere rab! aag mein unke siwa aur koi baqi nahi bacha jinhein Quran ne rok liya hai, yani jinka (dozakh mein) hamesha rehna (Allah ki taraf se) lazimi ho gaya hai. ibne-Ubaid ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Qatada ne kaha : yani jiska hamesha rehna lazimi ho gaya."
476,"dusri sanad se jis main ( abu-Awana ke bajaey) Saeed ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din momin jama hongey aur us (ki holnaakiyon se bchney ( ki fikr mein mubtala hongey ya ye baat unke dilon mein dali jaeygi. , . . . .) aagey ( abu-Awana ki hadis ki tarah hai, albatta unhon-ne us hadis mein ye kaha : phir main chothi baar Allah Taala ki khidmat mein hazir hunga (ya chothi baar lotunga) aur kahunga : aey mere rab! unke siwa jinhein Quran (ke faisley) ne rok rakha hai aur koi baqi nahi bachaa."
477,"Muaaz-bin-Hishaam ne kaha : mere walid ne mujhey Qatada ke hawale se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din Allah Taala mominon ko jama karega, phir us (din ki pareshani se bachney) ke liye unke dil mein ye baat dali jaeygi. . . . . ye hadis bhi un donon (abu-Awaana aur Saeed) ki hadis ki tarah hai, chothi baar ke barey mein ye kaha : to main kahunga : aey mere rab! aag mein unke siwa aur koi baqi nahi jisey Quran (ke faisley) ne rok liya hai, yani jiske liye (aag mein) hamesha rehna wajib ho gaya hai."
478,"Muhammad-bin Minhal Zareer (naa-beenaa) ne kaha : hamein Yazeed-bin-Zure ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba aur Hisham Dastwai ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . isi tarah abu-Ghassaan mismai aur Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : mere walid ne mujhey Qatada ke hawale se hadis sunai, (unhon-ne kahaa:) hamein Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is shakhs ko aag se nikal liya jaeyga jisne (laa ilaa-h illallaah) kaha aur uske dil mein aik jo ke wazan ke barabar khair hui, phir aisey shakhs ko aag se nikala jaeyga jisne (laa ilaa-h illallaah) kaha aur uske dil mein gandam ke daney ke barabar khair hui, phir usko aag se nikala jaeyga jisne (laa ilaa-h illallaah) kaha aur uske dil mein aik zarrey ke barabar bhi khair hui. (pichhey ki bahut si hadison se wazaahat hoti hai ke khair se murad eman hai.) ibne-Minhal ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya ke Yazeed ne kaha : main Shoba se mila aur unhein ye hadis sunai to Shoba ne kaha : hamein ye hadis Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunai, albatta Shoba ne, aik zarrey, ke bajaaey, makai ka daana, kaha, Yazeed ne kaha is lafz mein abu Bistam (Sho'ba) se tas-heef (huroof mein shak ki wjah se ghalati) ho gaee."
479,"Mabad-bin-Hilal Anzi ne kaha : ham log Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur Sabit ko apna sifarishi banaya (unke zariey se mulaqat ki ijazat hasil ki.) ham unke yahan pahunchey to wo chasht ki Namaz padh rahe they. Sabit ne hamarey liye (andar aaney ki) ijazat li. ham andar unke samney hazir huey. unhon-ne Sabit ko apne sath apni charpai par bitha liya . Sabit ne unse kaha : aey abu-Hamza ! Basra ke baashindon mein se aap ke (ye ( bhai aap se darkhaast kartey hain ke aap unhein shafaat ki hadis sunain. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya : jab qiyamat ka din hoga to log maujon ki tarah aik doosrey se takraa rahe hongey. wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur unse arz karengey : apni aulad ke haq mein sifarish kijiye (ke wo maidaane-hashr ke masaayib aur mushkil intizar se nijat paaein .) wo kahengey : main uske liye nahi hun. lekin tum Ibrahim ka daman thaam lo kyonke wo Allah Taala ke khaleel ( khalis dost ( hain. log Ibrahim ke paas jaengey. wo jawab dengey : main uske liye nahi. lekin tum Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas pahunch jao wo kaleem Allah hain (jin se Allah ne seedhey-seedhey kalam kya ( to Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas haziri hogi. wo farmaaengey : main uske liye nahi. lekin tum Esa ‌(al) ke sath lag jao kyonke wo Allah ki Rooh aur iska kalima hain. to Esa ‌(al) ‌ ke paas aamad hogi, wo farmaaengey : main uske liye nahi. lekin tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunch jao, to (unki ( aamad mere paas hogi. main jawab doonga is (kaam) ke liye main hun. main chal padoonga aur apne rab ke samney haziri ki ijazat chaahoonga, mujhey ijazat ata ki jaeygi, main iske samney khada hunga aur tareef ki aisi baton ke sath uski hamd karunga jis par main ab main qaadir nahi hun, Allah Taala hi ye (hamd) mere dil mein daalega, phir main iske huzoor sajdey mein gir jaunga, phir mujh se kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apna sar uthayen aur kahein, aap ki baat suni jaeygi, maangein, aapko diya jaeyga aur sifarish karein, aap ki sifarish qabool ki jaeygi. main arz karunga : aey mere rab! meri ummat ! meri ummat ! to mujh se kaha jaeyga : jayen jiske dil mein gehun ya jau ke daney ke barabar eman hai usey nikal lein, main jaaunga aur aisa karunga, phir main apne rab taala ke huzoor lot aaoonga aur hamd ke unhi Uslooon se uski tareef bayan karunga, phir iske samney sajdey mein gir jaaunga to mujhey kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apna sar uthayen aur kahein, aap ki baat suni jaeygi aur maangein, aapko diya jaeyga aur sifarish karein, aap ki sifarish qabool hogi. main arz karunga : aey mere rab! meri ummat ! meri ummat ! mujhey kaha jaeyga : jaaein, jiske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman ho, usey nikal lein. to main jaaunga aur aisa karunga, phir apne rab ke huzoor lot aaoonga aur us jaisi tareef se uski hamd karunga, phir iske samney sajdey mein gir jaaunga . to mujh se kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apna sar uthaaein, kahiin, aap ki baat suni jaeygi aur maangein, aapko diya jaeyga aur sifarish karein, aap ki sifarish qabool hogi. to main kahunga : aey mere rab! meri ummat! meri ummat! to mujh se kaha jaeyga : jaaein, jiske dil mein raai ke daney se kam, us se ( bhi) kam, us se (aur bhi) kam eman ho usey aag se nikal lein to main jaaunga aur aisa karunga. ye Hazrat Anas ki riwayat hai jo unhon-ne hamein bayan ki. (Ma'bad-bin-Hilaal Anzi ne) kaha : chunanche ham unke yahan se nikal aaey, jab ham chatiyal maidan ke oopri hissey par pahunchey to ham ne kaha : (kya hi achchhaa ho ( agar ham Hasan Basri ka rukh karein aur unhein salam kartey jaaein. wo ( Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf ke dar se) abu khaleefa ke ghar mein chhipey huey they. unhon-ne kaha : jab ham unke paas pahunchey to unhein salam kya. ham ne kaha : janab abu-Saeed ! ham aap ke bhai abu Hamza (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat hai) ke paas se aa rahe hain. ham ne kabhi is jaisi hadis nahi suni jo unhon shafaat ke barey mein hamein sunai. Hasan Basri ne kaha : laaein sunain . ham ne unhein hadis sunai to unhon-ne kaha : aagey sunaein. ham ne kaha : unhon-ne hamein us se zyada nahi sunaya. unhon (Hasan Basrii) ne kaha : hamein unhon-ne ye hadis bees baras pahley sunai thi, us waqt wo poori quwwaton ke Malik they. unhon-ne kuchh hissey chhod diya hai, malum nahi, Shekh bhool gaey ya unhon-ne tumhen poori hadis sunana pasand nahi kya ke kahin tum (is mein bayan ki hui baat hi par) bharosa na kar lo. ham ne kaha : aap hamein suna dein to wo hans padey aur kaha : insan jald-baaz paida kya gaya hai, maine tumharey samney is baat ka tazkira iske siwa (aur kisi wjah se) nahi kya tha magar isliye ke main tumhen ye hadis sunana chahta tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir main chothi baar apne rab ki taraf lotunga, phir unhi ta'reefon se uski hamd bayan karunga, phir uske huzoor sajda rez ho jaaunga to mujh se kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apna sar uthayen aur kahein, aap ki baat suni jaeygi aur maangein, aapko diya jaeyga aur sifarish karein aap ki sifarish qabool hogi. to main arz karunga : aey mere rab! mujhey unke barey mein (bhi) ijazat dijiye jinhoney ( sirf ( (laa Ilaah illallaah) kaha, Allah farmaeyga : ye aap ke liye nahi lekin meri izzat ki qasam, meri kibriyaaii, meri azmat aur meri badaai ki qasam! main unko ( bhi) jahannam se nikal loonga jinhoney (laa Ilaah illallaah) kaha, Mabad ka bayan hai : main Hasan Basri ke barey mein gawahi deta hun ke unhon-ne hamein bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se ye riwayat suni. mera khayal hai, unhon-ne kaha : bees saal pahley, aur is waqt unki salahiyatein bharpur thin."
480,"abu-Hayyan ne abu-Zura se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gosht laya gaya aur dasti utha kar aapko pesh ki gaee kyonke aapko dasti bahut pasand thi, aap ne apne daanton se aik baar usmein se khaya aur farmaya : main qiyamat ke din tamam insanon ka sardaar hoonga. kya tum jantey ho ye kaisey hoga? Allah Taala qiyamat ke din tamam aglon aur pichhlon ko aik hamwaar chatiyal maidan mein jama karega . bulaney wala sab ko apni awaz sunaaeyga aur (Allah ki) nazar sab ke aar paar (sab ko dekh rahi) hogi. suraj qareeb ho jaeyga aur logon ko is qadr gham aur bechaini hogi jo unki taqat se zyada aur naqabile-bardasht hoga. log aik doosrey se kahengey : kya dekhtey nahi tum kis haalat mein ho? kya dekhtey nahi tum par kaisi museebat aan padi hai? kya tum koi aisa shakhs talash nahi kartey jo tumhari sifarish kar de ? yani tumharey rab ke huzoor . chunanche log aik doosrey se kahengey : Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas chalo to wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey : aey Adam ! aap sab insanon ke walid hain, Allah Taala ne aapko apne hath se banaya aur aap main apni ( taraf se) Rooh phoonki aur farishton ko hukm diya to unhon-ne aapko sajda kya. aap apne rab ke huzoor hamari sifarish farmaein . aap dekhtey nahi ham kis haal mein hain? kya aap dekhtey nahi ham par kaisi museebat aan padi hai? Adam (Alaihissalam) jawab dengey : mera rab aaj itney ghussey mein hai jitney ghussey mein ab se pahley kabhi nahi aaya aur na iske baad kabhi aayega aur yaqinan usne mujhey aik khas darakht (ke qareeb janey ( se rokaa tha lekin maine uski nafarmani ki thi, mujhey apni jaan ki fikr hai, mujhey apni jaan bachani hai. tum kisi aur ke paas jao, Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao. log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey : aey Nuh ! aap zamin walon ki taraf bhejey gaey sabse pahley rasool hain aur Allah Taala ne aapko shukr-guzar bandey ka naam diya hai. aap dekhtey nahi ham kis haal mein hain? aap dekhtey nahi ham par kya museebat aan padi hai? wo unhein jawab dengey : aaj mera rab itney ghussey mein hai jitney ghussey mein na wo ab se pahley kabhi aaya na aainda kabhi aayega. haqiqat ye hai ke mere liye aik dua (khaas ki gai) thi wo maine apni qaum ke khilaf maang li. ( aaj to ( meri apni jaan ( par bani ( hai. mujhey apni jaan (ki fikr ( hai. tum Ibrahim ke paas jao, chunanche log Ibrahim ke paas hazir hongey aur arz guzaar hongey : aap Allah ke Nabi aur ahal zamin mein main uske khaleel ( sirf iske dost ( hain, apne rab ke huzoor hamari sifarish farmaaein, aap dekhtey nahi ham kis haal mein hain? kya aap dekhtey nahi ham par kya museebat aan padi hai? to Ibrahim unse kahengey : mera rab is qadr ghussey mein hai ke ab se pahley kabhi itney ghussey mein nahi aaya aur na aainda kabhi aayega aur apne ( teen ( jhoot yad karengey, (aur kahengey ( mujhey apni jaan ki fikr hai, mujhey to apni jaan bachani hai. kisi aur ke paas jao, Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ke paas jao. log Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ke khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey : aey Musa ! aap Allah ke rasool hain, Allah Taala ne aapko apne paigham aur apni ham kalami ke zariey se fazeelat ata ki, Allah ke huzoor hamarey liye sifarish keejiye, aap dekhtey nahi ham kis haal mein hain? aap dekhtey nahi ham par kya museebat aan padi hai? Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌unse kahengey : mera rab aaj is qadr ghussey mein hai ke na ab se pahley kabhi is qadr ghussey mein aaya aur na iske baad aayega. main aik jaan ko qatl kar chuka hun jiske qatl ka mujhey hukm na diya gaya tha. meri jaan (ka kya hoga ( meri jaan ( kaisey bachegi?) Esa ‌(al) ke paas jaao.log Esa ‌(al) ke paas aaeingey aur arz karengey : aey Eisaa! aap Allah ka kalima hain jisey usne Maryam ‌(al) ki taraf daala aur uski Rooh hain, isliye aap apne rab ke huzoor hamari sifarish farmaaein, aap hamari haalat nahi dekhtey jis mein ham hain? kya aap nahi dekhtey ham par kaisi museebat aan padi hai? to Esa ‌(al) unhein jawab dengey : mera rab itney ghussey mein hai jitney ghussey mein na wo us se pahley aaya aur na aainda kabhi aayega , wo apni kisi khata ka zikr nahi karengey, (kahengey mujhey) apni jaan ki fikr hai, mujhey apni jaan bachani hai. mere siwa kisi aur ke paas jao, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao. log mere paas aaeingey aur kahengey : aey Muhammad! aap Allah ke rasool aur aakhiri Nabi hain, Allah Taala ne aap ke agley pichhley tamam gunah (agar hotey to bhi) maaf kar diye, apne rab ke huzoor hamari sifarish farmaaein, aap dekhtey nahi ham kis haal mein hain? aap dekhtey nahi ham par kiya museebat aan padi hai? to main chal padoonga aur arsh ke nichey aaoonga aur apne rab ke huzoor sajdey mein gir jaunga, phir Allah Taala mujh par apni aisi tareefon aur apni aisi behtreen sana ke darwazey khol dega aur unhein mere dil mein daalega jo mujh se pahley kisi ke liye nahi kholey gaey, phir ( Allah ( farmaeyga : aey Muhammad! apna sar uthaiye, mangiye, aapko milega, sifarish keejiye, aap ki sifarish qabool hogi. to main sar uthaunga aur arz karunga : aey mere rab! meri ummat ! meri ummat ! to kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! aap ki ummat ke jin logon ka hisaab-kitaab nahi unko jannat ke darwazey mein se daaein darwazey se dakhil kar dijiye aur wo jannat ke baqi darwazon main (bhi) logon ke sath Sharik hain. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai! jannat ke 2 kiwaadon ke darmyan itna ( fasla ( hai jitna Makka aur) Shehre-hijr) ya Makka aur Basra ke darmyan hai."
481,"(eik dusri sanad se) Ammara-bin-Qaqa ne abu-Zura se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney sareed aur gosht ka piyala rakha gaya, aap ne dasti uthai , aapko bakri (ke gosht ( mein sabse zyada yahi hissey pasand tha, aap ne usmein se aik baar apne daanton se khaya aur farmaya : main qiyamat ke din tamam logon ka sardaar hoonga. phir dobara khaya aur farmaya : main qiyamat ke roz tamam insanon ka sardaar hoonga. jab aap ne dekha ke aap ke sathi (iske barey mein) aap se kuchh nahi poochh rahe to aap ne farmaya : tum poochhtey kyon nahi ke ye kaisey hoga? unhon-ne puchha : ye kaisey hoga? Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : log rabbul-aalameen ke samney khadey hongey. . . . .) Imaara ne bhi) Abu-Zura ke hawale se abu-Hayyan ki bayan ki hui hadis ki tarah bayan ki aur Ibrahim ke waqiey mein ye izafa kya : (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : Ibrahim ne sitarey ke barey mein apna qaul : ye mera rab hai, aur unke mabudon ke barey mein ye kehna : balke ye kaam unke badey ne kya hai, aur ye kehna : main bimar hun, yad kya. (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai! chaukhat ke donon baazuon tak jannat ke kiwadon mein se (har ( 2 kiwadon ke darmyan : itna fasla hai ke jitna Makka aur hijr ke darmyan , ya ( farmaya ( hijr aur Makka ke darmyan hai."
482,"Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne kaha : hamein abu-Malik Ashjai ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez abu-Malik ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah tabarak w taala logon ko jama karega to momin khadey ho jaeinge yahan tak ke jannat unke qareeb kar di jaeygi aur wo Adam ‌(al) ke paas aa kar arz karengey : aey walid buzurg ! hamarey liye jannat ka darwaza khulwaaiye . wo jawab dengey : kya jannat se tumhen nikalney ka sabab tumharey bap Adam ki khata ke ilawa koi aur cheez bani thi! main is kaam ka ahal nahi hun. mere betey, Allah ke khaleel Ibrahim ke paas jao. aap ne farmaya : Ibrahim kahengey : is kaam (ko karne) wala mein nahi hun, main khaleel tha (magar awwaleen shafaat ke us mansab se) peechhey-peechhey. tum Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ka rukh karo, jin se Allah Taala ne kalam kya. log Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ke paas aaeingey. wo jawab dengey : is kaam (ko karne) wala mein nahi hun. Allah Taala ki Rooh aur uske kalimey Esa ‌‌(al) ke paas jao. Esa ‌‌(al) farmaengey, main us kaam (ko karne) wala nahi hun. to log Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaeingey. aap Allah ke samney qiyam farmaengey aur aapko (shafaat ki) ijazat di jaeygi. amanat aur qarabat dari ko bheja jaeyga, wo pul siraat ki donon taraf daain aur baain khadi ho jaaeingii. tum mein se awwaleen shakhs bijli ki tarah guzar jaeyga, maine puchha : mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan ! bijli guzarney ki tarah, kya hai? aap ne farmaya : tum ne kabhi bijli ki taraf nahi dekha, kis tarah palak jhapakney mein guzarti aur laut'tii hai? phir hawa ke guzarney ki tarah (tezii se) phir parinda guzarney aur aadmi ke daudney ki tarah, unke aamaal unko lekar daudeingey aur tumhara Nabi pul siraat par khada hua keh raha hoga : aey mere rab! bacha bachaa (meri ummat ke har guzarney waley ko salamati se guzaar de.) yahan tak ke bandon ke aamaal unko lekar guzar na sakengey yahan tak ke aisa aadmi aaey gaa jis mein ghisat ghisat kar chalney se zyada ki istitaat na hogi. aap ne farmaya : ( pul ( siraat ke donon kinaron par lohey ke aankdey muallaq hongey, wo is baat par maamoor hongey ke jin logon ke barey mein hukm ho unko pakad lein, is tarah kuchh zakhmi ho kar nijat pa jaeinge aur kuchh aag mein dhakel diye jaengey. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Abu-Hurera ki jaan hai! jahannam ki gehrai 70 saal (ki masaafat) ke barabar hai."
483,"Jarir ne Mukhtar-bin-fulful se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logon mein se sabse pahlaa shakhs mein hunga jo jannat ke barey mein sifarish karega aur tamam anbiya se mere perokar zyada hongey."
484,"Sufiyan ne Mukhtar-bin-fulful se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din tamam anbiya ki nisbat mere perokar zyada hongey aur main pahlaa shakhs hunga jo jannat ka darwaza khatkhataaeyga."
485,"Zayda ne Mukhtar-bin-fulful se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat ke barey mein sabse pahlaa sifarish karne wala main hoonga, anbiya mein se kisi Nabi ki itni tasdeeq nahi ki gaee jitni meri ki gaee aur bila shubah anbiya mein aisa bhi Nabi hoga jinki ummat (dawat) mein se aik shakhs hi unki tasdeeq karta hoga."
486,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main qiyamat ke din jannat ke darwazey par aaoonga aur darwaza khulwaaunga. jannat ka darbaan poochhega : aap kon hain? mein jawab doonga : Muhammad ! wo kahega : mujhey aap hi ke barey mein hukm mila tha (ke (aap se pahley kisi ke liye darwaza na kholun."
487,"Malik-bin-Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har Nabi ki aik ( yaqeeni ( dua hai jo wo mangta hai. main chahta hun ke main apni dua ko qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye mehfooz rakhun."
488,"( Malik-bin-Anas ke bajaey) ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ne ibne-Shahab se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan har Nabi ki aik dua hai) jiski qabooliyat yaqeeni hai.) maine irada kya hai ke inshaAllah main apni is dua ko qiyamat ke roz apni ummat ki sifarish karne ke liye mehfooz rakhunga."
489,"ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ne ibne-Shahab se aur unhon-ne ( abu-Salma ke bajaey) Amr-bin-abii-Sufiyan-bin-Usaid-bin-Jariya saqafi se usi ki tarah hadis Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki."
490,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di ke Amr bin abi Sufiyan Saqafi ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Kab ahbaar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, bila shubah Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har Nabi ki aik ( yaqeeni ( dua hai jo wo karta hai aur main chahta hun ke insha-Allah main apni dua qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye mehfooz rakhun. is par Kab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ne ye farman ( seedhey-seedhey ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha? Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : haan !"
491,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har Nabi ki aik dua aisi hai jo ( yaqeeni taur par) qabool ki janey wali hai. har Nabi ne apni wo dua jaldi maang li, jabke maine apni dua qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye mehfooz kar li hai, chunanche ye dua insha-Allah meri ummat ke har us fard ko pahuncheygi jo Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na kartey huey faut hua.'"
492,"abu-Zura ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har Nabi ke liye aik qabool ki janey wali dua hai, wo usey mangta hai to ( zaroor ( qabool ki jati hai aur wo usey ata kar di jati hai. maine apni dua qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye chipa ( bacha ( kar rakhi hai."
493,"Muhammad-bin-Ziyad ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har Nabi ki aik dua hai jo usney apni ummat ke barey mein mangi aur wo uske liye qabool hui aur main chahta hun ke insha-Allah main apni dua ko qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye taal doon."
494,"Hisham ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har Nabi ki aik (yaqeenii maqbool) dua hai jo usney apni ummat ke liye ki jabke maine apni dua qiyamat ke roz apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye mehfooz kar li hai."
495,uper zikr ki gaee riwayat (Hishaam ke bajaey) Shoba ne Qatada se baqi bachi hui isi sanad ke sath bayan ki.
496,"Wakee aur abu-Usama ne Misar se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki, itna farq hai ke Wakee ki riwayat ke alfaz hain : aap ne farmaya : (har Nabi ko aik dua) ata ki gaee hai, aur abu-Usama ki riwayat ke alfaz hain : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai."
497,"Motamir ke walid Sulaiman-bin-Tarkhan ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . . . . . . aagey ki Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat ki tarah hai."
498,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat bayan kartey hain ke, har Nabi ke liye aik dua hai jo wo apni ummat ke barey mein kar chuka jabke maine apni dua qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki sifarish ke liye mehfooz kar rakhi hai."
499,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ibrahim ke barey mein Allah Taala ke farman : parwardigar, un buton ne bahuton ko gumrahi mein daala hai (mumkin hai ke meri aulad ko bhi ye gumrah kar dein, lihaza unmein se) jo mere tareeqey par chaley wo mera hai aur jo mere khilaf tariqa ikhtiyar karey to yaqinan to darguzar karne wala meharban hai. aur Esa ‌(al) ‌ ke qaul, agar to unhein azab de to wo terey bandey hain aur agar to unhein maaf farma de to bila shubah tu hi ghalib hikmat wala hai, ki tilawat farmai aur apne hath utha kar farmaya : aey Allah ! meri ummat , meri ummat , aur) be ikhtiyar ( ro padey . Allah Taala ne hukm diya : aey Jibreel ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao, jabke tumhara rab zyada jaanney wala hai, unse poochho ke aapko kya baat rulaa rahi hai? Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) aap ke paas aaey aur) wjah ( poochhi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo baat kahi thi unko batai, jabke wo (Allah is baat se) zyada achi tarah aagah hai, is par Allah Taala ne farmaya : aey Jibreel ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao aur kaho ke ham aap ki ummat ke barey mein aapko razi karengey aur ham aapko takleef na honey dengey."
500,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! mera bap kahan hai? aap ne farmaya : aag mein. phir jab wo palat gaya to aap ne usey bula kar farmaya : bila shubah mera bap aur tumhara bap aag mein hain.
501,"Jarir ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Musa-bin-Talha aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab ye aayat utri : aur apne qaribi rishtedaron ko daraaiye , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish ko bulaya. jab wo jama ho gaey to aap ne umumi haisiyat se (sab ko) aur khas karke ( alag khandanon aur logon ko unke naam ley lekar ( farmaya : aey Ka'b-bin-Luii ki aulad ! apne aapko aag se bacha lo, aey murra-bin-Ka'b ki aulaad! apne aapko aag se bacha lo, aey abd munaaf ki aulaad! apne aapko aag se bacha lo, aey banu-Haashim ki aulad ! apne aapko aag se bacha lo, aey abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! apne aapko aag se bacha lo, aey Fatima (binte-rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ! apne aapko aag se bacha lo, main Allah Taala ki taraf se (kisi pakad ki sura mein) tumharey liye kisi cheez ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta, tum logon ke sath rishta hai, usey mein isi tarah jodtaa rahunga jis tarah jodnaa chaahiye."
502,Abdul-Malik se ( Jarir ke ilawa ( abu-Awana ne bhi ye hadis isi sanad ke sath bayan ki. lekin Jarir ki riwayat zyada mukammal aur sair hasil hai.
503,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke jab aayat : aur apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaiye , nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safa pahaad par khadey ho kar farmaya : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beti Fatima ! aey abdul-Muttalib ki beti Safiya ! aey abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! main Allah Taala ki taraf se tumharey liye kisi cheez ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. (haan!) mere maal mein se jo chaho mujh se maang lo."
504,"ibne-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat utari gaee : aur apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaein, to aap ne farmaya : aey Quraish ke logo! apni jaanon ko Allah Taala se khareed lo, main Allah Taala ke (faisley ke) samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aa sakta , aey abdul-Muttalib ke betey Abbas ! main Allah ke) faisley ke) samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aa sakta, aey Allah ke rasool ki phoophii Safiya! main Allah ke) faisley ke) samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aa sakta , aey Allah ke rasool ki beti Fatima ! mujh se ( mere maal mein se) jo chaho maang lo, main Allah ke) faisley ke) samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aa sakta."
505,aik aur sanad se Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki.
506,"Yazeed bin Zaree ne (Sulaimaan) Taimi se, unhon-ne abu-Usmaan ke waastey se Hazrat Qabisa bin makhaariq aur Hazrat Zuhair bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha ke jab aayat : aur apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaiye , utri , kaha : to Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik pahaadii chattaan ki taraf tashrif le gaey aur uske sabse oonchey pattharon waley hissey par chadhey , phir awaz di : aey abd munaaf ki aulad ! main daraane wala hun, meri aur tumhari misal us aadmi ki hai jisne dushman ko dekha to wo khandan ko bachaney ke liye chal padaa aur usey khatrah hua ke dushman us se pahley na pahunch jaey to wo buland awaz se pukarney laga : afsos uski subah (ki tabahi! ("
507,( Yazeed bin Zaree ke bajaey) Motamir ne apne walid ( Sulaiman (ke hawale se baqi bachi hui pichhli sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
508,"abu-Usama ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Murra se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab ye aayat utri : aur apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaiye, (khaas kar) apne khandan ke mukhlis logon ko . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghar se) nikley yahan tak ke kohe-Safa par chadh gaey aur pukar kar kaha : afsos! uski subah (ki tabaahii) (sab aik doosrey se) poochhney lagey : ye kon pukar raha hai? ( kuchh ( logon ne kaha : Muhammad (sl), chunanche sab log aap ke paas jama ho gaey. aap ne farmaya : aey falan ki aulad ! aey falan ki aulad ! aey abd munaaf ki aulad ! aey abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! ye log aap ke qareeb jama ho gaey to aap ne puchha : tumhara kya khayal hai hai ke agar main tumhen khabar dun ke us pahaad ke daman se ghud-sawaar nikalney waley hain to kya tum meri tasdeeq karogey ? unhon-ne kaha : hamein aap se kabhi jhooti baat ( sunney (ka tajriba nahi hua. aap ne farmaya : to main tumhen aaney waley shadeed azab se dara raha hun. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to abu-Lahab kehney laga : tumharey liye tabahi ho, kya tum ne hamein isi baat ke liye jama kya tha? phir wo uth gaya. is par ye sura nazil hui : abu-Lahab ke donon hath tabah huey aur wo khud halaak hua. Aamash ne isi tarah sura ke aakhir tak padha ."
509,Aamash se ( abu-Usama ke bajaey) abu-Muawiya ne usi (pichhli (sanad ke sath bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din kohe-Safa par chadhey aur farmaya : afsos uski subah (ki tabaahi!) iske baad abu-Usama ki bayan ki hui hadis ki tarah riwayat ki aur aayat : ( وَأَنْذِرْ عَشِيرَتَكَ الْأَقْرَبِينَ ( utarney ka zikr nahi kya.
510,"abu-Awana ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris bin Nofal se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ke unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aap ne abu-Taalib ko kuchh nafa pahunchaya ? wo har taraf se aap ka bachaw kartey they aur aapki khaatir ghazabnaak hotey they. aap ne jawab diya : haan, wo kam gehri aag mein hain (jo takhnon tak aati hai) agar main na hota to wo jahannam ke sabse nichley tabqey mein hotey."
511,"Sufiyan (bin Uena ( ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! abu-Taalib har taraf se aap ki hifazat kartey they, aap ki madad kartey they aur aap ki khaatir ( mukhalifon par) ghussa kartey they, to kya us se unko kuchh nafa hua? aap ne farmaya : haan , maine unko aag ki athaah gahraaiyon mein paya to unko kam gehri aag tak nikal laayaa."
512,Sufiyan ( Sory ( ne isi sanad ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah abu-Awana ne bayan ki.
513,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aap ke chacha abu-Taalib ka tazkira kya gaya to aap ne farmaya : ummeed hai qiyamat ke din meri sifarish unko nafa degi aur unhein uthli (kam gehri ( aag mein daala jaeyga jo ( ba-mushkil ( unke takhnon tak pahunchti hogi, us se ( bhi) unka dimagh khaulega."
514,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ahale-jahannam mein se sabse kam azab mein wo hoga jo aag ki 2 jootiyaan pahney hoga, uski jootiyon ki garmi se Uska dimagh khaulega."
515,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dozkhiyon mein se sabse halka azab abu-Taalib ko hoga, unhon-ne 2 jootiyaan pahan rakhi hongi jin se unka dimagh khaulega."
516,"Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se sun kar hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ko khitab kartey huey suna, keh rahe they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : aap ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din dozkhiyon mein se sabse kam azab us aadmi ko hoga jiske talwon ke nichey aag ke 2 angaarey rakhey jaeinge , unse uska dimagh khaulega."
517,"(Shoba ke bajaey) Aamash ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dozkhiyon mein se sabse halkey azab wala shakhs wo hoga jiske donon jootey aur donon tasmey aag ke hongey, unse uska dimagh is tarah khauleyga jis tarah handiya khaultii hai, wo nahi samjheyga ke koi bhi us se zyada azab mein hai, halanke haqiqat mein wo un sab mein se halkey azab mein hoga."
518,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! ibne-Judaan jahiliyat ke daur mein sila rehmii karta tha aur mohtajon ko khana khilata tha to kya ye amal uske liye faayde-mand hongey? aap ne farmaya : usey fayda nahi pahunchaeingey, (kyonke) us ne kisi aik din ( bhi) ye nahi kaha tha : mere rab! hisaab-kitaab ke din meri khataein maaf farmana."
519,"Hazrat Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko buland awaz se bar-sare-aam ye kehtey huey suna : yaqinan aale-Ubai, yani falan mere wali nahi, mera wali sirf aur sirf Allah Taala hai aur nek momin hain."
520,"Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad ke waastey se Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein se 70 hazaar ( afraad ( baghair hisab ke jannat mein dakhil hongey. aik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah se dua kijiye ke wo mujhey bhi unmein shamil kar de, aap ne dua farmai : aey Allaah! usey unmein shamil kar. phir aik aur khada ho gaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! Allah Taala se dua farmaiye wo mujhey bhi unmein shamil kar de. aap ne jawab diya : Ukasha us mamley main tum se sabqat ley gaey."
521,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se hadis suni, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera se suni, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. . . . . .) aagey ( Rabe ki hadis ki tarah ( hai.)"
522,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne hadis sunai ke unhein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : meri ummat ka aik giroh jannat mein dakhil hoga, wo 70 hazaar afraad hongey, unke chehrey is tarah chamaktey hongey jis tarah chaudahwiin raat ko maahe-kaamil chamaktaa hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (is par) ukaasha-bin-Mohsin Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) apni surkh, safaid aur siyah dhaariyon wali chadar buland kartey huey uthey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah se dua farmaiye ke wo mujhey bhi unmein se kar de to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allaah! usey unmein se kar de. phir aik Ansari khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah se dua farmaiye ke wo mujhey bhi unmein se kar de to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usmein Ukasha tum se sabqat ley gaey."
523,"(Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ke bajaey) abu Yunus ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat se 70 hazaar afraad jannat mein dakhil hongey, chaand ki si sura mein, unka aik giroh hoga."
524,"Muhammad-bin Sirin ne kaha ke Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey ye hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat ke 70 hazaar log hisab ke baghair jannat mein dakhil hongey. sahaba kiram ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! wo kon log hain? aap ne farmaya : wo aisey log hain jo daaghney ke amal se ilaaj nahi karaatey, na hi dam karatey hain aur apne rab par kaamil bharosa kartey hain. Ukasha (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha : Allah se dua farmaiye ke wo mujhey bhi unmein (shaamil) kar de. aap ne farmaya : tum unmein se ho. (Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir aik aur aadmi khada hua aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Nabi ! Allah se dua kijiye ke wo mujhey ( bhi) unmein ( shamil ( kar de, aap ne farmaya : usmein Ukasha tum se sabqat ley gaey."
525,"Hakam-bin-Aaraj ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat ke 70 hazaar log hisab ke baghair jannat mein dakhil hongey. sahaba kiram ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! wo kon log hain? aap ne farmaya : wo aisey log hain jo dam nahi karwatey, shagoon nahi letey, daaghney ke zariey se ilaaj nahi karwatey aur apne rab par pura bharosa kartey hain."
526,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein se 70 hazaar ya saat (7) laakh afraad (abu-Haazim ko shak hai ke Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kon sa adad bataya) is tarah jannat mein dakhil hongey ke wo yakjaa hongey, eik-doosrey ko pakdey huey, unmein se pahlaa fard us waqt tak dakhil nahi hoga jab tak aakhiri fard (bhi sath hi) dakhil na hoga, ikatthey hi (jannat ke wasee darwazey se) andar jaengey. unke chehrey chaudahwin raat ke chaand jaisey hongey."
527,"Hushaim ne kaha : hamein Husain-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di, kaha ke main Saeed-bin-Jubair ke paas maujood tha, unhon-ne puchha : tum mein se wo sitara kis ne dekha tha jo kal raat tuta tha. maine kaha ke main Namaz mein nahi tha balke mujhey das liya gaya tha (kisi zehreeley janwar ne das liya tha) unhon-ne puchha : phir tum ne kya kya? maine kaha : maine dam karwaya . unhon-ne kaha : tumhen kis cheez ne is par aamada kiya? maine jawab diya is hadis ne jo hamein Shabi ne sunai. unhon-ne puchha : Shabi ne tumhen kon si hadis sunai ? maine kaha : unhon ( Shabi ( ne hamein Barida bin Hasib Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat sunai, unhon-ne bataya ke buri nazar lagney aur zehrili cheez ke dasney ke ilawa aur kisi cheez ke liye jhaad phoonk nahi. to Saeed ne kaha : jisne jo suna, usey ikhtiyar kya to achchha kya. lekin hamein Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis sunai ke aap ne farmaya : mere samney ummatein pesh ki gain, maine aik Nabi ko dekha, unke sath aik chhota sa (das se kam ka ( giroh tha, kisi (aur) Nabi ko dekha ke uske sath aik ya 2 ummatii they, koi Nabi aisa bhi tha ke uske sath koi ummatii na tha, achcha aik badi jamat mere samney laai gaee, mujhey guman hua ke ye mere ummatii hain, is par mujh se kaha gaya ke ye Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ aur unki qaum hai lekin aap ufuq ki taraf dekhein, maine dekha to (wahaan bhi) aik bahut badi jamat thi, mujhey bataya gaya : ye aap ki ummat hai. aur unke sath aisey 70 hazaar (log) hain jo kisi hisab kitab aur kisi azab ke baghair jannat mein dakhil ho jaengey. phir aap uthey aur apne ghar ke andar chaley gaey, wo (sahaaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ajmaeen) un logon ke barey mein guftgu mein masroof ho gaey, jo baghair hisab aur azab ke jannat mein dakhil hongey. unmein se kuchh ne kaha : shayad wo log hain jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ka sharf hasil hai. kuchh ne kaha : shayad ye log wo hongey jo Islami daur mein paida huey aur (eik lamha bhi) Allah Taala ke sath shirk nahi kya aur unhon-ne kuchh dusri baton ka bhi tazkira kya phir (kuchh der baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ghar se) nikal kar unke paas tashrif laey aur puchha : tum kin baton mein lagey huey ho? unhon-ne aapko wo baatein bataaiin, is par aap ne farmaya : wo aisey log hain jo na dam kartey hain, na dam karwatey hain, na shagoon letey hain aur wo apne rab par pura bharosaa kartey hain. is par Ukaasha-bin-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha : Allah se dua farmaiye ke wo mujhey bhi un logon main ( shamil ( kar de to aap ne farmaya : to unmein se hai. phir aik aur aadmi khada hua aur kehney laga : dua farmaiye ! Allah mujhey ( bhi) unmein se kar de to aap ne farmaya : Ukasha us ( farmaaish (ke zariey se tum se sabqat ley gaey."
528,"Husain-bin-Abdur-Rehman se ( Hushaim ke bajaey) Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne Saeed-bin-Jubair ke hawale se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere samney tamam ummatein pesh ki gain . . . . . phir hadis ka baqi hissey Hushaim ki tarah bayan kya aur shuruati hissey ( Husain ke waqiey (ka zikr nahi kya."
529,"abu-Ahwas ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Memoon se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : kya tum is baat par razi nahi ke tum ahle-jannat ka chotha hissey ho? ham ne ( khushi se) Allahu-akbar kaha, phir aap ne farmaya : kya tum is par razi na hogey ke tum ahle-jannat ka tehai hissey ho? kaha ke ham ne ( dobara ) narae-takbeer buland kya, phir aap ne farmaya : main ummeed karta hun ke tum ahle-jannat ka aadha hogey aur (ye kaisey hoga?) main iske barey mein abhi bataaunga. kaafiron (ke muqaabley) mein musalman us se zyada nahi jitney siyah rang ke bail mein aik safaid baal ya safaid rang ke bail mein aik siyah baal."
530,"Abu-Ishaq se ( abu-Ahwas ke bajaey) Shoba ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Memoon se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ham taqriban chalis (40) afraad aik khemey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke aap ne farmaya : kya tum is baat par razi hogey ke tum ahle-jannat ka chothai hissey ho? ham ne kaha : haan. to aap ne farmaya : kya tum is par razi ho jaogey ke tum ahle-jannat ka aik tehai hissey ho? ham ne kaha : haan. to aap ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! mujhey ummeed hai ke tum ahle-jannat mein se aadhey hogey aur uski wjah ye hai ke jannat mein us insan ke siwa koi dakhil na hoga jisne khud ko Allah ke sipurd kar diya aur mushrikon mein tumhari tadaad aisi hi hai jaisey siyah bail ki jild par aik safaid baal ya surkh bail ki jald par aik siyah baal."
531,"Maalik-bin-Mighwal ne Abu-Ishaq ke waastey se Amr-bin-Memoon se hadis sunai unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khitab kya aap ne chamdey ke aik khemey se tek lagai hui thi aur farmaya : yad rakho ! jannat mein Islam laney wali Rooh ke siwa koi dakhil na hoga. aey Allaah! kya maine paigham pahuncha diya? aey Allaah! to gawah rehna. kya tum pasand kartey ho ke tum ahle-jannat ka chothai hissey ho? ham ne kaha : ji haan , aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : kya tum pasand kartey ho ke tum ahle-jannat ka tehai hissey ho? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ji haan , aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : mujhey ummeed hai ke tum ahle-jannat ka aadha hogey, dusri ummaton main tum (is se zyada ( nahi ho magar ( aisey ( jis tarah aik siyah baal jo safaid rang ke bail par ho ya aik safaid baal jo siyah bail par ho."
532,"Jarir ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal wala Allah farmaeyga : aey Adam ! wo kahengey : main hazir hun ( mere rab! ( qismat ki khoobi (teri ata hai) aur saari khair terey hath mein hai ! kaha : Allah farmaeyga : dozkhiyon ki jamat ko alag kar do. Adam (Alaihissalam) arz karengey : dozkhiyon ki jamat ( tadaad mein) kya hai? Allah farmaeyga : har hazaar mein se nau so ninyaanwe . ye waqt hoga jab bachchey boodhey ho jaengey. har haamla apna hamal gira degi aur tum logon ko madhosh ki tarah dekhogey, halanke wo (nashey mein) madhosh na hongey balke Allah ka azab hi bahut sakht hoga. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye baat un (sahaaba kiram (rz)) par had darja nagawar guzri. unhon-ne puchha Mina : aey Allah ke rasool! ham mein se wo (eik) aadmi kon hai? to aap ne farmaya : khush ho jao, hazaar yaajooj-maajooj mein se hain aur aik tum mein se hai, (abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir aap ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! mujhey ummeed hai ke tum ahle-jannat ka chothai ( hissey ( hogey. ham ne Allah Taala ki hamd ki aur takbeer kahi ( Allahu-akbar kaha, ( , phir aap ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! mujhey ummeed hai ke tum ahle-jannat ka tehai ( hissey ( hogey. ham ne Allah ki hamd ki aur takbeer kahii, phir farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! mujhey ummeed hai ke tum ahle-jannat ka aadha hissey hogey. (doosri) ummaton ke muqaabley mein tumhari misal us safaid baal ki si hai jo siyah bail ki jild par hota hai ya us chhotey se nishan ki si hai jo gadhey ke agley paon par hota hai."
533,"(Jareer ke bajaey) Aamash ke 2 shagirdon Wakee aur abu-Muawiya ne isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, lekin donon ke alfaz hain is din logon main tum (is se zyada) nahi hogey magar ( aisey ( jis tarah aik safaid baal jo siyah bail par hota hai ya siyah baal jo safaid bail par hota hai. un donon ne gadhey ke agley paon ke nishan ka tazkira nahi kya."
